Text: FLASHFLOOD采用了与SPACESHIP相同的编码方案来处理其阶段性数据

en_text: FLASHFLOOD stages data it copies from the local system or removable drives in the "%WINDIR%\$NtUninstallKB885884$\" directory.
Text: FLASHFLOOD将它从本地系统或可移动驱动器复制的数据放在"%WINDIR%$NtUninstallKB885884$"目录中

en_text: FLASHFLOOD achieves persistence by making an entry in the Registry's Run key.
Text: FLASHFLOOD通过在注册表的 "运行 "键中建立一个条目来实现持久性

en_text: FLASHFLOOD searches for interesting files (either a default or customized set of file extensions) on the local system and removable media.
Text: FLASHFLOOD在本地系统和可移动媒体上搜索有趣的文件（默认或自定义的文件扩展名集）

en_text: FLASHFLOOD searches for interesting files (either a default or customized set of file extensions) on the local system. FLASHFLOOD will scan the My Recent Documents, Desktop, Temporary Internet Files, and TEMP directories. FLASHFLOOD also collects information stored in the Windows Address Book.
Text: FLASHFLOOD在本地系统中搜索有趣的文件（默认或自定义的文件扩展名集）。FLASHFLOOD将扫描我的最近文件、桌面、临时互联网文件和TEMP目录。FLASHFLOOD还收集存储在Windows地址簿中的信息。

en_text: FLASHFLOOD searches for interesting files (either a default or customized set of file extensions) on removable media and copies them to a staging area. The default file types copied would include data copied to the drive by SPACESHIP.
Text: FLASHFLOOD在可移动媒体上搜索有趣的文件（默认或自定义的文件扩展名集），并将其复制到一个暂存区域。复制的默认文件类型将包括由SPACESHIP复制到驱动器上的数据。

en_text: FlawedAmmyy will attempt to detect if a usable smart card is current inserted into a card reader.
Text: FlawedAmmyy将试图检测一个可用的智能卡是否当前被插入读卡器中

en_text: FlawedAmmyy will attempt to detect anti-virus products during the initial infection.
Text: FlawedAmmyy将试图在初始感染期间检测反病毒产品

en_text: FlawedAmmyy leverages WMI to enumerate anti-virus on the victim.
Text: FlawedAmmyy利用WMI来列举受害者身上的防病毒

en_text: FlawedAmmyy enumerates the privilege level of the victim during the initial infection.
Text: FlawedAmmyy列举了受害者在最初感染时的权限级别

en_text: FlawedAmmyy enumerates the current user during the initial infection.
Text: FlawedAmmyy枚举了初始感染期间的当前用户

en_text: FlawedAmmyy has used HTTP for C2.
Text: FlawedAmmyy已将HTTP用于C2

en_text: FlawedAmmyy has used SEAL encryption during the initial C2 handshake.
Text: FlawedAmmyy在最初的C2握手中使用了SEAL加密技术

en_text: FlawedGrace encrypts its C2 configuration files with AES in CBC mode.
Text: FlawedGrace在CBC模式下用AES对其C2配置文件进行加密

en_text: FLIPSIDE uses RDP to tunnel traffic from a victim environment.
Text: FLIPSIDE使用RDP从受害者环境中进行隧道通信

en_text: Forfiles can be used to subvert controls and possibly conceal command execution by not directly invoking cmd.
Text: Forfiles可以用来颠覆控制，并可能通过不直接调用cmd来掩盖命令的执行

en_text: Forfiles can be used to locate certain types of files/directories in a system.(ex: locate all files with a specific extension, name, and/or age)
Text: Forfiles可以用来定位某些类型的文件 Forfiles可用于定位某些类型的文件 Forfiles可以用来查找某些类型的文件 Forfiles可用来定位某些类型的文件

en_text: Forfiles can be used to act on (ex: copy, move, etc.) files/directories in a system during (ex: copy files into a staging area before).
Text: Forfiles可以用来对文件采取行动（例如：复制、移动等）

en_text: FrameworkPOS can collect elements related to credit card data from process memory.
Text: FrameworkPOS可以从进程内存中收集与信用卡数据有关的元素

en_text: FrameworkPOS can enumerate and exclude selected processes on a compromised host to speed execution of memory scraping.
Text: FrameworkPOS可以列举并排除被攻击主机上的选定进程，以加快执行内存搜刮

en_text: FrameworkPOS can identifiy payment card track data on the victim and copy it to a local file in a subdirectory of C:\Windows.
Text: FrameworkPOS可以识别受害者的支付卡跟踪数据，并将其复制到C:\Windows的一个子目录中的本地文件

en_text: FrameworkPOS can use DNS tunneling for exfiltration of credit card data.
Text: FrameworkPOS可以使用DNS隧道来渗出信用卡数据

en_text: FrameworkPOS can XOR credit card information before exfiltration.
Text: FrameworkPOS可以在渗出前XOR信用卡信息

en_text: Frankenstein has enumerated hosts, looking for the public IP address of the system.
Text: Frankenstein列举了主机，寻找系统的公共IP地址

en_text: Frankenstein has enumerated hosts, looking for the system's machine name.
Text: Frankenstein列举了主机，寻找系统的机器名称

en_text: Frankenstein has enumerated hosts via Empire, gathering the username, domain name, machine name, and other system information.
Text: Frankenstein通过Empire列举了主机，收集了用户名、域名、机器名称和其他系统信息

en_text: FruitFly takes screenshots of the user's desktop.
Text: FruitFly对用户的桌面进行截图

en_text: FruitFly will delete files on the system.
Text: FruitFly将删除系统中的文件

en_text: FruitFly executes and stores obfuscated Perl scripts.
Text: FruitFly可以执行和存储混淆的Perl脚本

en_text: FruitFly persists via a Launch Agent.
Text: FruitFly通过一个启动代理持续存在

en_text: FruitFly looks for specific files and file types.
Text: FruitFly寻找特定的文件和文件类型

en_text: FruitFly has the ability to list processes on the system.
Text: FruitFly有能力列出系统中的进程

en_text: FruitFly saves itself with a leading "." to make it a hidden file.
Text: FruitFly在保存自己的时候，会在前面加一个"."，使其成为一个隐藏文件

en_text: FTP may be used to exfiltrate data separate from the main command and control protocol.
Text: FTP可被用于渗出数据，与主命令和控制协议分开

en_text: Fysbis has the ability to create and execute commands in a remote shell for CLI.
Text: Fysbis 具有在远程 shell 中创建和执行 CLI 命令的能力

en_text: Fysbis can perform keylogging.
Text: Fysbis可以进行键盘记录

en_text: Fysbis can use Base64 to encode its C2 traffic.
Text: Fysbis可以使用Base64对其C2流量进行编码

en_text: Fysbis can collect information about running processes.
Text: Fysbis可以收集运行中的进程信息

en_text: Fysbis has used the command ls /etc | egrep -e"fedora*|debian*|gentoo*|mandriva*|mandrake*|meego*|redhat*|lsb-*|sun-*|SUSE*|release" to determine which Linux OS version is running.
Text: Fysbis使用了命令ls Fysbis使用了ls命令 Fysbis使用了ls指令 Fysbis用命令ls

en_text: Fysbis has masqueraded as the rsyncd and dbus-inotifier services.
Text: Fysbis伪装成rsyncd和dbus-inotifier服务

en_text: Fysbis has masqueraded as trusted software rsyncd and dbus-inotifier.
Text: Fysbis伪装成可信的软件rsyncd和dbus-inotifier

en_text: Fysbis has established persistence using a systemd service.
Text: Fysbis已经使用systemd服务建立了持久性

en_text: Fysbis has been encrypted using XOR and RC4.
Text: Fysbis已经用XOR和RC4进行了加密

en_text: Fysbis has the ability to delete files.
Text: Fysbis有删除文件的能力

en_text: Fysbis has the ability to search for files.
Text: Fysbis有搜索文件的能力

en_text: Gallmaker sent emails with malicious Microsoft Office documents attached.
Text: Gallmaker发送了附有恶意微软Office文档的电子邮件

en_text: Gallmaker used PowerShell to download additional payloads and for execution.
Text: Gallmaker使用PowerShell下载额外的有效载荷并进行执行

en_text: Gallmaker has used WinZip, likely to archive data prior to exfiltration.
Text: Gallmaker使用了WinZip，可能是为了在渗出前对数据进行存档

en_text: Gallmaker attempted to exploit Microsoft’s DDE protocol in order to gain access to victim machines and for execution.
Text: Gallmaker试图利用微软的DDE协议，以获得对受害者机器的访问并进行执行

en_text: Gallmaker sent victims a lure document with a warning that asked victims to "enable content" for execution.
Text: Gallmaker向受害者发送了一份带有警告的引诱文件，要求受害者 "启用内容 "以便执行

en_text: Gamaredon Group macros can scan for Microsoft Word and Excel files to inject with additional malicious macros. Gamaredon Group has also used its backdoors to automatically list interesting files (such as Office documents) found on a system.
Text: Gamaredon Group的宏程序可以扫描微软的Word和Excel文件，以注入额外的恶意宏程序。Gamaredon集团还利用其后门自动列出在系统中发现的有趣文件（如Office文档）。

en_text: Gamaredon Group has created a scheduled task to launch an executable every 10 minutes.
Text: Gamaredon集团创建了一个计划任务，每10分钟启动一个可执行文件

en_text: Gamaredon Group has collected files from infected systems and uploaded them to a C2 server.
Text: Gamaredon集团从受感染的系统中收集文件并将其上传到C2服务器

en_text: Gamaredon Group's malware can take screenshots of the compromised computer every minute.
Text: Gamaredon集团的恶意软件可以每分钟对被攻击的电脑进行截图

en_text: Gamaredon Group malware can insert malicious macros into documents using a Microsoft.Office.Interop object.
Text: Gamaredon集团的恶意软件可以使用Microsoft.Office.Interop对象在文档中插入恶意宏

en_text: Gamaredon Group malware has used rundll32 to launch additional malicious components.
Text: Gamaredon集团的恶意软件使用rundll32来启动其他恶意组件

en_text: Gamaredon Group malware has collected Microsoft Office documents from mapped network drives.
Text: Gamaredon集团的恶意软件已经从映射的网络驱动器中收集了微软的办公文件

en_text: Gamaredon Group malware has used CreateProcess to launch additional malicious components.
Text: Gamaredon集团的恶意软件已经使用CreateProcess来启动其他恶意组件

en_text: Gamaredon Group tools have contained an application to check performance of USB flash drives. Gamaredon Group has also used malware to scan for removable drives.
Text: Gamaredon集团的工具包含了一个检查USB闪存驱动器性能的应用程序。Gamaredon集团还使用恶意软件来扫描可移动驱动器。

en_text: Gamaredon Group tools decrypted additional payloads from the C2. Gamaredon Group has also decoded base64-encoded source code of a downloader.
Text: Gamaredon集团的工具从C2中解密了额外的有效载荷。Gamaredon集团还解密了一个下载器的base64编码的源代码。

en_text: Gamaredon Group tools can delete files used during an infection.
Text: Gamaredon集团的工具可以删除感染期间使用的文件

en_text: Gamaredon Group tools have registered Run keys in the registry to give malicious VBS files persistence.
Text: Gamaredon集团的工具在注册表中注册了 "运行 "键，使恶意的VBS文件具有持久性

en_text: A Gamaredon Group file stealer has the capability to steal data from newly connected logical volumes on a system, including USB drives.
Text: Gamaredon集团的文件窃取器有能力从系统上新连接的逻辑卷中窃取数据，包括USB驱动器

en_text: A Gamaredon Group file stealer can transfer collected files to a hardcoded C2 server.
Text: Gamaredon集团的文件窃取者可以将收集到的文件传输到一个硬编码的C2服务器

en_text: A Gamaredon Group file stealer can gather the victim's computer name and drive serial numbers to send to a C2 server.
Text: Gamaredon集团的文件窃取者可以收集受害者的计算机名称和驱动器序列号，以发送至C2服务器

en_text: A Gamaredon Group file stealer can gather the victim's username to send to a C2 server.
Text: Gamaredon集团的文件窃取者可以收集受害者的用户名，以发送至C2服务器

en_text: A Gamaredon Group file stealer can communicate over HTTP for C2.
Text: Gamaredon集团的文件窃取者可以通过HTTP进行C2通信

en_text: Gamaredon Group has used DOCX files to download malicious DOT document templates. Gamaredon Group can also inject malicious macros or remote templates into documents already present on compromised systems.
Text: Gamaredon集团利用DOCX文件下载恶意的DOT文件模板。Gamaredon集团还可以将恶意的宏或远程模板注入到已经存在于被攻击系统的文件中。

en_text: Tools used by Gamaredon Group are capable of downloading and executing additional payloads.
Text: Gamaredon集团使用的工具能够下载和执行额外的有效载荷

en_text: Gamaredon Group has used GitHub repositories for downloaders which will be obtained by the group's .NET executable on the compromised system.
Text: Gamaredon集团使用了GitHub存储库的下载器，这些下载器将由该集团的.NET可执行程序在被攻击的系统上获得

en_text: Gamaredon Group has compiled the source code for a downloader directly on the infected system using the built-in Microsoft.CSharp.CSharpCodeProvider class.
Text: Gamaredon集团使用内置的Microsoft.CSharp.CSharpCodeProvider类在受感染的系统上直接编译了一个下载器的源代码

en_text: Gamaredon Group has attempted to get users to click on Office attachments with malicious macros embedded.
Text: Gamaredon集团试图让用户点击嵌入有恶意宏的Office附件

en_text: Gamaredon Group has obfuscated .NET executables by inserting junk code.
Text: Gamaredon集团通过插入垃圾代码混淆了.NET可执行文件

en_text: Gamaredon Group has removed security settings for VBA macro execution by changing registry values HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Office\<version>\<product>\Security\VBAWarnings and HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Office\<version>\<product>\Security\AccessVBOM.
Text: Gamaredon集团通过改变注册表值HKCU\Software\MicrosoftOffice\<version>\<product>Security\VBAWarnings和HKCU\Software\MicrosoftOffice\<version>\<product>Security\AccessVBOM来删除VBA宏执行的安全设置

en_text: Gamaredon Group has delivered spearphishing emails with malicious attachments to targets.
Text: Gamaredon集团向目标发送了带有恶意附件的鱼叉式网络钓鱼邮件

en_text: Gamaredon Group has delivered macros which can tamper with Microsoft Office security settings.
Text: Gamaredon集团已经交付了可以篡改微软Office安全设置的宏

en_text: Gamaredon Group has used modules that automatically upload gathered documents to the C2 server.
Text: Gamaredon集团已经使用了自动上传收集的文件到C2服务器的模块

en_text: Gamaredon Group has deployed scripts on compromised systems that automatically scan for interesting documents.
Text: Gamaredon集团已经在被破坏的系统上部署了脚本，自动扫描有趣的文件

en_text: Gamaredon Group has used various batch scripts to establish C2 and download additional files. Gamaredon Group's backdoor malware has also been written to a batch file.
Text: Gamaredon集团已使用各种批处理脚本建立C2和下载额外的文件。Gamaredon集团的后门恶意软件也被写入了一个批处理文件。

en_text: Gamaredon Group has delivered self-extracting 7z archive files within malicious document attachments, and used obfuscated or encrypted scripts.
Text: Gamaredon集团在恶意文件附件中提供自解压的7z档案文件，并使用混淆或加密的脚本

en_text: Gamaredon Group has used an Outlook VBA module on infected systems to send phishing emails with malicious attachments to other employees within the organization.
Text: Gamaredon集团在受感染的系统上使用Outlook VBA模块，向组织内的其他员工发送带有恶意附件的网络钓鱼邮件

en_text: Gamaredon Group has embedded malicious macros in document templates, which executed VBScript. Gamaredon Group has also delivered Microsoft Outlook VBA projects with embedded macros.
Text: Gamaredon集团在文件模板中嵌入了恶意的宏，执行VBScript。Gamaredon集团还交付了嵌入宏的Microsoft Outlook VBA项目。

en_text: Gamaredon Group has inserted malicious macros into existing documents, providing persistence when they are reopened. Gamaredon Group has loaded the group's previously delivered VBA project by relaunching Microsoft Outlook with the /altvba option, once the Application.Startup event is received.
Text: Gamaredon集团在现有的文件中插入了恶意的宏，当它们被重新打开时提供持久性。Gamaredon集团通过使用/altvba选项重新启动微软Outlook，一旦收到Application.Startup事件，就会加载该集团先前交付的VBA项目

en_text: Gamaredon Group has injected malicious macros into all Word and Excel documents on mapped network drives.
Text: Gamaredon集团在映射的网络驱动器上的所有Word和Excel文档中注入了恶意的宏程序

en_text: Gazer versions are signed with various valid certificates; one was likely faked and issued by Comodo for "Solid Loop Ltd," and another was issued for "Ultimate Computer Support Ltd."
Text: Gazer版本使用各种有效证书签名；其中一个可能是伪造的，由Comodo为 "Solid Loop Ltd "签发，另一个是为 "Ultimate Computer Support Ltd "签发

en_text: Gazer uses custom encryption for C2 that uses 3DES.
Text: Gazer对C2使用自定义加密，该加密使用3DES

en_text: Gazer uses custom encryption for C2 that uses RSA.
Text: Gazer对使用RSA的C2使用自定义加密

en_text: Gazer obtains the current user's security identifier.
Text: Gazer获取当前用户的安全标识符

en_text: Gazer injects its communication module into an Internet accessible process through which it performs C2.
Text: Gazer将其通信模块注入一个可访问的互联网进程，通过该进程执行C2

en_text: Gazer logs its actions into files that are encrypted with 3DES. It also uses RSA to encrypt resources.
Text: Gazer将其行动记录在用3DES加密的文件中

en_text: Gazer can establish persistence by creating a scheduled task.
Text: Gazer可以通过创建一个计划任务来建立持久性

en_text: Gazer can establish persistence through the system screensaver by configuring it to execute the malware.
Text: Gazer可以通过配置系统屏幕保护程序来执行恶意软件，从而建立持久性

en_text: Gazer can establish persistence by creating a .lnk file in the Start menu or by modifying existing .lnk files to execute the malware through cmd.exe.
Text: Gazer可以通过在 "开始 "菜单中创建一个.lnk文件，或通过修改现有的.lnk文件，通过cmd.exe执行恶意软件，建立持久性

en_text: Gazer can establish persistence by creating a .lnk file in the Start menu.
Text: Gazer可以通过在开始菜单中创建一个.lnk文件来建立持久性

en_text: Gazer can establish persistence by setting the value "Shell" with "explorer.exe, %malware_pathfile%" under the Registry key HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon.
Text: Gazer可以通过在注册表键HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon下设置 "Shell "值为 "explorer.exe, %malware_pathfile%"来建立持久性

en_text: Gazer can execute a task to download a file.
Text: Gazer可以执行一个任务来下载一个文件

en_text: Gazer communicates with its C2 servers over HTTP.
Text: Gazer通过HTTP与它的C2服务器进行通信

en_text: Gazer has commands to delete files and persistence mechanisms from the victim.
Text: Gazer有删除文件和受害者的持久性机制的命令

en_text: Gazer performs thread execution hijacking to inject its orchestrator into a running thread from a remote process.
Text: Gazer执行线程执行劫持，将其协调器注入来自远程进程的运行线程中

en_text: GCMAN uses Putty for lateral movement.
Text: GCMAN使用Putty进行横向移动

en_text: GCMAN uses VNC for lateral movement.
Text: GCMAN使用VNC进行横向移动

en_text: GeminiDuke collects information on running processes and environment variables from the victim.
Text: GeminiDuke从受害者那里收集关于运行进程和环境变量的信息

en_text: GeminiDuke collects information on local user accounts from the victim.
Text: GeminiDuke会收集受害者的本地用户账户信息

en_text: GeminiDuke collects information on network settings and Internet proxy settings from the victim.
Text: GeminiDuke会收集受害者的网络设置和互联网代理设置信息

en_text: GeminiDuke collects information on programs and services on the victim that are configured to automatically run at startup.
Text: GeminiDuke会收集受害者身上被配置为在启动时自动运行的程序和服务的信息

en_text: GeminiDuke uses HTTP and HTTPS for command and control.
Text: GeminiDuke使用HTTP和HTTPS进行指挥和控制

en_text: GeminiDuke collects information from the victim, including installed drivers, programs previously executed by users, programs and services configured to automatically run at startup, files and folders present in any user's home folder, files and folders present in any user's My Documents, programs installed to the Program Files folder, and recently accessed files, folders, and programs.
Text: GeminiDuke收集受害者的信息，包括已安装的驱动程序、用户以前执行的程序、配置为在启动时自动运行的程序和服务、存在于任何用户的主文件夹中的文件和文件夹、存在于任何用户的我的文档中的文件和文件夹、安装到Program Files文件夹中的程序以及最近访问的文件、文件夹和程序

en_text: Get2 has the ability to run executables with command-line arguments.
Text: Get2具有用命令行参数运行可执行文件的能力

en_text: Get2 has the ability to inject DLLs into processes.
Text: Get2有能力将DLLs注入到进程中

en_text: Get2 has the ability to identify the current username of an infected host.
Text: Get2有能力识别受感染主机的当前用户名

en_text: Get2 has the ability to identify the computer name and Windows version of an infected host.
Text: Get2有能力识别受感染主机的计算机名称和Windows版本

en_text: Get2 has the ability to identify running processes on an infected host.
Text: Get2有能力识别受感染主机上的运行进程

en_text: Get2 has the ability to use HTTP to send information collected from an infected host to C2.
Text: Get2有能力使用HTTP将从受感染主机收集的信息发送到C2

en_text: gh0st RAT    has encrypted TCP communications to evade detection.
Text: gh0st RAT对TCP通信进行了加密，以躲避检测

en_text: gh0st RAT can create a new service to establish persistence.
Text: gh0st RAT可以创建一个新的服务来建立持久性

en_text: gh0st RAT can load DLLs into memory.
Text: gh0st RAT可以将DLLs加载到内存中

en_text: gh0st RAT can download files to the victim’s machine.
Text: gh0st RAT可以下载文件到受害者的机器

en_text: gh0st RAT can inject malicious code into process created by the "Command_Create&Inject" function.
Text: gh0st RAT可以向由 "Command_Create "创建的进程注入恶意代码

en_text: gh0st RAT can capture the victim’s screen remotely.
Text: gh0st RAT可以远程捕获受害者的屏幕

en_text: gh0st RAT is able to wipe event logs.
Text: gh0st RAT能够擦除事件日志

en_text: gh0st RAT is able to open a remote shell to execute commands.
Text: gh0st RAT能够打开一个远程外壳来执行命令

en_text: gh0st RAT uses RC4 and XOR to encrypt C2 traffic.
Text: gh0st RAT使用RC4和XOR来加密C2流量

en_text: gh0st RAT has altered the InstallTime subkey.
Text: gh0st RAT已经改变了InstallTime子键

en_text: gh0st RAT has checked for the existence of a Service key to determine if it has already been installed on the system.
Text: gh0st RAT已经检查了服务密钥的存在，以确定它是否已经被安装在系统上

en_text: gh0st RAT has decrypted and loaded the gh0st RAT DLL into memory, once the initial dropper executable is launched.
Text: gh0st RAT已经解密并将gh0st RAT DLL加载到内存中，一旦启动初始dropper可执行文件

en_text: gh0st RAT has used the InterlockedExchange, SeShutdownPrivilege, and ExitWindowsEx Windows API functions.
Text: gh0st RAT已经使用了InterlockedExchange、SeShutdownPrivilege和ExitWindowsEx Windows API函数

en_text: gh0st RAT has gathered system architecture, processor, OS configuration, and installed hardware information.
Text: gh0st RAT已经收集了系统结构、处理器、操作系统配置和已安装的硬件信息

en_text: gh0st RAT has the capability to list processes.
Text: gh0st RAT有能力列出进程

en_text: gh0st RAT has the capability to to delete files.
Text: gh0st RAT有能力删除文件

en_text: gh0st RAT has a keylogger.
Text: gh0st RAT有一个键盘记录器

en_text: gh0st RAT    operators have used dynamic DNS to mask the true location of their C2 behind rapidly changing IP addresses.
Text: gh0st RAT运营商使用动态DNS来掩盖其C2在快速变化的IP地址后面的真实位置

en_text: gh0st RAT has used an encrypted protocol within TCP segments to communicate with the C2.
Text: gh0st RAT在TCP段内使用了一个加密协议与C2进行通信

en_text: gh0st RAT has used Zlib to compress C2 communications data before encrypting it.
Text: gh0st RAT在加密前使用Zlib来压缩C2通信数据

en_text: gh0st RAT has added a Registry Run key to establish persistence.
Text: gh0st RAT增加了一个注册表运行键来建立持久性

en_text: GLOOXMAIL communicates to servers operated by Google using the Jabber/XMPP protocol.
Text: GLOOXMAIL使用Jabber与谷歌运营的服务器进行通信

en_text: Gold Dragon checks the running processes on the victim’s machine.
Text: Gold Dragon检查受害者机器上的运行进程

en_text: Gold Dragon uses cmd.exe to execute commands for discovery.
Text: Gold Dragon使用cmd.exe来执行发现的命令

en_text: Gold Dragon collects endpoint information using the systeminfo command.
Text: Gold Dragon使用systeminfo命令收集端点信息

en_text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD has conducted malicious spam (malspam) campaigns to gain access to victim's machines.
Text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD进行了恶意的垃圾邮件（malspam）活动，以获得对受害者机器的访问

en_text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD has exploited Oracle WebLogic vulnerabilities for initial compromise.
Text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD利用Oracle WebLogic的漏洞进行了初步破坏

en_text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD has used publicly-accessible RDP and remote management and monitoring (RMM) servers to gain access to victim machines.
Text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD利用可公开访问的RDP和远程管理和监控（RMM）服务器来获得对受害者机器的访问

en_text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD has distributed ransomware by backdooring software installers via a strategic web compromise of the site hosting Italian WinRAR.
Text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD通过对托管意大利WinRAR的网站进行战略性网络妥协，通过后门软件安装程序分发赎金软件

en_text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD has breached Managed Service Providers (MSP's) to deliver malware to MSP customers.
Text: GOLD SOUTHFIELD已经侵入管理服务提供商（MSP），向MSP客户提供恶意软件

en_text: GoldenSpy has included a program "ExeProtector", which monitors for the existence of GoldenSpy on the infected system and redownloads if necessary.
Text: GoldenSpy包含一个程序 "ExeProtector"，它可以监测受感染系统中是否存在GoldenSpy，并在必要时重新下载

en_text: GoldenSpy constantly attempts to download and execute files from the remote C2, including GoldenSpy itself if not found on the system.
Text: GoldenSpy不断尝试从远程C2下载和执行文件，包括GoldenSpy本身，如果在系统中没有发现

en_text: GoldenSpy's installer has delayed installation of GoldenSpy for two hours after it reaches a victim system.
Text: GoldenSpy的安装程序在到达受害者系统后，已经将GoldenSpy的安装时间推迟了两个小时

en_text: GoldenSpy's setup file installs initial executables under the folder %WinDir%\System32\PluginManager.
Text: GoldenSpy的设置文件在%WinDir%\System32\PluginManager文件夹下安装初始可执行文件

en_text: GoldenSpy's uninstaller has base64-encoded its variables.
Text: GoldenSpy的卸载程序对其变量进行了base64编码

en_text: GoldenSpy's uninstaller can delete registry entries, files and folders, and finally itself once these tasks have been completed.
Text: GoldenSpy的卸载程序可以删除注册表项、文件和文件夹，一旦这些任务完成，最后自己也可以删除

en_text: GoldenSpy can execute remote commands in the Windows command shell using the WinExec() API.
Text: GoldenSpy可以使用WinExec()API在Windows命令壳中执行远程命令

en_text: GoldenSpy can execute remote commands via the command-line interface.
Text: GoldenSpy可以通过命令行界面执行远程命令

en_text: GoldenSpy can create new users on an infected system.
Text: GoldenSpy可以在受感染的系统上创建新用户

en_text: GoldenSpy has used the Ryeol HTTP Client to facilitate HTTP internet communication.
Text: GoldenSpy使用了Ryeol HTTP客户端来促进HTTP互联网通信

en_text: GoldenSpy has exfiltrated host environment information to an external C2 domain via port 9006.
Text: GoldenSpy通过9006端口将主机环境信息外泄到外部C2域

en_text: GoldenSpy has used HTTP over ports 9005 and 9006 for network traffic, 9002 for C2 requests, 33666 as a WebSocket, and 8090 to download files.
Text: GoldenSpy通过端口9005和9006使用HTTP进行网络通信，9002用于C2请求，33666作为WebSocket，8090用于下载文件

en_text: GoldenSpy has established persistence by running in the background as an autostart service.
Text: GoldenSpy通过作为自动启动服务在后台运行，建立了持久性

en_text: GoldenSpy has been packaged with a legitimate tax preparation software.
Text: GoldenSpy已被包装成一个合法的报税软件

en_text: GoldenSpy has gathered operating system information.
Text: GoldenSpy已经收集了操作系统的信息

en_text: Goopy's decrypter have been inflated with junk code in between legitimate API functions, and also included infinite loops to avoid analysis.
Text: Goopy的解密器在合法的API函数之间添加了垃圾代码，还包括无限循环以避免分析

en_text: Goopy has impersonated the legitimate goopdate.dll, which was dropped on the target system with a legitimate GoogleUpdate.exe.
Text: Goopy冒充合法的goopdate.dll，用合法的GoogleUpdate.exe投放到目标系统

en_text: Goopy has used a polymorphic decryptor to decrypt itself at runtime.
Text: Goopy使用了一个多态的解密器，在运行时解密自己

en_text: Goopy has checked for the Google Updater process to ensure Goopy was loaded properly.
Text: Goopy已经检查了Google Updater进程，以确保Goopy被正确加载

en_text: Goopy has the ability to exfiltrate documents from infected systems.
Text: Goopy有能力从受感染的系统中渗出文件

en_text: Goopy has the ability to disable Microsoft Outlook's security policies to disable macro warnings.
Text: Goopy有能力禁用微软Outlook的安全策略来禁用宏警告

en_text: Goopy has the ability to enumerate the infected system's user name.
Text: Goopy有能力列举被感染系统的用户名

en_text: Goopy has the ability to use cmd.exe to execute commands passed from an Outlook C2 channel.
Text: Goopy有能力使用cmd.exe来执行从Outlook C2通道传递的命令

en_text: Goopy has the ability to use a Microsoft Outlook backdoor macro to communicate with its C2.
Text: Goopy有能力使用微软Outlook的后门宏来与它的C2通信

en_text: Goopy has the ability to communicate with its C2 over DNS.
Text: Goopy有能力通过DNS与它的C2通信

en_text: Goopy has the ability to  enumerate the infected system's user name via GetUserNameW.
Text: Goopy有能力通过GetUserNameW来列举被感染系统的用户名称

en_text: Goopy has the ability to communicate with its C2 over HTTP.
Text: Goopy有能力通过HTTP与它的C2通信

en_text: Goopy has the ability to maintain persistence by creating scheduled tasks set to run every hour.
Text: Goopy有能力通过创建设置为每小时运行的计划任务来保持持久性

en_text: Goopy has the ability to exfiltrate data over the Microsoft Outlook C2 channel.
Text: Goopy有能力通过微软Outlook C2通道渗出数据

en_text: Goopy has the ability to side-load malicious DLLs with legitimate applications from Kaspersky, Microsoft, and Google.
Text: Goopy有能力在卡巴斯基、微软和谷歌的合法应用程序中侧载恶意DLLs

en_text: Goopy has had null characters padded in its malicious DLL payload.
Text: Goopy在其恶意的DLL有效载荷中填充了空字符

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can create a .lnk file and add a Registry Run key to establish persistence.
Text: Gorgon Group恶意软件可以创建一个.lnk文件并添加一个注册表运行键来建立持久性

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can use process hollowing to inject one of its trojans into another process.
Text: Gorgon Group恶意软件可以利用进程空洞化，将其一个木马程序注入另一个进程中

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can use cmd.exe to download and execute payloads and to execute commands on the system.
Text: Gorgon Group恶意软件可以使用cmd.exe下载和执行有效载荷并在系统上执行命令

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can use PowerShell commands to download and execute a payload and open a decoy document on the victim’s machine.
Text: Gorgon Group恶意软件可以使用PowerShell命令来下载和执行有效载荷，并在受害者的机器上打开一个诱饵文件

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can attempt to disable security features in Microsoft Office and Windows Defender using the taskkill command.
Text: Gorgon Group恶意软件可以使用taskkill命令试图禁用Microsoft Office和Windows Defender的安全功能

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can deactivate security mechanisms in Microsoft Office by editing several keys and values under HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Office\.
Text: Gorgon Group恶意软件可以通过编辑HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Office\下的几个键和值来停用微软办公室的安全机制

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can download a remote access tool, ShiftyBug, and inject into another process.
Text: Gorgon Group恶意软件可以下载一个远程访问工具ShiftyBug，并注入到另一个进程

en_text: Gorgon Group has used -W Hidden to conceal PowerShell windows by setting the WindowStyle parameter to hidden.
Text: Gorgon Group使用了-W Hidden，通过将WindowStyle参数设置为隐藏，来隐藏PowerShell窗口

en_text: Gorgon Group attempted to get users to launch malicious Microsoft Office attachments delivered via spearphishing emails.
Text: Gorgon Group试图让用户启动通过鱼叉式网络钓鱼邮件发送的恶意微软Office附件

en_text: Gorgon Group sent emails to victims with malicious Microsoft Office documents attached.
Text: Gorgon Group向受害者发送了附有恶意微软Office文档的电子邮件

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can download additional files from C2 servers.
Text: Gorgon集团的恶意软件可以从C2服务器下载更多的文件

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can decode contents from a payload that was Base64 encoded and write the contents to a file.
Text: Gorgon集团的恶意软件可以对经过Base64编码的有效载荷的内容进行解码，并将内容写入一个文件

en_text: Gorgon Group malware can leverage the Windows API call, CreateProcessA(), for execution.
Text: Gorgon集团的恶意软件可以利用Windows API调用CreateProcessA()来执行

en_text: Gorgon Group has used macros in Spearphishing Attachments as well as executed VBScripts on victim machines.
Text: Gorgon集团在网络钓鱼附件中使用宏，并在受害者机器上执行VBS脚本

en_text: GravityRAT creates a scheduled task to ensure it is re-executed everyday.
Text: GravityRAT创建了一个计划任务，以确保它每天重新执行

en_text: The author of GravityRAT submitted samples to VirusTotal for testing, showing that the author modified the code to try to hide the DDE object in a different part of the document.
Text: GravityRAT的作者向VirusTotal提交了测试样本，显示作者修改了代码，试图将DDE对象隐藏在文件的不同部分

en_text: GravityRAT can obtain the date and time of a system.
Text: GravityRAT可以获得一个系统的日期和时间

en_text: GravityRAT lists the running processes on the system.
Text: GravityRAT列出了系统上的运行进程

en_text: GravityRAT steals files with the following extensions: .docx, .doc, .pptx, .ppt, .xlsx, .xls, .rtf, and .pdf.
Text: GravityRAT窃取以下扩展名的文件：.docx, .doc, .pptx, .ppt, .xlsx, .xls, .rtf, 和 .pdf

en_text: GravityRAT uses HTTP for C2.
Text: GravityRAT使用HTTP进行C2

en_text: GravityRAT uses the netstat command to find open ports on the victim’s machine.
Text: GravityRAT使用netstat命令来寻找受害者机器上的开放端口

en_text: GravityRAT uses WMI to check the BIOS and manufacturer information for strings like "VMWare", "Virtual", and "XEN" and another WMI request to get the current temperature of the hardware to determine if it's a virtual machine environment.
Text: GravityRAT使用WMI检查BIOS和制造商信息，查看 "VMWare"、"Virtual "和 "XEN "等字符串，并使用另一个WMI请求来获取硬件的当前温度，以确定它是否是一个虚拟机环境

en_text: GravityRAT collects the MAC address, computer name, and CPU information.
Text: GravityRAT收集了MAC地址、计算机名称和CPU信息

en_text: GravityRAT collects the victim IP address, MAC address, as well as the victim account domain name.
Text: GravityRAT收集了受害者的IP地址、MAC地址以及受害者账户域名

en_text: GravityRAT collects the victim username along with other account information (account type, description, full name, SID and status).
Text: GravityRAT收集了受害者的用户名以及其他账户信息（账户类型、描述、全名、SID和状态）

en_text: GravityRAT collects the volumes mapped on the system, and also steals files with the following extensions: .docx, .doc, .pptx, .ppt, .xlsx, .xls, .rtf, and .pdf.
Text: GravityRAT收集系统上映射的卷，也偷取具有以下扩展名的文件：.docx, .doc, .pptx, .ppt, .xlsx, .xls, .rtf, 和.pdf

en_text: GravityRAT collects various information via WMI requests, including CPU information in the Win32_Processor entry (Processor ID, Name, Manufacturer and the clock speed).
Text: GravityRAT通过WMI请求收集各种信息，包括Win32_Processor条目中的CPU信息（处理器ID、名称、制造商和时钟速度）

en_text: GravityRAT has used HTTP over a non-standard port, such as TCP port 46769.
Text: GravityRAT通过一个非标准端口使用HTTP，如TCP端口46769

en_text: GravityRAT has been delivered via Word documents using DDE for execution.
Text: GravityRAT已经通过使用DDE执行的Word文档交付

en_text: GravityRAT has a feature to list the available services on the system.
Text: GravityRAT有一个功能，列出系统上的可用服务

en_text: GravityRAT executes commands remotely on the infected host.
Text: GravityRAT在受感染的主机上远程执行命令

en_text: GravityRAT supports file encryption (AES with the key "lolomycin2017").
Text: GravityRAT支持文件加密（AES与密钥 "lolomycin2017"）

en_text: GreyEnergy has used Tor relays for Command and Control servers.
Text: GreyEnergy公司将Tor中继器用于指挥和控制服务器

en_text: GreyEnergy can securely delete a file by hooking into the DeleteFileA and DeleteFileW functions in the Windows API.
Text: GreyEnergy可以通过与Windows API中的DeleteFileA和DeleteFileW函数挂钩，安全地删除一个文件

en_text: GreyEnergy can download additional modules and payloads.
Text: GreyEnergy可以下载额外的模块和有效载荷

en_text: GreyEnergy enumerates all Windows services.
Text: GreyEnergy列举了所有的Windows服务

en_text: GreyEnergy encrypts communications using AES256.
Text: GreyEnergy使用AES256对通信进行加密

en_text: GreyEnergy uses cmd.exe to execute itself in-memory.
Text: GreyEnergy使用cmd.exe来在内存中执行自己

en_text: GreyEnergy uses HTTP and HTTPS for C2 communications.
Text: GreyEnergy使用HTTP和HTTPS进行C2通信

en_text: GreyEnergy encrypts communications using RSA-2048.
Text: GreyEnergy使用RSA-2048对通信进行加密

en_text: GreyEnergy is packed for obfuscation.
Text: GreyEnergy是为混淆视听而包装的

en_text: GreyEnergy modifies conditions in the Registry and adds keys.
Text: GreyEnergy修改了注册表中的条件并增加了密钥

en_text: GreyEnergy chooses a service, drops a DLL file, and writes it to that serviceDLL Registry key.
Text: GreyEnergy选择一个服务，丢弃一个DLL文件，并将其写入该serviceDLL注册表键

en_text: GreyEnergy encrypts its configuration files with AES-256 and also encrypts its strings.
Text: GreyEnergy用AES-256对其配置文件进行加密，并对其字符串进行加密

en_text: GreyEnergy digitally signs the malware with a code-signing certificate.
Text: GreyEnergy用代码签名证书对恶意软件进行数字签名

en_text: GreyEnergy has a module for Mimikatz to collect Windows credentials from the victim’s machine.
Text: GreyEnergy有一个Mimikatz模块，用于收集受害者机器上的Windows凭证

en_text: GreyEnergy has a module to harvest pressed keystrokes.
Text: GreyEnergy有一个模块可以收集按下的键盘

en_text: GreyEnergy has a module to inject a PE binary into a remote process.
Text: GreyEnergy有一个模块可以向远程进程注入PE二进制文件

en_text: GreyEnergy uses PsExec locally in order to execute rundll32.exe at the highest privileges (NTAUTHORITY\SYSTEM).
Text: GreyEnergy在本地使用PsExec，以便以最高权限（NTAUTHORITY/SYSTEM）执行rundll32.exe

en_text: GRIFFON has used PowerShell to execute the Meterpreter downloader TinyMet.
Text: GRIFFON使用PowerShell来执行Meterpreter下载器TinyMet

en_text: GRIFFON has used sctasks for persistence.
Text: GRIFFON使用了sctasks的持久性

en_text: GRIFFON has used a persistence module that stores the implant inside the Registry, which executes at logon.
Text: GRIFFON使用了一个持久性模块，将植入物存储在注册表内，在登录时执行

en_text: GRIFFON has used a screenshot module that can be used to take a screenshot of the remote system.
Text: GRIFFON使用了一个屏幕截图模块，可以用来对远程系统进行屏幕截图

en_text: GRIFFON has used a reconnaissance module that can be used to retrieve the date and time of the system.
Text: GRIFFON使用了一个侦查模块，可以用来检索系统的日期和时间

en_text: GRIFFON has used a reconnaissance module that can be used to retrieve Windows domain membership information.
Text: GRIFFON使用了一个侦察模块，可以用来检索Windows域成员信息

en_text: GRIFFON has used a reconnaissance module that can be used to retrieve information about a victim's computer, including the resolution of the workstation .
Text: GRIFFON使用了一个侦察模块，可以用来检索受害者计算机的信息，包括工作站的分辨率

en_text: GRIFFON is written in and executed as JavaScript/JScript.
Text: GRIFFON是用JavaScript编写和执行的

en_text: Malware used by Group5 is capable of capturing keystrokes.
Text: Group5使用的恶意软件能够捕捉到键盘信息

en_text: Malware used by Group5 is capable of watching the victim's screen.
Text: Group5使用的恶意软件能够监视受害者的屏幕

en_text: Malware used by Group5 is capable of remotely deleting files from victims.
Text: Group5使用的恶意软件能够远程删除受害者的文件

en_text: Group5 disguised its malicious binaries with several layers of obfuscation, including encrypting the files.
Text: Group5用几层混淆法来掩饰其恶意二进制文件，包括对文件进行加密

en_text: gsecdump can dump LSA secrets.
Text: gsecdump 可以转储 LSA 秘密

en_text: gsecdump can dump Windows password hashes from the SAM.
Text: gsecdump可以从SAM中转储Windows密码哈希值。

en_text: H1N1 contains a command to download and execute a file from a remotely hosted URL using WinINet HTTP requests.
Text: H1N1包含一个使用WinINet HTTP请求从远程托管的URL下载和执行一个文件的命令

en_text: H1N1 kills and disables services for Windows Security Center, and Windows Defender.
Text: H1N1病毒杀死并禁用了Windows安全中心和Windows Defender的服务

en_text: H1N1 kills and disables services for Windows Firewall.
Text: H1N1病毒杀死并禁用了Windows防火墙的服务

en_text: H1N1 dumps usernames and passwords from Firefox, Internet Explorer, and Outlook.
Text: H1N1将用户名和密码从Firefox、Internet Explorer和Outlook中转出

en_text: H1N1 has functionality to copy itself to network shares.
Text: H1N1具有将自己复制到网络共享的功能

en_text: H1N1 has functionality to copy itself to removable media.
Text: H1N1具有将自身复制到可移动媒体的功能

en_text: H1N1 disable recovery options and deletes shadow copies from the victim.
Text: H1N1使恢复选项失效，并删除了受害者的影子副本

en_text: H1N1 encrypts C2 traffic using an RC4 key.
Text: H1N1使用RC4密钥对C2流量进行加密

en_text: H1N1 uses multiple techniques to obfuscate strings, including XOR.
Text: H1N1使用多种技术来混淆字符串，包括XOR

en_text: H1N1 uses a custom packing algorithm.
Text: H1N1使用了一种定制的包装算法

en_text: H1N1 bypasses user access control by using a DLL hijacking vulnerability in the Windows Update Standalone Installer (wusa.exe).
Text: H1N1通过利用Windows Update独立安装程序（wusa.exe）中的DLL劫持漏洞绕过用户访问控制

en_text: H1N1 kills and disables services by using cmd.exe.
Text: H1N1通过使用cmd.exe杀死和禁用服务

en_text: H1N1 obfuscates C2 traffic with an altered version of base64.
Text: H1N1用改变过的base64版本混淆了C2流量

en_text: Hacking Team UEFI Rootkit is a UEFI BIOS rootkit developed by the company Hacking Team to persist remote access software on some targeted systems.
Text: Hacking Team UEFI Rootkit是一个由Hacking Team公司开发的UEFI BIOS rootkit，用于在一些目标系统上坚持远程访问软件

en_text: HALFBAKED can obtain screenshots from the victim.
Text: HALFBAKED可以获得受害者的截图

en_text: HALFBAKED can obtain information about running processes on the victim.
Text: HALFBAKED可以获得受害者身上正在运行的进程的信息

en_text: HALFBAKED can obtain information about the OS, processor, and BIOS.
Text: HALFBAKED可以获得有关操作系统、处理器和BIOS的信息

en_text: HALFBAKED can delete a specified file.
Text: HALFBAKED可以删除一个指定的文件

en_text: HALFBAKED can use WMI queries to gather system information.
Text: HALFBAKED可以使用WMI查询来收集系统信息

en_text: HALFBAKED can execute PowerShell scripts.
Text: HALFBAKED可以执行PowerShell脚本

en_text: The "tDiscoverer" variant of HAMMERTOSS establishes a C2 channel by downloading resources from Web services like Twitter and GitHub. HAMMERTOSS binaries contain an algorithm that generates a different Twitter handle for the malware to check for instructions every day.
Text: HAMMERTOSS的 "tDiscoverer "变种通过从Twitter和GitHub等网络服务下载资源建立了一个C2渠道。HAMMERTOSS二进制文件包含一个算法，该算法每天为恶意软件生成一个不同的Twitter手柄以检查指令。

en_text: The "Uploader" variant of HAMMERTOSS visits a hard-coded server over HTTP/S to download the images HAMMERTOSS uses to receive commands.
Text: HAMMERTOSS的 "上传者 "变体通过HTTP访问一个硬编码的服务器

en_text: HAMMERTOSS has used -WindowStyle hidden to conceal PowerShell windows.
Text: HAMMERTOSS使用了-WindowStyle hidden来掩盖PowerShell窗口

en_text: HAMMERTOSS is controlled via commands that are appended to image files.
Text: HAMMERTOSS是通过附加在图像文件上的命令来控制的

en_text: HAMMERTOSS exfiltrates data by uploading it to accounts created by the actors on Web cloud storage providers for the adversaries to retrieve later.
Text: HAMMERTOSS通过将数据上传到行为者在网络云存储供应商上创建的账户，供对手日后检索，从而渗出数据

en_text: Hancitor has decoded Base64 encoded URLs to insert a recipient’s name into the filename of the Word document. Hancitor has also extracted executables from ZIP files.
Text: Hancitor曾对Base64编码的URL进行解码，将收件人的名字插入Word文档的文件名中

en_text: Hancitor has used verclsid.exe to download and execute a malicious script.
Text: Hancitor利用verclsid.exe下载并执行一个恶意脚本

en_text: Hancitor has used Base64 to encode malicious links. Hancitor has also delivered compressed payloads in ZIP files to victims.
Text: Hancitor使用Base64对恶意链接进行编码

en_text: Hancitor has used CallWindowProc and EnumResourceTypesA to interpret and execute shellcode.
Text: Hancitor使用CallWindowProc和EnumResourceTypesA来解释和执行shellcode

en_text: Hancitor has deleted files using the VBA kill function.
Text: Hancitor使用VBA杀毒功能删除了文件

en_text: Hancitor has used malicious Microsoft Word documents, sent via email, which prompted the victim to enable macros.
Text: Hancitor使用恶意的Microsoft Word文件，通过电子邮件发送，促使受害者启用宏

en_text: Hancitor has used PowerShell to execute commands.
Text: Hancitor使用了PowerShell来执行命令

en_text: Hancitor has been delivered via phishing emails with malicious attachments.
Text: Hancitor是通过带有恶意附件的钓鱼邮件传播的

en_text: Hancitor has been delivered via phishing emails which contained malicious links.
Text: Hancitor是通过含有恶意链接的网络钓鱼邮件传播的

en_text: Hancitor has relied upon users clicking on a malicious link delivered through phishing.
Text: Hancitor依靠用户点击通过网络钓鱼提供的恶意链接

en_text: Hancitor has used a macro to check that an ActiveDocument shape object in the lure message is present. If this object is not found, the macro will exit without downloading additional payloads.
Text: Hancitor用一个宏来检查诱饵信息中的ActiveDocument形状对象是否存在

en_text: Hancitor has the ability to download additional files from C2.
Text: Hancitor有能力从C2下载其他文件

en_text: Hancitor  has added Registry Run keys to establish persistence.
Text: Hancitor增加了注册表运行键来建立持久性

en_text: HARDRAIN opens the Windows Firewall to modify incoming connections.
Text: HARDRAIN打开Windows防火墙以修改进入的连接

en_text: HARDRAIN uses cmd.exe to execute netshcommands.
Text: HARDRAIN使用cmd.exe来执行netsh命令

en_text: HARDRAIN uses FakeTLS to communicate with its C2 server.
Text: HARDRAIN使用FakeTLS来与它的C2服务器进行通信

en_text: HARDRAIN uses the command cmd.exe /c netsh firewall add portopening TCP 443 "adp" and makes the victim machine function as a proxy server.
Text: HARDRAIN使用命令cmd.exe HARDRAIN使用命令cmd.exe

en_text: HARDRAIN binds and listens on port 443 with a FakeTLS method.
Text: HARDRAIN通过FakeTLS方法在443端口进行绑定和监听

en_text: Havij is used to automate SQL injection.
Text: Havij是用来自动进行SQL注入的

en_text: HAWKBALL has created a cmd.exe reverse shell, executed commands, and uploaded output via the command line.
Text: HAWKBALL创建了一个cmd.exe反向外壳，执行命令，并通过命令行上传输出

en_text: HAWKBALL can collect the OS version, architecture information, and computer name.
Text: HAWKBALL可以收集操作系统版本、架构信息和计算机名称

en_text: HAWKBALL can collect the user name of the system.
Text: HAWKBALL可以收集系统的用户名

en_text: HAWKBALL has leveraged several Windows API calls to create processes, gather disk information, and detect debugger activity.
Text: HAWKBALL利用了几个Windows API调用来创建进程，收集磁盘信息，并检测调试器活动

en_text: HAWKBALL has exploited Microsoft Office vulnerabilities CVE-2017-11882 and CVE-2018-0802 to deliver the payload.
Text: HAWKBALL利用了微软Office漏洞CVE-2017-11882和CVE-2018-0802来传递有效载荷

en_text: HAWKBALL has used an OLE object that uses Equation Editor to drop the embedded shellcode.
Text: HAWKBALL使用了一个OLE对象，该对象使用Equation Editor来投放嵌入的shellcode

en_text: HAWKBALL has used HTTP to communicate with a single hard-coded C2 server.
Text: HAWKBALL已经使用HTTP与单一的硬编码C2服务器进行通信

en_text: HAWKBALL has sent system information and files over the C2 channel.
Text: HAWKBALL已经通过C2通道发送了系统信息和文件

en_text: HAWKBALL has encrypted the payload with an XOR-based algorithm.
Text: HAWKBALL用一种基于XOR的算法对有效载荷进行了加密

en_text: HAWKBALL has the ability to delete files.
Text: HAWKBALL有删除文件的能力

en_text: HAWKBALL has encrypted data with XOR before sending it over the C2 channel.
Text: HAWKBALL在通过C2通道发送数据之前，已经用XOR进行了加密

en_text: hcdLoader installs itself as a service for persistence.
Text: hcdLoader将自己安装成一个用于持久化的服务

en_text: hcdLoader provides command-line access to the compromised system.
Text: hcdLoader提供对被破坏系统的命令行访问

en_text: HDoor scans to identify open ports on the victim.
Text: HDoor扫描以识别受害者的开放端口

en_text: HDoor kills anti-virus found on the victim.
Text: HDoor杀死了在受害者身上发现的反病毒

en_text: A Helminth VBScript receives a batch script to execute a set of commands in a command prompt.
Text: Helminth VBScript接收一个批处理脚本，在命令提示符下执行一组命令

en_text: The executable version of Helminth has a module to log clipboard contents.
Text: Helminth的可执行版本有一个模块可以记录剪贴板内容

en_text: The executable version of Helminth has a module to log keystrokes.
Text: Helminth的可执行版本有一个模块来记录击键

en_text: The Helminth config file is encrypted with RC4.
Text: Helminth的配置文件是用RC4加密的

en_text: One version of Helminth uses a PowerShell script.
Text: Helminth的一个版本使用PowerShell脚本

en_text: One version of Helminth consists of VBScript scripts.
Text: Helminth的一个版本由VBScript脚本组成

en_text: Helminth splits data into chunks up to 23 bytes and sends the data in DNS queries to its C2 server.
Text: Helminth将数据分割成最多23个字节的小块，并将数据以DNS查询的方式发送到其C2服务器

en_text: Helminth can use DNS for C2.
Text: Helminth可以使用DNS进行C2

en_text: Helminth can use HTTP for C2.
Text: Helminth可以使用HTTP进行C2

en_text: Helminth can provide a remote shell. One version of Helminth uses batch scripting.
Text: Helminth可以提供一个远程外壳

en_text: Helminth can download additional files.
Text: Helminth可以下载额外的文件

en_text: Helminth has used a scheduled task for persistence.
Text: Helminth使用了一个预定任务来实现持久性

en_text: Helminth has checked for the domain admin group and Exchange Trusted Subsystem groups using the commands net group Exchange Trusted Subsystem /domain and net group domain admins /domain.
Text: Helminth使用命令net group Exchange Trusted Subsystem检查了域管理组和Exchange Trusted Subsystem组

en_text: Helminth establishes persistence by creating a shortcut in the Start Menu folder.
Text: Helminth通过在开始菜单文件夹中创建一个快捷方式来建立持久性

en_text: Helminth samples have been signed with legitimate, compromised code signing certificates owned by software company AI Squared.
Text: Helminth样本已经用软件公司AI Squared拥有的合法的、被破坏的代码签名证书进行了签名

en_text: Helminth has checked the local administrators group.
Text: Helminth已经检查了本地管理员组

en_text: Helminth has used Tasklist to get information on processes.
Text: Helminth已经使用Tasklist来获取进程信息

en_text: Helminth encrypts data sent to its C2 server over HTTP with RC4.
Text: Helminth用RC4对通过HTTP发送到其C2服务器的数据进行加密

en_text: Helminth creates folders to store output from batch scripts prior to sending the information to its C2 server.
Text: Helminth在将信息发送到其C2服务器之前，会创建文件夹来存储批处理脚本的输出

en_text: HiddenWasp creates a user account as a means to provide initial persistence to the compromised machine.
Text: HiddenWasp创建了一个用户账户，作为向被攻击机器提供初始持久性的手段

en_text: HiddenWasp downloads a tar compressed archive from a download server to the system.
Text: HiddenWasp从下载服务器上下载一个tar压缩档案到系统

en_text: HiddenWasp encrypts its configuration and payload.
Text: HiddenWasp对其配置和有效载荷进行加密

en_text: HiddenWasp adds itself as a shared object to the LD_PRELOAD environment variable.
Text: HiddenWasp将自己作为一个共享对象添加到LD_PRELOAD环境变量中

en_text: HiddenWasp uses a script to automate tasks on the victim's machine and to assist in execution.
Text: HiddenWasp使用脚本在受害者的机器上自动执行任务并协助执行

en_text: HiddenWasp uses an RC4-like algorithm with an already computed PRGA generated key-stream for network communication.
Text: HiddenWasp使用类似于RC4的算法，用已经计算好的PRGA生成的密钥流进行网络通信

en_text: HiddenWasp uses a rootkit to hook and implement functions on the system.
Text: HiddenWasp使用一个rootkit在系统上钩住并实现功能

en_text: HiddenWasp uses a cipher to implement a decoding function.
Text: HiddenWasp使用一个密码来实现一个解码功能

en_text: HiddenWasp communicates with a simple network protocol over TCP.
Text: HiddenWasp通过TCP的简单网络协议进行通信。

en_text: HiddenWasp installs reboot persistence by adding itself to /etc/rc.local.
Text: HiddenWasp通过将自己添加到 HiddenWasp通过将自己加入到 HiddenWasp通过添加自己到 HiddenWasp通过把自己添加到

en_text: HIDEDRV injects a DLL for Downdelph into the explorer.exe process.
Text: HIDEDRV将一个Downdelph的DLL注入explorer.exe进程中

en_text: HIDEDRV is a rootkit that hides certain operating system artifacts.
Text: HIDEDRV是一个隐藏某些操作系统工件的rootkit

en_text: Hikit uses certmgr.exe -add GlobalSign.cer -c -s -r localMachine Root and certmgr.exe -add GlobalSign.cer -c -s -r localMachineTrustedPublisher to install a self-generated certificate to the local trust store as a root CA and Trusted Publisher.
Text: Hikit使用certmgr.exe -add GlobalSign.cer -c -s -r localMachine Root和certmgr.exe -add GlobalSign.cer -c -s -r localMachineTrustedPublisher将自己生成的证书作为根CA和受信任发布者安装到本地信任商店

en_text: Hikit has used DLL Search Order Hijacking to load oci.dll as a persistence mechanism.
Text: Hikit使用了DLL搜索顺序劫持来加载oci.dll作为一种持久性机制。

en_text: Hikit is a Rootkit that has been used by Axiom.
Text: Hikit是一个Rootkit，已被Axiom使用

en_text: Hikit has used HTTP for C2.
Text: Hikit已将HTTP用于C2

en_text: Hikit has the ability to create a remote shell and run given commands.
Text: Hikit有能力创建一个远程shell并运行给定的命令

en_text: Hikit supports peer connections.
Text: Hikit支持同行连接

en_text: Hikit performs XOR encryption.
Text: Hikit执行XOR加密

en_text: Hi-Zor creates a Registry Run key to establish persistence.
Text: Hi-Zor创建一个注册表运行键来建立持久性。

en_text: Hi-Zor executes using regsvr32.exe called from the Registry Run Keys / Startup Folder persistence mechanism.
Text: Hi-Zor使用从注册表运行键调用的regsvr32.exe执行

en_text: Hi-Zor uses various XOR techniques to obfuscate its components.
Text: Hi-Zor使用各种XOR技术来混淆其组件

en_text: Hi-Zor encrypts C2 traffic with a double XOR using two distinct single-byte keys.
Text: Hi-Zor使用两个不同的单字节密钥对C2流量进行双XOR加密

en_text: Hi-Zor communicates with its C2 server over HTTPS.
Text: Hi-Zor通过HTTPS与它的C2服务器进行通信

en_text: Hi-Zor encrypts C2 traffic with TLS.
Text: Hi-Zor用TLS对C2流量进行加密

en_text: Hi-Zor has the ability to upload and download files from its C2 server.
Text: Hi-Zor有能力从其C2服务器上传和下载文件

en_text: Hi-Zor deletes its RAT installer file as it executes its DLL payload file.
Text: Hi-Zor在执行其DLL有效载荷文件时，会删除其RAT安装程序文件

en_text: EvilBunny has created Registry keys for persistence in [HKLM|HKCU]\…\CurrentVersion\Run.
Text: HKCU]\…\CurrentVersion\Run.

en_text: HOMEFRY can perform credential dumping.
Text: HOMEFRY可以进行凭证转储

en_text: HOMEFRY uses a command-line interface.
Text: HOMEFRY使用一个命令行界面

en_text: Some strings in HOMEFRY are obfuscated with XOR x56.
Text: HOMEFRY中的一些字符串是用XOR x56来混淆的

en_text: Honeybee collects data from the local victim system.
Text: Honeybee从本地受害者系统收集数据

en_text: Honeybee's service-based DLL implant can execute a downloaded file with parameters specified using CreateProcessAsUser.
Text: Honeybee的基于服务的DLL植入可以执行一个下载的文件，并使用CreateProcessAsUser指定参数

en_text: Honeybee's service-based DLL implant traverses the FTP server’s directories looking for files with keyword matches for computer names or certain keywords.
Text: Honeybee的基于服务的DLL植入物遍历FTP服务器的目录，寻找与计算机名称或某些关键词相匹配的文件

en_text: Several commands are supported by the Honeybee's implant via the command-line interface and there’s also a utility to execute any custom command on an infected endpoint. Honeybee used batch scripting.
Text: Honeybee的植入物通过命令行界面支持几个命令，还有一个工具可以在受感染的终端上执行任何自定义命令。Honeybee使用了批处理脚本。

en_text: Honeybee drops files with base64-encoded data.
Text: Honeybee掉落的文件有base64编码的数据

en_text: Honeybee adds collected files to a temp.zip file saved in the %temp% folder, then base64 encodes it and uploads it to control server.
Text: Honeybee将收集的文件添加到保存在%temp%文件夹中的temp.zip文件中，然后对其进行base64编码并上传到控制服务器

en_text: Honeybee launches a DLL file that gets executed as a service using svchost.exe
Text: Honeybee启动了一个DLL文件，该文件被作为一个服务使用svchost.exe执行

en_text: Honeybee removes batch files to reduce fingerprint on the system as well as deletes the CAB file that gets encoded upon infection.
Text: Honeybee删除批处理文件以减少系统上的指纹，以及删除感染后被编码的CAB文件

en_text: Honeybee uses FTP for command and control.
Text: Honeybee使用FTP进行指挥和控制

en_text: Honeybee uses a combination of NTWDBLIB.dll and cliconfg.exe to bypass UAC protections using DLL hijacking.
Text: Honeybee使用NTWDBLIB.dll和cliconfg.exe的组合，利用DLL劫持绕过UAC保护

en_text: Honeybee gathers computer name and information using the systeminfo command.
Text: Honeybee使用systeminfo命令收集计算机名称和信息

en_text: Honeybee gathers a list of processes using the tasklist command and then is sent back to the control server.
Text: Honeybee使用tasklist命令收集了一个进程列表，然后被送回控制服务器

en_text: Honeybee uses a dropper called MaoCheng that harvests a stolen digital signature from Adobe Systems.
Text: Honeybee使用了一个名为MaoCheng的投放器，该投放器从Adobe Systems收获了一个被盗的数字签名

en_text: Honeybee uses a batch file that configures the ComSysApp service to autostart in order to establish persistence.
Text: Honeybee使用一个批处理文件，将ComSysApp服务配置为自动启动，以便建立持久性

en_text: Honeybee uses a batch file to load a DLL into the svchost.exe process.
Text: Honeybee使用一个批处理文件将一个DLL加载到svchost.exe进程

en_text: Honeybee uses a batch file that modifies Registry keys to launch a DLL into the svchost.exe process.
Text: Honeybee使用一个修改注册表键的批处理文件来启动一个DLL到svchost.exe进程

en_text: Honeybee drops a Word file containing a Base64-encoded file in it that is read, decoded, and dropped to the disk by the macro.

en_text: Honeybee has batch files that modify the system service COMSysApp to load a malicious DLL.

en_text: Honeybee embeds a Visual Basic script within a malicious Word document as part of initial access; the script is executed when the Word document is opened.

en_text: Honeybee performs data exfiltration is accomplished through the following command-line command: from  (- --).txt.
Text: Honeybee执行的数据渗透是通过以下命令行命令完成的：from (- -).txt

en_text: A variant of HOPLIGHT hooks lsass.exe, and lsass.exe then checks the Registry for the data value 'rdpproto' under the key SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Lsa Name.
Text: HOPLIGHT的一个变种钩住lsass.exe，然后lsass.exe在SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Lsa Name键下检查注册表的数据值'rdpproto'

en_text: HOPLIGHT has the ability to connect to a remote host in order to upload and download files.

en_text: HOPLIGHT can launch cmd.exe to execute commands on the system.
Text: HOPLIGHT可以启动cmd.exe，在系统上执行命令

en_text: HOPLIGHT has used svchost.exe to execute a malicious DLL .
Text: HOPLIGHT利用svchost.exe来执行一个恶意的DLL . HOPLIGHT使用svchost.exe来执行一个恶意的DLL . HOPLIGHT利用svchost.exe来执行一个恶意的DLL

en_text: HOPLIGHT has utilized Zlib compression to obfuscate the communications payload.
Text: HOPLIGHT利用Zlib压缩技术来混淆通信有效载荷

en_text: HOPLIGHT has used its C2 channel to exfiltrate data.
Text: HOPLIGHT利用其C2渠道来渗出数据

en_text: HOPLIGHT has modified the firewall using netsh.
Text: HOPLIGHT使用netsh修改了防火墙

en_text: HOPLIGHT has used WMI to recompile the Managed Object Format (MOF) files in the WMI repository.
Text: HOPLIGHT使用WMI重新编译了WMI资源库中的管理对象格式（MOF）文件

en_text: HOPLIGHT has connected outbound over TCP port 443 with a FakeTLS method.
Text: HOPLIGHT通过TCP 443端口向外连接，采用FakeTLS方式

en_text: HOPLIGHT has modified Managed Object Format (MOF) files within the Registry to run specific commands and create persistence on the system.
Text: HOPLIGHT修改了注册表内的管理对象格式（MOF）文件，以运行特定的命令并在系统上创建持久性

en_text: HOPLIGHT has been observed collecting system time from victim machines.
Text: HOPLIGHT已经被观察到从受害者机器上收集系统时间

en_text: HOPLIGHT has injected into running processes.
Text: HOPLIGHT已经注入到运行的进程中

en_text: HOPLIGHT has multiple C2 channels in place in case one fails.
Text: HOPLIGHT有多个C2渠道，以备一个渠道失效时使用

en_text: HOPLIGHT has multiple proxy options that mask traffic between the malware and the remote operators.
Text: HOPLIGHT有多个代理选项，可以掩盖恶意软件和远程操作员之间的通信

en_text: HOPLIGHT has the capability to harvest credentials and passwords from the SAM database.
Text: HOPLIGHT有能力从SAM数据库中获取凭证和密码

en_text: HotCroissant has compressed network communications and encrypted them with a custom stream cipher.
Text: HotCroissant对网络通信进行了压缩，并用一个定制的流密码对其进行加密

en_text: HotCroissant can retrieve a list of applications from the SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\App Paths registry key.
Text: HotCroissant可以从SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\App Paths注册表键中检索到一个应用程序列表

en_text: HotCroissant can perform dynamic DLL importing and API lookups using LoadLibrary and GetProcAddress on obfuscated strings.
Text: HotCroissant可以使用LoadLibrary和GetProcAddress对混淆的字符串进行动态DLL导入和API查询

en_text: HotCroissant can remotely open applications on the infected host with the ShellExecuteA command.
Text: HotCroissant可以通过ShellExecuteA命令远程打开被感染主机上的应用程序

en_text: HotCroissant has used the open source UPX executable packer.
Text: HotCroissant使用了开源的UPX可执行文件打包器

en_text: HotCroissant has attempted to install a scheduled task named "Java Maintenance64" on startup to establish persistence.
Text: HotCroissant试图在启动时安装一个名为 "Java Maintenance64 "的计划任务以建立持久性

en_text: HotCroissant has encrypted strings with single-byte XOR and base64 encoded RC4.
Text: HotCroissant用单字节的XOR和base64编码的RC4对字符串进行了加密

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to upload a file from the command and control (C2) server to the victim machine.
Text: HotCroissant有能力从命令和控制（C2）服务器向受害者机器上传文件

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to download files from the infected host to the command and control (C2) server.
Text: HotCroissant有能力从受感染的主机下载文件到指挥和控制（C2）服务器

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to do real time screen viewing on an infected host.
Text: HotCroissant有能力对受感染的主机进行实时屏幕查看

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to retrieve a list of services on the infected host.
Text: HotCroissant有能力检索受感染主机上的服务列表

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to retrieve a list of files in a given directory as well as drives and drive types.
Text: HotCroissant有能力检索一个给定目录中的文件列表以及驱动器和驱动器类型

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to list running processes on the infected host.
Text: HotCroissant有能力列出受感染主机上的运行进程

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to list the names of all open windows on the infected host.
Text: HotCroissant有能力列出受感染主机上所有打开的窗口的名称

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to clean up installed files, delete files, and delete itself from the victim’s machine.
Text: HotCroissant有能力清理已安装的文件，删除文件，并从受害者的机器上删除自己

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to determine if the current user is an administrator, Windows product name, processor name, screen resolution, and physical RAM of the infected host.
Text: HotCroissant有能力确定当前用户是否为管理员、受感染主机的Windows产品名称、处理器名称、屏幕分辨率和物理内存

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to identify the IP address of the compromised machine.
Text: HotCroissant有能力识别被攻击机器的IP地址

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to collect the username on the infected host.
Text: HotCroissant有能力收集受感染主机上的用户名

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to stop services on the infected host.
Text: HotCroissant有能力停止受感染主机上的服务

en_text: HotCroissant has the ability to hide the window for operations performed on a given file.
Text: HotCroissant有能力隐藏对某一文件进行操作的窗口

en_text: HTRAN can install a rootkit to hide network connections from the host OS.

en_text: HTRAN can proxy TCP socket connections to obfuscate command and control infrastructure.
Text: HTRAN可以代理TCP套接字连接，以掩盖命令和控制基础设施

en_text: HTRAN can inject into into running processes.
Text: HTRAN可以注入到运行的进程中

en_text: HTTPBrowser's installer contains a malicious file named navlu.dll to decrypt and run the RAT. navlu.dll is also the name of a legitimate Symantec DLL.
Text: HTTPBrowser的安装程序包含一个名为navlu.dll的恶意文件，用于解密和运行RAT

en_text: HTTPBrowser's code may be obfuscated through structured exception handling and return-oriented programming.
Text: HTTPBrowser的代码可以通过结构化的异常处理和面向返回的编程来进行混淆

en_text: HTTPBrowser is capable of capturing keystrokes on victims.
Text: HTTPBrowser能够捕获受害者的键盘点击

en_text: HTTPBrowser is capable of writing a file to the compromised system from the C2 server.
Text: HTTPBrowser能够从C2服务器向被攻击的系统写入文件

en_text: HTTPBrowser is capable of listing files, folders, and drives on a victim.
Text: HTTPBrowser能够列出受害者的文件、文件夹和驱动器

en_text: HTTPBrowser is capable of spawning a reverse shell on a victim.
Text: HTTPBrowser能够在受害者身上生成一个反向外壳

en_text: HTTPBrowser has established persistence by setting the HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run key value for wdm to the path of the executable. It has also used the Registry entry HKEY_USERS\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run vpdn "%ALLUSERPROFILE%\%APPDATA%\vpdn\VPDN_LU.exe" to establish persistence.
Text: HTTPBrowser通过设置HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run键值为wdm的可执行文件的路径来建立持久性。它还使用注册表项HKEY_USERS\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run vpdn "%ALLUSERPROFILE%\%APPDATA%\vpdn\VPDN_LU.exe" 来建立持久性。

en_text: HTTPBrowser abuses the Windows DLL load order by using a legitimate Symantec anti-virus binary, VPDN_LU.exe, to load a malicious DLL that mimics a legitimate Symantec DLL, navlu.dll.
Text: HTTPBrowser通过使用合法的赛门铁克反病毒二进制文件VPDN_LU.exe来加载一个模仿合法的赛门铁克DLL文件navlu.dll的恶意DLL，从而滥用了Windows DLL的加载顺序

en_text: HTTPBrowser has used DNS for command and control.
Text: HTTPBrowser已经使用DNS进行指挥和控制

en_text: HTTPBrowser has used HTTP and HTTPS for command and control.
Text: HTTPBrowser已经使用HTTP和HTTPS进行指挥和控制

en_text: HTTPBrowser has used DLL side-loading.
Text: HTTPBrowser已经使用了DLL侧面加载

en_text: httpclient uses HTTP for command and control.
Text: httpclient使用HTTP进行命令和控制

en_text: httpclient encrypts C2 content with XOR using a single byte, 0x12.
Text: httpclient使用单字节0x12的XOR对C2内容进行加密

en_text: httpclient opens cmd.exe on the victim.
Text: httpclient在受害者身上打开cmd.exe

en_text: Hydraq C2 traffic is encrypted using bitwise NOT and XOR operations.
Text: Hydraq C2流量是使用位数NOT和XOR操作进行加密的

en_text: Hydraq includes a component based on the code of VNC that can stream a live feed of the desktop of an infected host.
Text: Hydraq包括一个基于VNC代码的组件，可以流式传输受感染主机桌面的实时信息

en_text: Hydraq creates new services to establish persistence.
Text: Hydraq创建了新的服务以建立持久性

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can adjust token privileges.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它调整令牌权限

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can read data from files.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它读取文件中的数据

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can load and call DLL functions.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它加载和调用DLL函数

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can monitor services.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它监控服务

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can monitor processes.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它监控进程

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can check for the existence of files, including its own components, as well as retrieve a list of logical drives.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它检查文件的存在，包括它自己的组件，以及检索逻辑驱动器的列表

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can retrieve IP addresses of compromised machines.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它检索被攻击机器的IP地址

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can clear all system event logs.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它清除所有的系统事件日志

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can delete files.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它删除文件

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can download files and additional malware components.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它下载文件和其他恶意软件组件

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can retrieve system information, such as CPU speed, from Registry keys.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过这个后门从注册表键中获取系统信息，如CPU速度。

en_text: Hydraq creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can retrieve information such as computer name, OS version, processor speed, memory size, and CPU speed.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过这个后门获取计算机名称、操作系统版本、处理器速度、内存大小和CPU速度等信息

en_text: Hydraq creates a Registry subkey to register its created service, and can also uninstall itself later by deleting this value. Hydraq's backdoor also enables remote attackers to modify and delete subkeys.
Text: Hydraq创建了一个注册表子键来注册其创建的服务，并且还可以在以后通过删除这个值来卸载自己。Hydraq的后门还使远程攻击者能够修改和删除子键。

en_text: Hydraq uses svchost.exe to execute a malicious DLL included in a new service group.
Text: Hydraq使用svchost.exe来执行一个包含在新服务组中的恶意DLL

en_text: Hydraq connects to a predefined domain on port 443 to exfil gathered information.
Text: Hydraq通过443端口连接到一个预定义的域，以渗出收集的信息

en_text: Hydraq uses basic obfuscation in the form of spaghetti code.
Text: Hydraq以意大利语代码的形式使用基本的混淆功能

Text: HyperBro利用一个合法的应用程序侧载一个DLL来解密、解压和运行一个有效载荷

Text: HyperBro有能力运行一个应用程序（CreateProcessW）或脚本

en_text: IcedID has created a scheduled task that executes every hour to establish persistence.
Text: IcedID创建了一个计划任务，每小时执行一次以建立持久性

en_text: IcedID has called ZwWriteVirtualMemory, ZwProtectVirtualMemory, ZwQueueApcThread, and NtResumeThread to inject itself into a remote process.
Text: IcedID调用了ZwWriteVirtualMemory、ZwProtectVirtualMemory、ZwQueueApcThread和NtResumeThread，将自己注入到一个远程进程

en_text: IcedID has embedded binaries within RC4 encrypted .png files.
Text: IcedID将二进制文件嵌入RC4加密的.png文件中

en_text: IcedID has the ability to identify Workgroup membership.
Text: IcedID具有识别工作组成员的能力

en_text: IcedID can query LDAP to identify additional users on the network to infect.
Text: IcedID可以查询LDAP，以确定网络上其他要感染的用户

en_text: IcedID can inject itself into a suspended msiexec.exe process to send beacons to C2 while appearing as a normal msi application.
Text: IcedID可以将自己注入一个暂停的msiexec.exe进程，向C2发送信标，同时显示为一个正常的msi应用程序

en_text: IcedID has used web injection attacks to redirect victims to spoofed sites designed to harvest banking and other credentials.  IcedID can use a self signed TLS certificate in connection with the spoofed site and simultaneously maintains a live connection with the legitimate site to display the correct URL and certificates in the browser.
Text: IcedID利用网络注入攻击，将受害者重定向到旨在获取银行和其他证书的欺骗性网站。 IcedID可以使用一个自签名的TLS证书与被欺骗的网站连接，同时与合法网站保持实时连接，在浏览器中显示正确的URL和证书。

en_text: IcedID has used ZwQueueApcThread to inject itself into remote processes.
Text: IcedID使用ZwQueueApcThread将自己注入到远程进程

en_text: IcedID has been delivered via phishing e-mails with malicious attachments.
Text: IcedID是通过带有恶意附件的钓鱼邮件传递的

en_text: IcedID has established persistence by creating a Registry run key.
Text: IcedID通过创建一个注册表运行键建立了持久性

en_text: IcedID has packed and encrypted its loader module.
Text: IcedID已经打包并加密了它的加载器模块

en_text: IcedID has utilzed encrypted binaries and base64 encoded strings.
Text: IcedID已经利用了加密的二进制文件和base64编码的字符串

en_text: IcedID has used WMI to execute binaries.
Text: IcedID已经使用WMI来执行二进制文件

en_text: IcedID has used obfuscated VBA string expressions.
Text: IcedID已经使用了混淆的VBA字符串表达式

en_text: IcedID has been executed through Word documents with malicious embedded macros.
Text: IcedID已经通过带有恶意嵌入式宏的Word文档执行

en_text: IcedID has the ability to download additional modules and a configuration file from C2.
Text: IcedID有能力从C2下载额外的模块和一个配置文件

en_text: IcedID has the ability to identify the computer name and OS version on a compromised host.
Text: IcedID有能力识别被攻击主机上的计算机名称和操作系统版本

en_text: IcedID has used HTTPS in communications with C2.
Text: IcedID在与C2的通信中使用了HTTPS

en_text: IcedID has used SSL and TLS in communications with C2.
Text: IcedID在与C2的通信中使用了SSL和TLS

Text: ifconfig可以用来显示Unix系统上的适配卡配置，包括TCP的信息

en_text: iKitten will zip up the /Library/Keychains directory before exfiltrating it.
Text: iKitten会拉上 iKitten会拉上拉链 iKitten会将拉链拉上 iKitten会把拉链拉上

en_text: iKitten will look for the current IP address.
Text: iKitten将寻找当前的IP地址

en_text: iKitten lists the current processes running.

en_text: Imminent Monitor has decoded malware components that are then dropped to the system.
Text: Imminent Monitor对恶意软件组件进行了解码，然后将其投放到系统中

en_text: Imminent Monitor has encrypted the spearphish attachments to avoid detection from email gateways; the debugger also encrypts information before sending to the C2.
Text: Imminent Monitor对鱼叉式攻击的附件进行了加密，以避免被电子邮件网关发现；调试器也在向C2发送之前对信息进行了加密

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a remote microphone monitoring capability.
Text: Imminent Monitor具有远程麦克风监控功能

en_text: Imminent Monitor has leveraged CreateProcessW() call to execute the debugger.
Text: Imminent Monitor利用CreateProcessW()调用来执行调试器

en_text: Imminent Monitor has deleted files related to its dynamic debugger feature.
Text: Imminent Monitor已经删除了与其动态调试器功能有关的文件

en_text: Imminent Monitor has uploaded a file containing debugger logs, network information and system information to the C2.
Text: Imminent Monitor已经上传了一个包含调试器日志、网络信息和系统信息的文件到C2

en_text: Imminent Monitor has the capability to run a cryptocurrency miner on the victim machine.
Text: Imminent Monitor有能力在受害者机器上运行一个加密货币矿工

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a "Process Watcher" feature to monitor processes in case the client ever crashes or gets closed.
Text: Imminent Monitor有一个 "进程观察者 "的功能，在客户端崩溃或被关闭的情况下监测进程

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a CommandPromptPacket and ScriptPacket module(s) for creating a remote shell and executing scripts.
Text: Imminent Monitor有一个CommandPromptPacket和ScriptPacket模块，用于创建远程外壳和执行脚本

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a PasswordRecoveryPacket module for recovering browser passwords.
Text: Imminent Monitor有一个PasswordRecoveryPacket模块，用于恢复浏览器密码

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a dynamic debugging feature to check whether it is located in the %TEMP% directory, otherwise it copies itself there.
Text: Imminent Monitor有一个动态调试功能，检查它是否位于%TEMP%目录下，否则它就把自己复制到那里

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a dynamic debugging feature to set the file attribute to hidden.
Text: Imminent Monitor有一个动态调试功能，可以将文件属性设置为隐藏

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a feature to disable Windows Task Manager.
Text: Imminent Monitor有一个功能可以禁用Windows任务管理器

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a keylogging module.
Text: Imminent Monitor有一个键盘记录模块

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a module for performing remote desktop access.
Text: Imminent Monitor有一个模块用于执行远程桌面访问

en_text: Imminent Monitor has a remote webcam monitoring capability.
Text: Imminent Monitor有一个远程网络摄像头监控功能
