en_text: SecretsDump and Mimikatz modules within Impacket can perform credential dumping to obtain account and password information.
Text: Impacket中的SecretsDump和Mimikatz模块可以进行凭证转储，以获取账户和密码信息

en_text: Inception has used weaponized documents attached to spearphishing emails for reconnaissance and initial compromise.
Text: Inception公司利用附在鱼叉式网络钓鱼电子邮件中的武器化文件进行侦察和初步破坏

en_text: Inception has used PowerShell to execute malicious commands and payloads.
Text: Inception利用PowerShell来执行恶意命令和有效载荷

en_text: Inception has used VBScript to execute malicious commands and payloads.
Text: Inception利用VBScript来执行恶意命令和有效载荷

en_text: Inception used chains of compromised routers to proxy C2 communications between them and cloud service providers.
Text: Inception利用被破坏的路由器链来代理它们与云服务提供商之间的C2通信

en_text: Inception has used malicious HTA files to drop and execute malware.
Text: Inception利用恶意的HTA文件来投放和执行恶意软件

en_text: Inception has used decoy documents to load malicious remote payloads via HTTP.
Text: Inception利用诱饵文件，通过HTTP加载恶意的远程有效载荷

en_text: Inception has used specific malware modules to gather domain membership.
Text: Inception使用了特定的恶意软件模块来收集域名成员

en_text: Inception has used a reconnaissance module to identify active processes and other associated loaded modules.
Text: Inception使用了一个侦察模块来识别活跃的进程和其他相关的加载模块

en_text: Inception has used a reconnaissance module to gather information about the operating system and hardware on the infected host.
Text: Inception使用了一个侦察模块来收集被感染主机上的操作系统和硬件信息

en_text: Inception used a browser plugin to steal passwords and sessions from Internet Explorer, Chrome, Opera, Firefox, Torch, and Yandex.
Text: Inception使用一个浏览器插件，从Internet Explorer、Chrome、Opera、Firefox、Torch和Yandex窃取密码和会话

en_text: Inception used a file listing plugin to collect information about file and directories both on local and remote drives.
Text: Inception使用一个文件列表插件来收集本地和远程驱动器上的文件和目录的信息

en_text: Inception used a file hunting plugin to collect .txt, .pdf, .xls or .doc files from the infected host.
Text: Inception使用一个文件猎取插件，从受感染的主机上收集.txt、.pdf、.xls或.doc文件

en_text: Inception has ensured persistence at system boot by setting the value regsvr32 %path%\ctfmonrn.dll /s.
Text: Inception通过设置regsvr32 %path%\ctfmonrn.dll的值，确保了系统启动时的持久性

en_text: Inception has maintained persistence by modifying Registry run key value  HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\.
Text: Inception通过修改注册表运行键值HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Microsoft/Windows/CurrentVersion/Run/来保持持久性

en_text: Inception has incorporated at least five different cloud service providers into their C2 infrastructure including CloudMe.
Text: Inception已经将至少五个不同的云服务提供商纳入其C2基础设施，包括CloudMe

en_text: Inception has exploited CVE-2012-0158, CVE-2014-1761, CVE-2017-11882 and CVE-2018-0802 for execution.
Inception has enumerated installed software on compromised systems.
Text: Inception已经列举了被破坏的系统上安装的软件

en_text: Inception has encrypted network communications with AES.
Text: Inception用AES对网络通信进行了加密

en_text: Inception has encrypted malware payloads dropped on victim machines with AES and RC4 encryption.
Text: Inception用AES和RC4加密法对投放在受害者机器上的恶意软件有效载荷进行了加密

en_text: Inception lured victims into clicking malicious files for machine reconnaissance and to execute malware.
Text: Inception诱使受害者点击恶意文件进行机器侦查并执行恶意软件

en_text: Inception has used HTTP, HTTPS, and WebDav in network communications.
Text: Inception在网络通信中使用了HTTP、HTTPS和WebDav

en_text: InnaputRAT variants have attempted to appear legitimate by using the file names SafeApp.exe and NeutralApp.exe.
Text: InnaputRAT变种试图通过使用文件名SafeApp.exe和NeutralApp.exe来显得合法

en_text: InnaputRAT variants have attempted to appear legitimate by adding a new service named OfficeUpdateService.
Text: InnaputRAT变种试图通过添加一个名为OfficeUpdateService的新服务而显得合法

en_text: InnaputRAT enumerates directories and obtains file attributes on a system.
Text: InnaputRAT枚举目录并获取系统中的文件属性

en_text: InnaputRAT launches a shell to execute commands on the victim’s machine.
Text: InnaputRAT启动一个外壳，在受害者的机器上执行命令

en_text: InnaputRAT uses the API call ShellExecuteW for execution.
Text: InnaputRAT使用API调用ShellExecuteW来执行

en_text: InnaputRAT uses an 8-byte XOR key to obfuscate API names and other strings contained in the payload.
Text: InnaputRAT使用一个8字节的XOR密钥来混淆API名称和有效载荷中包含的其他字符串

en_text: InnaputRAT gathers volume drive information and system information.
Text: InnaputRAT收集卷轴驱动器信息和系统信息

en_text: InnaputRAT has a command to delete files.
Text: InnaputRAT有一个删除文件的命令

en_text: InvisiMole InvisiMole can identify proxy servers used by the victim and use them for C2 communication.
Text: InvisiMole InvisiMole可以识别受害者使用的代理服务器，并利用它们进行C2通信

en_text: InvisiMole can capture screenshots of not only the entire screen, but of each separate window open, in case they are overlapping.
Text: InvisiMole不仅可以捕获整个屏幕的截图，还可以捕获打开的每个独立窗口的截图，以防它们重叠

en_text: InvisiMole gathers the local system time from the victim’s machine.
Text: InvisiMole从受害者的机器上收集本地系统时间

en_text: InvisiMole samples were timestomped by the authors by setting the PE timestamps to all zero values. InvisiMole also has a built-in command to modify file times.
Text: InvisiMole的样本被作者通过将PE的时间戳设置为所有的零值来进行时间控制

en_text: InvisiMole has disguised its droppers as legitimate software or documents, matching their original names and locations, and saved its files as mpr.dll in the Windows folder.
Text: InvisiMole将其投放器伪装成合法软件或文件，与它们的原始名称和位置相匹配，并将其文件保存为Windows文件夹中的mpr.dll

en_text: InvisiMole has undergone regular technical improvements in an attempt to evade detection.
Text: InvisiMole经历了定期的技术改进，以试图逃避检测

en_text: InvisiMole can capture keystrokes on a compromised host.
Text: InvisiMole可以捕获被攻击主机上的按键

en_text: InvisiMole can create hidden system directories.
Text: InvisiMole可以创建隐藏的系统目录

en_text: InvisiMole can decrypt, unpack and load a DLL from its resources, or from blobs encrypted with Data Protection API, two-key triple DES, and variations of the XOR cipher.
Text: InvisiMole可以从DLL的资源中解密、解包和加载DLL，或者从用数据保护API、双键三重DES和XOR密码的变体加密的Blobs中解密

en_text: InvisiMole can collect jpeg files from connected MTP devices.
Text: InvisiMole可以从连接的MTP设备收集jpeg文件

en_text: InvisiMole can collect data from the system, and can monitor changes in specified directories.
Text: InvisiMole可以从系统中收集数据，并可以监测指定目录的变化

en_text: InvisiMole can disconnect previously connected remote drives.
Text: InvisiMole可以断开以前连接的远程驱动器的连接

en_text: InvisiMole can spread within a network via the BlueKeep (CVE-2019-0708) and EternalBlue (CVE-2017-0144) vulnerabilities in RDP and SMB respectively.
Text: InvisiMole可以分别通过RDP和SMB中的BlueKeep（CVE-2019-0708）和EternalBlue（CVE-2017-0144）漏洞在网络中传播

en_text: InvisiMole can sort and collect specific documents as well as generate a list of all files on a newly inserted drive and store them in an encrypted file.
Text: InvisiMole可以分类和收集特定的文件，以及生成新插入的驱动器上的所有文件的列表，并将它们存储在一个加密的文件中

en_text: InvisiMole can obtain running services on the victim.
Text: InvisiMole可以获得受害者上的运行服务

en_text: InvisiMole can obtain a list of running processes.
Text: InvisiMole可以获得一个正在运行的进程列表

en_text: InvisiMole can check for artifacts of VirtualBox, Virtual PC and VMware environment, and terminate itself if they are detected.
Text: InvisiMole可以检查VirtualBox、Virtual PC和VMware环境的人工制品，如果检测到它们，就终止自己

en_text: InvisiMole can check for the presence of network sniffers, AV, and BitDefender firewall.
Text: InvisiMole可以检查是否存在网络嗅探器、AV和BitDefender防火墙

en_text: InvisiMole can inject its backdoor as a portable executable into a target process.
Text: InvisiMole可以将其后门作为一个可移植的可执行文件注入目标进程中

en_text: InvisiMole can upload files to the victim's machine for operations.
Text: InvisiMole可以将文件上传到受害者的机器上进行操作

en_text: InvisiMole can inject itself into another process to avoid detection including use of a technique called ListPlanting that customizes the sorting algorithm in a ListView structure.
Text: InvisiMole可以将自己注入另一个进程，以避免被发现，包括使用一种叫做ListPlanting的技术，在ListView结构中定制排序算法

en_text: InvisiMole can can remove all system restore points.
Text: InvisiMole可以可以删除所有的系统还原点

en_text: InvisiMole can list information about files in a directory and recently opened or used documents. InvisiMole can also search for specific files by supplied file mask.
Text: InvisiMole可以列出一个目录中的文件和最近打开或使用的文件的信息

en_text: InvisiMole can enumerate windows and child windows on a compromised host.
Text: InvisiMole可以列举被攻击主机上的窗口和子窗口

en_text: InvisiMole can enumerate Registry values, keys, and data.
Text: InvisiMole可以列举注册表的值、键和数据

en_text: InvisiMole can launch a remote shell to execute commands.
Text: InvisiMole可以启动一个远程外壳来执行命令

en_text: InvisiMole can scan the network for open ports and vulnerable instances of RDP and SMB protocols.
Text: InvisiMole可以扫描网络中开放的端口以及RDP和SMB协议的脆弱实例

en_text: InvisiMole can use the ITaskService, ITaskDefinition and ITaskSettings COM interfaces to schedule a task.
Text: InvisiMole可以使用ITaskService、ITaskDefinition和ITaskSettings COM接口来安排一个任务

en_text: InvisiMole can use winapiexec tool for indirect execution of  ShellExecuteW and CreateProcessA.
Text: InvisiMole可以使用winapiexec工具来间接执行ShellExecuteW和CreateProcessA

en_text: InvisiMole can use zlib to compress and decompress data.
Text: InvisiMole可以使用zlib来压缩和解压数据

en_text: InvisiMole can use a .lnk shortcut for the Control Panel to establish persistence.
Text: InvisiMole可以使用控制面板的.lnk快捷方式来建立持久性

en_text: InvisiMole can record sound using input audio devices.
Text: InvisiMole可以使用输入音频设备录制声音。

en_text: InvisiMole can use Data Protection API to encrypt its components on the victim’s computer, to evade detection, and to make sure the payload can only be decrypted and loaded on one specific compromised computer.
Text: InvisiMole可以使用数据保护API对受害者计算机上的组件进行加密，以逃避检测，并确保有效载荷只能在一台特定的被攻击计算机上解密和加载

en_text: InvisiMole can use fileless UAC bypass and create an elevated COM object to escalate privileges.
Text: InvisiMole可以使用无文件的UAC绕过，并创建一个升高的COM对象来提升权限

en_text: InvisiMole can use a modified base32 encoding to encode data within the subdomain of C2 requests.
Text: InvisiMole可以使用修改过的base32编码对C2请求的子域内的数据进行编码

en_text: InvisiMole can use a JavaScript file as part of its execution chain.
Text: InvisiMole可以使用一个JavaScript文件作为其执行链的一部分

en_text: InvisiMole can collect information about installed software used by specific users, software executed on user login, and software executed by each system.
Text: InvisiMole可以收集关于特定用户使用的已安装软件、用户登录时执行的软件以及每个系统执行的软件的信息

en_text: InvisiMole can gather information on the mapped drives, OS version, computer name, DEP policy, memory size, and system volume serial number.
Text: InvisiMole可以收集关于映射驱动器、操作系统版本、计算机名称、DEP策略、内存大小和系统卷序号的信息

en_text: InvisiMole can gather network share information.
Text: InvisiMole可以收集网络共享信息

en_text: InvisiMole can inject its code into a trusted process via the APC queue.
Text: InvisiMole可以通过APC队列将其代码注入一个受信任的进程

en_text: InvisiMole can register itself for execution and persistence via the Control Panel.
Text: InvisiMole可以通过控制面板注册自己的执行和持久性

en_text: InvisiMole can be launched by using DLL search order hijacking in which the wrapper DLL is placed in the same folder as explorer.exe and loaded during startup into the Windows Explorer process instead of the legitimate library.
Text: InvisiMole可以通过使用DLL搜索顺序劫持来启动，其中包装DLL被放置在与explorer.exe相同的文件夹中，并在启动期间加载到Windows Explorer进程中，而不是合法库

en_text: InvisiMole can deliver trojanized versions of software and documents, relying on user execution.
Text: InvisiMole可以依靠用户的执行，提供木马化的软件和文件版本

en_text: InvisiMole can replace legitimate software or documents in the compromised network with their trojanized versions, in an attempt to propagate itself within the network.
Text: InvisiMole可以用木马版本替换被攻击网络中的合法软件或文件，试图在网络中传播自己

en_text: InvisiMole can mimic HTTP protocol with custom HTTP "verbs" HIDE, ZVVP, and NOP.
Text: InvisiMole可以用自定义的HTTP "动词 "HIDE、ZVVP和NOP来模仿HTTP协议

en_text: InvisiMole can remotely activate the victim’s webcam to capture content.
Text: InvisiMole可以远程激活受害者的网络摄像头来捕捉内容

en_text: InvisiMole can place a lnk file in the Startup Folder to achieve persistence.
Text: InvisiMole可以在启动文件夹中放置一个lnk文件来实现持久性

en_text: InvisiMole can register a Windows service named CsPower as part of its execution chain, and a Windows service named clr_optimization_v2.0.51527_X86 to achieve persistence.
Text: InvisiMole可以注册一个名为CsPower的Windows服务作为其执行链的一部分，以及一个名为clr_optimization_v2.0.51527_X86的Windows服务来实现持久性

en_text: InvisiMole can function as a proxy to create a server that relays communication between the client and C&C server, or between two clients.
Text: InvisiMole可以作为一个代理，创建一个服务器，转发客户端和C语言之间的通信

en_text: InvisiMole has exploited CVE-2007-5633 vulnerability in the speedfan.sys driver to obtain kernel mode privileges.
Text: InvisiMole利用speedfan.sys驱动中的CVE-2007-5633漏洞，获得内核模式权限

en_text: InvisiMole has used Windows services as a way to execute its malicious payload.
Text: InvisiMole利用Windows服务作为执行其恶意有效载荷的方式

en_text: InvisiMole lists local users and session information.
Text: InvisiMole列出了本地用户和会话信息

en_text: InvisiMole determines a working directory where it stores all the gathered data about the compromised machine.
Text: InvisiMole确定一个工作目录，在那里存储所有收集到的关于被攻击机器的数据

en_text: InvisiMole uses variations of a simple XOR encryption routine for C&C communications.
Text: InvisiMole使用C语言的简单XOR加密程序的变化

en_text: InvisiMole uses HTTP for C2 communications.
Text: InvisiMole使用HTTP进行C2通信

en_text: InvisiMole has used rundll32.exe for execution.
Text: InvisiMole使用rundll32.exe来执行

en_text: InvisiMole has used TCP to download additional modules.
Text: InvisiMole使用TCP下载了额外的模块

en_text: InvisiMole uses WinRAR to compress data that is intended to be exfiltrated.
Text: InvisiMole使用WinRAR来压缩打算外流的数据

en_text: InvisiMole uses a variation of the XOR cipher to encrypt files before exfiltration.
Text: InvisiMole使用XOR密码的一个变种，在渗出前对文件进行加密

en_text: InvisiMole has used a custom implementation of DNS tunneling to embed C2 communications in DNS requests and replies.
Text: InvisiMole使用了DNS隧道的定制实现，将C2通信嵌入DNS请求和回复中

en_text: InvisiMole has used scheduled tasks named MSST and \Microsoft\Windows\Autochk\Scheduled to establish persistence.
Text: InvisiMole使用了名为MSST和\Microsoft\Windows\Autochk\Scheduled的计划任务来建立持久性

en_text: InvisiMole has attempted to disguise itself by registering under a seemingly legitimate service name.
Text: InvisiMole试图通过用一个看似合法的服务名称注册来伪装自己

en_text: InvisiMole gathers information on the IP forwarding table, MAC address, configured proxy, and network SSID.
Text: InvisiMole收集关于IP转发表、MAC地址、配置的代理和网络SSID的信息

en_text: InvisiMole avoids analysis by encrypting all strings, internal files, configuration data and by using a custom executable format.
Text: InvisiMole通过加密所有字符串、内部文件、配置数据和使用自定义的可执行格式，避免了分析

en_text: InvisiMole has been configured with several servers available for alternate C2 communications.
Text: InvisiMole已经配置了几个服务器，可用于备用的C2通信

en_text: InvisiMole has deleted files and directories including XML and files successfully uploaded to C2 servers.
Text: InvisiMole已经删除了文件和目录，包括XML和成功上传到C2服务器的文件

en_text: InvisiMole has a command to create, set, copy, or delete a specified Registry key or value.
Text: InvisiMole有一个命令，可以创建、设置、复制或删除指定的注册表键或值

en_text: InvisiMole has a command to disable routing and the Firewall on the victim’s machine.
Text: InvisiMole有一个命令可以禁用受害者机器上的路由和防火墙

en_text: InvisiMole has a command to list account information on the victim’s machine.
Text: InvisiMole有一个命令可以列出受害者机器上的账户信息

en_text: InvisiMole has installed legitimate but vulnerable Total Video Player software and wdigest.dll library drivers on compromised hosts to exploit stack overflow and input validation vulnerabilities for code execution.
Text: InvisiMole在被攻击的主机上安装了合法但有漏洞的Total Video Player软件和wdigest.dll库驱动程序，利用堆栈溢出和输入验证漏洞进行代码执行

en_text: InvisiMole has executed legitimate tools in hidden windows.
Text: InvisiMole在隐藏窗口中执行合法工具

en_text: Invoke-PSImage can be used to embed a PowerShell script within the pixels of a PNG file.
Text: Invoke-PSImage可以用来将PowerShell脚本嵌入PNG文件的像素中

en_text: ipconfig can be used to display adapter configuration on Windows systems, including information for TCP/IP, DNS, and DHCP.
Text: ipconfig可以用来在Windows系统上显示适配器的配置，包括TCP的信息

en_text: ISMInjector creates scheduled tasks to establish persistence.
Text: ISMInjector创建计划任务以建立持久性

en_text: ISMInjector hollows out a newly created process RegASM.exe and injects its payload into the hollowed process.
Text: ISMInjector将一个新创建的进程RegASM.exe挖空，并将其有效载荷注入被挖空的进程中

en_text: ISMInjector uses the certutil command to decode a payload file.
Text: ISMInjector使用certutil命令来解码一个有效载荷文件

en_text: ISMInjector is obfuscated with the off-the-shelf SmartAssembly .NET obfuscator created by red-gate.com.
Text: ISMInjector是用red-gate.com创建的现成的SmartAssembly.NET混淆器来混淆的

en_text: Ixeshe collects the username from the victim’s machine.
Text: Ixeshe从受害者的机器上收集用户名

en_text: Ixeshe sets its own executable file's attributes to hidden.
Text: Ixeshe将自己的可执行文件的属性设置为隐藏

en_text: Ixeshe can collect data from a local system.
Text: Ixeshe可以从本地系统收集数据

en_text: Ixeshe can list file and directory information.
Text: Ixeshe可以列出文件和目录信息

en_text: Ixeshe can list running services.
Text: Ixeshe可以列出正在运行的服务

en_text: Ixeshe can list running processes.
Text: Ixeshe可以列出正在运行的进程

en_text: Ixeshe can achieve persistence by adding itself to the HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run Registry key.
Text: Ixeshe可以通过将自己添加到HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run注册表键中来实现持久性

en_text: Ixeshe can download and execute additional files.
Text: Ixeshe可以下载和执行其他文件

en_text: Ixeshe enumerates the IP address, network proxy settings, and domain name from a victim's system.
Text: Ixeshe列举了受害者系统中的IP地址、网络代理设置和域名

en_text: Ixeshe is capable of executing commands via cmd.
Text: Ixeshe能够通过cmd执行命令

en_text: Ixeshe uses HTTP for command and control.
Text: Ixeshe使用HTTP进行指挥和控制

en_text: Ixeshe has used registry values and file names associated with Adobe software, such as AcroRd32.exe.
Text: Ixeshe使用了与Adobe软件相关的注册表值和文件名，如AcroRd32.exe

en_text: Ixeshe uses custom Base64 encoding schemes to obfuscate command and control traffic in the message body of HTTP requests.
Text: Ixeshe使用自定义的Base64编码方案来混淆HTTP请求的消息体中的命令和控制流量

en_text: Ixeshe has a command to delete a file from the machine.
Text: Ixeshe有一个命令可以从机器上删除一个文件

en_text: Ixeshe collects the computer name of the victim's system during the initial infection.
Text: Ixeshe在最初感染时收集了受害者系统的计算机名称

en_text: Janicab captured audio and sent it out to a C2 server.
Text: Janicab捕获音频并将其发送到C2服务器

en_text: Janicab captured screenshots and sent them out to a C2 server.
Text: Janicab捕捉到屏幕截图并将其发送到C2服务器

en_text: Janicab used a valid AppleDeveloperID to sign the code to get past security restrictions.
Text: Janicab使用一个有效的AppleDeveloperID来签署代码，以突破安全限制

en_text: Janicab used a cron job for persistence on Mac devices.
Text: Janicab在Mac设备上使用一个cron job来实现持久性

en_text: JCry has encrypted files and demanded Bitcoin to decrypt those files.
Text: JCry对文件进行了加密，并要求用比特币来解密这些文件

en_text: JCry has used cmd.exe to launch PowerShell.
Text: JCry使用cmd.exe来启动PowerShell

en_text: JCry has achieved execution by luring users to click on a file that appeared to be an Adobe Flash Player update installer.
Text: JCry通过引诱用户点击一个似乎是Adobe Flash Player更新安装程序的文件来实现执行

en_text: JCry has used PowerShell to execute payloads.
Text: JCry已经使用PowerShell来执行有效载荷

en_text: JCry has used VBS scripts.
Text: JCry已经使用了VBS脚本

en_text: JCry has created payloads in the Startup directory to maintain persistence.
Text: JCry已经在启动目录中创建了有效载荷，以保持持久性

en_text: JHUHUGIT variants have communicated with C2 servers over HTTP and HTTPS.
Text: JHUHUGIT变体通过HTTP和HTTPS与C2服务器进行了通信

en_text: JHUHUGIT tests if it can reach its C2 server by first attempting a direct connection, and if it fails, obtaining proxy settings and sending the connection through a proxy, and finally injecting code into a running browser if the proxy method fails.
Text: JHUHUGIT测试它是否能到达其C2服务器，首先尝试直接连接，如果失败，则获取代理设置并通过代理发送连接，如果代理方法失败，最后将代码注入运行中的浏览器

en_text: JHUHUGIT obtains a build identifier as well as victim hard drive information from Windows registry key HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\Disk\Enum. Another JHUHUGIT variant gathers the victim storage volume serial number and the storage device name.
Text: JHUHUGIT从Windows注册表键HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\Disk\Enum获取构建标识符以及受害者硬盘信息。另一个JHUHUGIT变体收集了受害者的存储卷序列号和存储设备名称。

en_text: The JHUHUGIT dropper can delete itself from the victim. Another JHUHUGIT variant has the capability to delete specified files.
Text: JHUHUGIT滴管可以从受害者身上删除自己。另一个JHUHUGIT变种有能力删除指定文件。

en_text: JHUHUGIT obtains a list of running processes on the victim.
Text: JHUHUGIT获取受害者上运行的进程列表

en_text: JHUHUGIT can retrieve an additional payload from its C2 server. JHUHUGIT has a command to download files to the victim’s machine.
Text: JHUHUGIT可以从其C2服务器检索到一个额外的有效载荷

en_text: JHUHUGIT uses a .bat file to execute a .dll.
Text: JHUHUGIT使用一个.bat文件来执行一个.dll

en_text: JHUHUGIT is executed using rundll32.exe.
Text: JHUHUGIT是用rundll32.exe执行的

en_text: JHUHUGIT has used COM hijacking to establish persistence by hijacking a class named MMDeviceEnumerator and also by registering the payload as a Shell Icon Overlay handler COM object ({{3543619C-D563-43f7-95EA-4DA7E1CC396A}}).
Text: JHUHUGIT通过劫持一个名为MMDeviceEnumerator的类，同时将有效载荷注册为Shell Icon Overlay handler COM对象（{{3543619C-D563-43f7-95EA-4DA7E1CC396A}），利用COM劫持来建立持久性

en_text: JHUHUGIT has used a Registry Run key to establish persistence by executing JavaScript code within the rundll32.exe process.
Text: JHUHUGIT通过在rundll32.exe进程中执行JavaScript代码，使用了一个注册表运行键来建立持久性

en_text: JHUHUGIT has registered itself as a scheduled task to run each time the current user logs in.
Text: JHUHUGIT已将自己注册为一个计划任务，在当前用户每次登录时运行

en_text: JHUHUGIT has registered itself as a service to establish persistence.
Text: JHUHUGIT已经将自己注册为一项服务，以建立持久性

en_text: JHUHUGIT has exploited CVE-2015-1701 and CVE-2015-2387 to escalate privileges.
Text: JHUHUGIT已利用CVE-2015-1701和CVE-2015-2387升级权限

en_text: JHUHUGIT has registered a Windows shell script under the Registry key HKCU\Environment\UserInitMprLogonScript to establish persistence.
Text: JHUHUGIT在注册表键HKCU\Environment\UserInitMprLogonScript下注册了一个Windows shell脚本以建立持久性

en_text: JHUHUGIT performs code injection injecting its own functions to browser processes.
Text: JHUHUGIT执行代码注入，将自己的功能注入到浏览器进程

en_text: Many strings in JHUHUGIT are obfuscated with a XOR algorithm.
Text: JHUHUGIT中的许多字符串是用XOR算法混淆的

en_text: JPIN contains a custom keylogger.
Text: JPIN包含一个自定义的键盘记录器

en_text: JPIN's installer/uninstaller component deletes itself if it encounters a version of Windows earlier than Windows XP or identifies security-related processes running.
Text: JPIN的安装/卸载程序组件如果遇到比Windows XP更早的Windows版本或识别出正在运行的安全相关进程，就会自我删除。

en_text: JPIN checks for the presence of certain security-related processes and deletes its installer/uninstaller component if it identifies any of them.
Text: JPIN检查是否存在某些与安全有关的进程并删除其安装程序

en_text: JPIN can obtain the permissions of the victim user.
Text: JPIN可以获得受害用户的权限

en_text: JPIN can obtain the victim user name.
Text: JPIN可以获得受害者的用户名

en_text: JPIN can obtain network information, including DNS, IP, and proxies.
Text: JPIN可以获得网络信息，包括DNS、IP和代理机构

en_text: JPIN can obtain system information such as OS version and disk space.
Text: JPIN可以获得系统信息，如操作系统版本和磁盘空间

en_text: JPIN can list running services.
Text: JPIN可以列出正在运行的服务

en_text: JPIN can list running processes.
Text: JPIN可以列出正在运行的进程

en_text: JPIN can enumerate drives and their types. It can also change file permissions using cacls.exe.
Text: JPIN可以列举驱动器和它们的类型

en_text: JPIN can enumerate Registry keys.
Text: JPIN可以列举注册表的键值

en_text: JPIN can use the command-line utility cacls.exe to change file permissions.
Text: JPIN可以使用命令行工具cacls.exe来改变文件权限

en_text: JPIN can communicate over FTP.
Text: JPIN可以通过FTP进行通信

en_text: JPIN can send email over SMTP.
Text: JPIN可以通过SMTP发送电子邮件

en_text: JPIN can lower security settings by changing Registry keys.
Text: JPIN可以通过改变注册表键来降低安全设置

en_text: JPIN can download files and upgrade itself.
Text: JPIN可以下载文件并自我升级

en_text: JPIN can inject content into lsass.exe to load a module.
Text: JPIN可以在lsass.exe中注入内容，以加载一个模块。

en_text: A JPIN uses a encrypted and compressed payload that is disguised as a bitmap within the resource section of the installer.
Text: JPIN使用一个加密和压缩的有效载荷，在安装程序的资源部分伪装成位图

en_text: jRAT’s Java payload is encrypted with AES. Additionally, backdoor files are encrypted using DES as a stream cipher. Later variants of jRAT also incorporated AV evasion methods such as Java bytecode obfuscation via the commercial Allatori obfuscation tool.
Text: jRAT的Java有效载荷是用AES加密的。此外，后门文件是用DES作为流密码进行加密的。jRAT的后期变种还纳入了AV规避方法，如通过商业的Allatori混淆工具对Java字节码进行混淆。

en_text: jRAT has the capability to capture video from a webcam.
Text: jRAT具有从网络摄像头捕捉视频的能力

en_text: jRAT can be configured to reconnect at certain intervals.
Text: jRAT可以被配置为在一定时间内重新连接

en_text: jRAT can capture clipboard data.
Text: jRAT可以捕获剪贴板数据

en_text: jRAT can capture microphone recordings.
Text: jRAT可以捕获麦克风的录音

en_text: jRAT can query and kill system processes.
Text: jRAT可以查询和杀死系统进程

en_text: jRAT can capture passwords from common web browsers such as Internet Explorer, Google Chrome, and Firefox.
Text: jRAT可以从Internet Explorer、Google Chrome和Firefox等常见网络浏览器中捕获密码

en_text: jRAT can capture passwords from common chat applications such as MSN Messenger, AOL, Instant Messenger, and and Google Talk.
Text: jRAT可以从MSN Messenger、AOL、Instant Messenger和Google Talk等常见的聊天程序中捕获密码

en_text: jRAT can list security software, such as by using WMIC to identify anti-virus products installed on the victim’s machine and to obtain firewall details.
Text: jRAT可以列出安全软件，例如通过使用WMIC来识别受害者机器上安装的反病毒产品并获得防火墙的详细信息

en_text: jRAT can list and manage startup entries.
Text: jRAT可以列出并管理启动项

en_text: jRAT can list local services.
Text: jRAT可以列出当地的服务

en_text: jRAT can list network connections.
Text: jRAT可以列出网络连接

en_text: jRAT can browse file systems.
Text: jRAT可以浏览文件系统

en_text: jRAT can steal keys for VPNs and cryptocurrency wallets.
Text: jRAT可以窃取VPN和加密货币钱包的密钥

en_text: jRAT can gather victim internal and external IPs.
Text: jRAT可以收集受害者的内部和外部IP

en_text: jRAT can download and execute files.
Text: jRAT可以下载和执行文件

en_text: jRAT can map UPnP ports.
Text: jRAT可以映射UPnP端口

en_text: jRAT can support RDP control.
Text: jRAT可以支持RDP控制

en_text: jRAT can serve as a SOCKS proxy server.
Text: jRAT可以作为一个SOCKS代理服务器

en_text: jRAT uses WMIC to identify anti-virus products installed on the victim’s machine and to obtain firewall details.
Text: jRAT使用WMIC来识别受害者机器上安装的防病毒产品，并获得防火墙的详细信息

en_text: jRAT has been distributed as HTA files with JScript.
Text: jRAT已作为HTA文件与JScript一起分发

en_text: jRAT has been distributed as HTA files with VBScript.
Text: jRAT已作为HTA文件与VBScript一起分发

en_text: jRAT has command line access.
Text: jRAT有命令行权限

en_text: jRAT has the capability to take screenshots of the victim’s machine.
Text: jRAT有能力对受害者的机器进行截图

en_text: jRAT has the capability to log keystrokes from the victim’s machine, both offline and online.
Text: jRAT有能力记录受害者机器的击键，包括离线和在线

en_text: jRAT payloads have been packed.
Text: jRAT有效载荷已经打包

en_text: jRAT has a function to delete files from the victim’s machine.
Text: jRAT有一个从受害者的机器上删除文件的功能

en_text: jRAT collects information about the OS (version, build type, install date) as well as system up-time upon receiving a connection from a backdoor.
Text: jRAT在收到来自后门的连接时，会收集有关操作系统（版本、构建类型、安装日期）以及系统运行时间的信息

en_text: KARAE can upload and download files, including second-stage malware.
Text: KARAE可以上传和下载文件，包括第二阶段的恶意软件

en_text: KARAE can use public cloud-based storage providers for command and control.
Text: KARAE可以使用基于公共云的存储供应商进行指挥和控制

en_text: KARAE can collect system information.
Text: KARAE可以收集系统信息

en_text: KARAE was distributed through torrent file-sharing websites to South Korean victims, using a YouTube video downloader application as a lure.
Text: KARAE通过torrent文件共享网站向韩国受害者传播，使用YouTube视频下载器应用程序作为诱饵

en_text: Kazuar encodes communications to the C2 server in Base64.
Text: Kazuar将与C2服务器的通信以Base64编码

en_text: Kazuar uploads files from a specified directory to the C2 server.
Text: Kazuar将指定目录下的文件上传到C2服务器

en_text: Kazuar can install itself as a new service.
Text: Kazuar可以把自己安装成一个新的服务

en_text: Kazuar can accept multiple URLs for C2 servers.
Text: Kazuar可以接受C2服务器的多个URL

en_text: Kazuar can overwrite files with random data before deleting them.
Text: Kazuar可以在删除文件前用随机数据覆盖文件

en_text: Kazuar uses cmd.exe to execute commands on the victim’s machine.
Text: Kazuar使用cmd.exe在受害者的机器上执行命令

en_text: Kazuar uses FTP and FTPS to communicate with the C2 server.
Text: Kazuar使用FTP和FTPS与C2服务器通信

en_text: Kazuar uses HTTP and HTTPS to communicate with the C2 server. Kazuar can also act as a webserver and listen for inbound HTTP requests through an exposed API.
Text: Kazuar使用HTTP和HTTPS与C2服务器通信。Kazuar也可以作为一个网络服务器，通过暴露的API监听入站的HTTP请求。

en_text: Kazuar is obfuscated using the open source ConfuserEx protector. Kazuar also obfuscates the name of created files/folders/mutexes and encrypts debug messages written to log files using the Rijndael cipher.
Text: Kazuar使用开源的ConfuserEx保护器进行模糊处理。Kazuar还对创建的文件/文件夹/mutexes的名称进行混淆，并使用Rijndael密码对写入日志文件的调试信息进行加密。

en_text: Kazuar gathers information on local groups and members on the victim’s machine.
Text: Kazuar收集了受害者机器上的本地组和成员的信息

en_text: Kazuar gathers information on the system and local drives.
Text: Kazuar收集系统和本地驱动器的信息

en_text: Kazuar downloads additional plug-ins to load on the victim’s machine, including the ability to upgrade and replace its own binary.
Text: Kazuar下载额外的插件加载到受害者的机器上，包括升级和替换自己的二进制文件的能力

en_text: Kazuar adds a .lnk file to the Windows startup folder.
Text: Kazuar在Windows启动文件夹中添加一个.lnk文件

en_text: Kazuar adds a sub-key under several Registry run keys.
Text: Kazuar在几个注册表运行键下添加了一个子键

en_text: Kazuar finds a specified directory, lists the files and metadata about those files.
Text: Kazuar找到一个指定的目录，列出文件和关于这些文件的元数据

en_text: Ke3chang gathered information and files from local directories for exfiltration.
Text: Ke3chang从本地目录中收集信息和文件进行渗透

en_text: Ke3chang malware RoyalCli and BS2005 have communicated over HTTP with the C2 server through Internet Explorer (IE) by using the COM interface IWebBrowser2.
Text: Ke3chang恶意软件RoyalCli和BS2005通过Internet Explorer（IE）使用COM接口IWebBrowser2与C2服务器进行了HTTP通信

en_text: Ke3chang malware RoyalDNS has used DNS for C2.
Text: Ke3chang恶意软件RoyalDNS已使用DNS进行C2

en_text: Ke3chang backdoor RoyalDNS established persistence through adding a service called Nwsapagent.
Text: Ke3chang后门RoyalDNS通过添加一个名为Nwsapagent的服务建立了持久性

en_text: Ke3chang has used the right-to-left override character in spearphishing attachment names to trick targets into executing .scr and .exe files.
Text: Ke3chang利用鱼叉式网络钓鱼附件名称中从右到左的覆盖字符，欺骗目标执行.scr和.exe文件

en_text: Ke3chang performs local network configuration discovery using ipconfig.
Text: Ke3chang使用ipconfig执行本地网络配置发现

en_text: Ke3chang has used Mimikatz to generate Kerberos golden tickets.
Text: Ke3chang使用Mimikatz来生成Kerberos金票

en_text: Ke3chang performs account discovery using commands such as net localgroup administrators and net group "REDACTED" /domain on specific permissions groups.
Text: Ke3chang使用net localgroup administrators和net group "REDACTED "等命令进行账户发现

en_text: Ke3chang performs service discovery using net start commands.
Text: Ke3chang使用net start命令执行服务发现

en_text: Ke3chang performs local network connection discovery using netstat.
Text: Ke3chang使用netstat执行本地网络连接发现

en_text: Ke3chang performs operating system information discovery using systeminfo.
Text: Ke3chang使用systeminfo执行操作系统信息发现

en_text: Malware used by Ke3chang can run commands on the command-line interface.
Text: Ke3chang使用的恶意软件可以在命令行界面上运行命令

en_text: Ke3chang has used a tool known as RemoteExec (similar to PsExec) to remotely execute batch scripts and binaries.
Text: Ke3chang使用了一个被称为RemoteExec（类似于PsExec）的工具来远程执行批脚本和二进制文件

en_text: Ke3chang used a SharePoint enumeration and data dumping tool known as spwebmember.
Text: Ke3chang使用了一个名为spwebmember的SharePoint枚举和数据转储工具

en_text: Ke3chang uses command-line interaction to search files and directories.
Text: Ke3chang使用命令行交互来搜索文件和目录

en_text: Ke3chang performs process discovery using tasklist commands.
Text: Ke3chang使用任务列表命令执行进程发现

en_text: Ke3chang used a .NET tool to dump data from Microsoft Exchange mailboxes.
Text: Ke3chang使用一个.NET工具从微软Exchange邮箱中转储数据

en_text: Ke3chang has dumped credentials, including by using Mimikatz.
Text: Ke3chang已经倾销了证书，包括通过使用Mimikatz

en_text: Ke3chang has used keyloggers.
Text: Ke3chang已经使用了键盘记录器

en_text: Ke3chang has used network scanning and enumeration tools, including Ping.
Text: Ke3chang已经使用了网络扫描和枚举工具，包括Ping

en_text: Ke3chang has dumped credentials, including by using gsecdump.
Text: Ke3chang已经转储了证书，包括通过使用gsecdump

en_text: Ke3chang regained access after eviction via the corporate VPN solution with a stolen VPN certificate, which they had extracted from a compromised host.
Text: Ke3chang在被驱逐后通过公司的VPN解决方案重新获得了访问权，他们使用的是偷来的VPN证书，该证书是从被攻击的主机上提取的

en_text: Ke3chang has used batch scripts in its malware to install persistence mechanisms.
Text: Ke3chang在其恶意软件中使用批处理脚本来安装持久化机制。

en_text: Ke3chang transferred compressed and encrypted RAR files containing exfiltration through the established backdoor command and control channel during operations.
Text: Ke3chang在行动中通过已建立的后门指挥和控制渠道传输包含渗出的压缩和加密的RAR文件

en_text: Ke3chang performs discovery of permission groups net group /domain.
Text: Ke3chang执行发现权限组的网组 Ke3chang执行发现权限组网组 Ke3chang执行发现权限组网组的工作 Ke3chang执行发现权限组网群

en_text: Kessel's configuration is hardcoded and RC4 encrypted within the binary.
Text: Kessel的配置是硬编码的，并在二进制中进行了RC4加密

en_text: Kessel has trojanized the ssh_login and user-auth_pubkey functions to steal plaintext credentials.
Text: Kessel对ssh_login和user-auth_pubkey函数进行了木马化，以窃取明文凭证

en_text: Kessel has maliciously altered the OpenSSH binary on targeted systems to create a backdoor.
Text: Kessel恶意地改变了目标系统上的OpenSSH二进制文件，以创建一个后门

en_text: Kessel has exfiltrated information gathered from the infected system to the C2 server.
Text: Kessel将从受感染的系统中收集的信息渗透到C2服务器

en_text: Kessel can download additional modules from the C2 server.
Text: Kessel可以从C2服务器下载额外的模块

en_text: Kessel can split the data to be exilftrated into chunks that will fit in subdomains of DNS queries.
Text: Kessel可以将要放出的数据分割成适合DNS查询的子域的块状

en_text: Kessel can exfiltrate credentials and other information via HTTP POST request, TCP, and DNS.
Text: Kessel可以通过HTTP POST请求、TCP和DNS渗出凭证和其他信息

en_text: Kessel can create a reverse shell between the infected host and a specified system.
Text: Kessel可以在被感染的主机和指定的系统之间创建一个反向的外壳

en_text: Kessel can RC4-encrypt credentials before sending to the C2.
Text: Kessel可以在向C2发送之前对凭证进行RC4加密

en_text: Kessel has exfiltrated data via hexadecimal-encoded subdomain fields of DNS queries.
Text: Kessel通过DNS查询的十六进制编码的子域字段来渗出数据

en_text: Kessel has collected the DNS address of the infected host.
Text: Kessel已经收集了被感染主机的DNS地址

en_text: Kessel has collected the system architecture, OS version, and MAC address information.
Text: Kessel已经收集了系统架构、操作系统版本和MAC地址信息

en_text: Kessel has decrypted the binary's configuration once the main function was launched.
Text: Kessel在主功能启动后，已经解密了二进制的配置

en_text: KeyBoy installs a keylogger for intercepting credentials and keystrokes.
Text: KeyBoy安装了一个键盘记录器，用于拦截凭证和击键

en_text: KeyBoy installs a service pointing to a malicious DLL dropped to disk.
Text: KeyBoy安装了一个指向丢到磁盘上的恶意DLL的服务

en_text: KeyBoy time-stomped its DLL in order to evade detection.
Text: KeyBoy对其DLL进行了时间处理，以逃避检测

en_text: KeyBoy issues the command reg add "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon" to achieve persistence.
Text: KeyBoy发出命令reg添加 "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon "以实现持久化

en_text: KeyBoy has a download and upload functionality.
Text: KeyBoy具有下载和上传功能

en_text: KeyBoy can launch interactive shells for communicating with the victim machine.
Text: KeyBoy可以启动交互式外壳，与受害者机器进行通信

en_text: KeyBoy can determine the public or WAN IP address for the system.
Text: KeyBoy可以确定系统的公共或WAN IP地址

en_text: KeyBoy can gather extended system information, such as information about the operating system, disks, and memory.
Text: KeyBoy可以收集扩展的系统信息，如关于操作系统、磁盘和内存的信息

en_text: KeyBoy uses PowerShell commands to download and execute payloads.
Text: KeyBoy使用PowerShell命令来下载和执行有效载荷

en_text: KeyBoy uses Python scripts for installing files and performing execution.
Text: KeyBoy使用Python脚本来安装文件和进行执行

en_text: KeyBoy uses VBS scripts for installing files and performing execution.
Text: KeyBoy使用VBS脚本来安装文件和执行

en_text: KeyBoy uses -w Hidden to conceal a PowerShell window that downloads a payload.
Text: KeyBoy使用-w隐藏来隐藏一个下载有效载荷的PowerShell窗口

en_text: KeyBoy uses custom SSL libraries to impersonate SSL in C2 traffic.
Text: KeyBoy使用定制的SSL库来冒充C2流量中的SSL

en_text: KeyBoy uses the Dynamic Data Exchange (DDE) protocol to download remote payloads.
Text: KeyBoy使用动态数据交换（DDE）协议来下载远程有效载荷

en_text: KeyBoy attempts to collect passwords from browsers.
Text: KeyBoy试图从浏览器中收集密码

en_text: KeyBoy has a command to launch a file browser or explorer on the system.
Text: KeyBoy有一个命令，可以在系统上启动一个文件浏览器或资源管理器

en_text: KeyBoy has a command to perform screen grabbing.
Text: KeyBoy有一个命令可以进行屏幕抓取

en_text: Keydnap adds the setuid flag to a binary so it can easily elevate in the future.
Text: Keydnap将setuid标志添加到二进制文件中，这样它就可以在未来轻松地提升

en_text: Keydnap uses HTTPS for command and control.
Text: Keydnap使用HTTPS进行指挥和控制

en_text: Keydnap uses the keychaindump project to read securityd memory.
Text: Keydnap使用keychaindump项目来读取securityd内存

en_text: Keydnap uses Python for scripting to execute additional commands.
Text: Keydnap使用Python作为脚本来执行额外的命令

Text: Koadic使用Windows脚本主机（VBScript）执行其大部分操作，并运行任意的shellcode

Text: Koadic有两种提升完整性的方法

Text: Komplex木马创建了一个持久的启动代理，用$HOME调用

en_text: KONNI creates a shortcut called "Anti virus service.lnk" in an apparent attempt to masquerade as a legitimate file.
Text: KONNI创建了一个名为 "反病毒服务.lnk "的快捷方式，显然是想伪装成一个合法文件

en_text: A version of KONNI searches for filenames created with a previous version of the malware, suggesting different versions targeted the same victims and the versions may work together.
Text: KONNI的一个版本会搜索用以前版本的恶意软件创建的文件名，这表明不同的版本针对的是同一个受害者，而且这些版本可能会一起工作

en_text: A version of KONNI drops a Windows shortcut into the Startup folder to establish persistence.
Text: KONNI的一个版本将一个Windows快捷方式放入启动文件夹以建立持久性

en_text: A version of KONNI drops a Windows shortcut on the victim’s machine to establish persistence.
Text: KONNI的一个版本在受害者的机器上投放了一个Windows快捷方式以建立持久性

en_text: KONNI has duplicated the token of a high integrity process to spawn an instance of cmd.exe under an impersonated user.
Text: KONNI复制了一个高完整性进程的令牌，在一个冒名的用户下生成了cmd.exe的实例

en_text: KONNI has the capability to perform keylogging.
Text: KONNI具有进行键盘记录的能力

Text: KONNI可以从Firefox、Chrome和Opera中窃取配置文件（包含凭证信息）

en_text: KONNI can collect the IP address from the victim’s machine.
Text: KONNI可以从受害者的机器上收集IP地址

en_text: KONNI can gather the OS version, architecture information, connected drives, hostname, and computer name from the victim’s machine and has used systeminfo.exe to get a snapshot of the current system state of the target machine.
Text: KONNI可以从受害者的机器上收集操作系统版本、架构信息、连接的驱动器、主机名和计算机名，并已使用systeminfo.exe获得目标机器当前系统状态的快照

en_text: KONNI can collect the username from the victim’s machine.

Text: KONNI可以对受害者的机器进行截图

Text: KONNI利用FTP将侦查数据外流

en_text: KONNI has used cmd.exe execute arbitrary commands on the infected host across different stages of the infection change.
Text: KONNI使用cmd.exe在感染主机上执行任意命令，跨越感染变化的不同阶段

en_text: KONNI used PowerShell to download and execute a specific 64-bit version of the malware.

en_text: KONNI has used Rundll32 to execute its loader for privilege escalation purposes.
Text: KONNI使用Rundll32来执行其加载器，以达到权限升级的目的

en_text: KONNI bypassed UAC with the "AlwaysNotify" settings.
Text: KONNI通过 "AlwaysNotify "设置绕过了UAC

en_text: KONNI has modified ComSysApp service to load the malicious DLL payload.
Text: KONNI修改了ComSysApp服务以加载恶意的DLL有效载荷

en_text: KONNI has modified registry keys of ComSysApp service and Svchost on the machine to gain persistence.
Text: KONNI修改了机器上ComSysApp服务和Svchost的注册表键，以获得持久性

en_text: KONNI has used HTTP for C2.
Text: KONNI已将HTTP用于C2

en_text: KONNI has used certutil to download and decode base64 encoded strings.
Text: KONNI已经使用certutil下载和解码base64编码的字符串

en_text: KONNI had a feature to steal data from the clipboard.
Text: KONNI有一个功能，可以从剪贴板上偷取数据

en_text: KONNI has used a custom base64 key to encode stolen data before exfiltration.
Text: KONNI在渗透前使用了一个定制的base64密钥来对被盗数据进行编码

en_text: Kwampirs creates a new service named WmiApSrvEx to establish persistence.
Text: Kwampirs创建了一个名为WmiApSrvEx的新服务来建立持久性

en_text: Kwampirs downloads additional files from C2 servers.
Text: Kwampirs从C2服务器下载其他文件

en_text: Kwampirs uses rundll32.exe in a Registry value added to establish persistence.
Text: Kwampirs使用rundll32.exe在注册表中添加值来建立持久性

en_text: Kwampirs uses a large list of C2 servers that it cycles through until a successful connection is established.
Text: Kwampirs使用一个庞大的C2服务器列表，它循环使用，直到建立成功的连接

en_text: Kwampirs collects a list of users belonging to the local users and administrators groups with the commands net localgroup administrators and net localgroup users.
Text: Kwampirs通过net localgroup administrators和net localgroup users命令收集属于本地用户和管理员组的用户列表

en_text: Kwampirs collects a list of files and directories in C:\ with the command dir /s /a c:\ >> "C:\windows\TEMP[RANDOM].tmp".
Text: Kwampirs通过命令dir收集C:\中的文件和目录列表

en_text: Kwampirs collects a list of domain groups with the command net localgroup /domain.
Text: Kwampirs通过命令net localgroup收集域组的列表

en_text: Kwampirs collects a list of network shares with the command net share.
Text: Kwampirs通过命令net share收集网络共享的列表

en_text: Kwampirs collects a list of accounts with the command net users.
Text: Kwampirs通过命令net users收集一个账户列表

en_text: Kwampirs collects a list of available servers with the command net view.
Text: Kwampirs通过命令net view收集可用的服务器列表

en_text: Kwampirs collects password policy information with the command net accounts.
Text: Kwampirs通过命令net账户收集密码策略信息

en_text: Kwampirs collects a list of running services with the command tasklist /svc.
Text: Kwampirs通过命令tasklist收集正在运行的服务列表

en_text: Kwampirs collects a list of running services with the command tasklist /v.
Text: Kwampirs通过命令tasklist收集正在运行的服务列表

en_text: Kwampirs collects a list of active and listening connections by using the command netstat -nao as well as a list of available network mappings with net use.
Text: Kwampirs通过使用netstat -nao命令收集活动和监听连接的列表，以及使用net的可用网络映射的列表

en_text: Kwampirs collects network adapter and interface information by using the commands ipconfig /all, arp -a and route print. It also collects the system's MAC address with getmac and domain configuration with net config workstation.
Text: Kwampirs通过使用命令ipconfig /all、arp -a和route print来收集网络适配器和接口信息。它还用getmac收集系统的MAC地址，用net config workstation收集域配置。

en_text: Kwampirs collects OS version information such as registered owner details, manufacturer details, processor type, available storage, installed patches, hostname, version info, system date, and other system information by using the commands systeminfo, net config workstation, hostname, ver, set, and date /t.
Text: Kwampirs通过使用命令systeminfo、net config workstation、hostname、ver、set和date收集操作系统的版本信息，如注册所有者的详细信息、制造商的详细信息、处理器类型、可用存储空间、已安装的补丁、主机名、版本信息、系统日期和其他系统信息

en_text: Kwampirs collects registered owner details by using the commands systeminfo and net config workstation.
Text: Kwampirs通过使用命令systeminfo和net config workstation收集注册所有者的详细信息

en_text: Kwampirs establishes persistence by adding a new service with the display name "WMI Performance Adapter Extension" in an attempt to masquerade as a legitimate WMI service.
Text: Kwampirs通过添加一个显示名为 "WMI性能适配器扩展 "的新服务来建立持久性，试图伪装成合法的WMI服务

en_text: Kwampirs copies itself over network shares to move laterally on a victim network.
Text: Kwampirs通过网络共享复制自己，在受害者网络上横向移动

en_text: Kwampirs downloads additional files that are base64-encoded and encrypted with another cipher.
Text: Kwampirs下载了额外的文件，这些文件是以base64编码的，并以另一种密码进行加密

en_text: Kwampirs decrypts and extracts a copy of its main DLL payload when executing.
Text: Kwampirs在执行时解密并提取其主要DLL有效载荷的副本

en_text: LaZagne can perform credential dumping from LSA secrets to obtain account and password information.

en_text: LaZagne can obtain credentials from macOS Keychains.

en_text: LaZagne can perform credential dumping from MSCache to obtain account and password information.

en_text: LaZagne can obtain credentials from web browsers such as Google Chrome, Internet Explorer, and Firefox.
Text: LaZagne可以从谷歌浏览器、IE浏览器和火狐浏览器等网络浏览器中获取凭证

en_text: LaZagne can obtain credentials from chats, databases, mail, and WiFi.
Text: LaZagne可以从聊天记录、数据库、邮件和WiFi中获取凭证

en_text: LaZagne can perform credential dumping from memory to obtain account and password information.
Text: LaZagne可以从内存中执行凭证转储，以获得账户和密码信息

en_text: LaZagne can obtain credentials from databases, mail, and WiFi across multiple platforms.
