Text: TEMP.Veles利用VPN在受害者环境中持续存在

en_text: TEMP.Veles has used Mimikatz and a custom tool, SecHack, to harvest credentials.
Text: TEMP.Veles使用了Mimikatz和一个自定义工具SecHack来获取凭证

en_text: TEMP.Veles has used compromised VPN accounts.
Text: TEMP.Veles使用了被泄露的VPN账户

en_text: TEMP.Veles has used a publicly-available PowerShell-based tool, WMImplant. The group has also used PowerShell to perform Timestomping.
Text: TEMP.Veles使用了一个公开的基于PowerShell的工具，WMImplant。该组织还使用PowerShell来执行Timestomping。

en_text: TEMP.Veles used timestomping to modify the $STANDARD_INFORMATION attribute on tools.
Text: TEMP.Veles使用时间分解法来修改工具上的$STANDARD_INFORMATION属性

en_text: TEMP.Veles has modified files based on the open-source project cryptcat in an apparent attempt to decrease AV detection rates.
Text: TEMP.Veles修改了基于开源项目cryptcat的文件，显然是为了降低AV检测率

en_text: TEMP.Veles has relied on encrypted SSH-based tunnels to transfer tools and for remote command/program execution.
Text: TEMP.Veles依靠基于SSH的加密隧道来传输工具，并用于远程命令

en_text: TEMP.Veles has used scheduled task XML triggers.
Text: TEMP.Veles已经使用了预定任务的XML触发器

en_text: TEMP.Veles has used port-protocol mismatches on ports such as 443, 4444, 8531, and 50501 during C2.
Text: TEMP.Veles在C2期间在443、4444、8531和50501等端口上使用了端口协议错配

en_text: TEMP.Veles has modified and added entries within HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Image File Execution Options to maintain persistence.
Text: TEMP.Veles在HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Image File Execution Options中修改并添加了条目，以保持持久性

en_text: TEMP.Veles has planted Web shells on Outlook Exchange servers.
Text: TEMP.Veles在Outlook Exchange服务器上植入了Web shells

en_text: TEMP.Veles has created staging folders in directories that were infrequently used by legitimate users or processes.
Text: TEMP.Veles在合法用户或进程不经常使用的目录中创建了暂存文件夹

en_text: TEMP.Veles routinely deleted tools, logs, and other files after they were finished with them.
Text: TEMP.Veles在使用完工具、日志和其他文件后，会定期删除这些文件

en_text: TEMP.Veles utilized RDP throughout an operation.
Text: TEMP.Veles在整个行动中利用了RDP

en_text: TEXTMATE uses DNS TXT records for C2.
Text: TEXTMATE使用DNS TXT记录进行C2

en_text: TEXTMATE executes cmd.exe to provide a reverse shell to adversaries.
Text: TEXTMATE执行cmd.exe，为对手提供一个反向外壳

en_text: Thrip leveraged PowerShell to run commands to download payloads, traverse the compromised networks, and carry out reconnaissance.
Text: Thrip利用PowerShell来运行命令，下载有效载荷，穿越被破坏的网络，并进行侦察

en_text: Thrip has used WinSCP to exfiltrate data from a targeted organization over FTP.
Text: Thrip利用WinSCP通过FTP从一个目标组织渗出数据

en_text: Thrip used a cloud-based remote access software called LogMeIn for their attacks.
Text: Thrip使用一种名为LogMeIn的云端远程访问软件进行攻击

en_text: TINYTYPHON installs itself under Registry Run key to establish persistence.
Text: TINYTYPHON将自己安装在注册表运行键下，以建立持久性

en_text: TINYTYPHON searches through the drive containing the OS, then all drive letters C through to Z, for documents matching certain extensions.
Text: TINYTYPHON搜索包含操作系统的驱动器，然后是所有驱动器的字母C到Z，以寻找符合某些扩展名的文件

en_text: TINYTYPHON has used XOR with 0x90 to obfuscate its configuration file.
Text: TINYTYPHON用0x90的XOR来混淆其配置文件

en_text: TinyZBot contains functionality to collect information from the clipboard.
Text: TinyZBot包含从剪贴板收集信息的功能

en_text: TinyZBot contains keylogger functionality.
Text: TinyZBot包含键盘记录器功能

en_text: TinyZBot contains screen capture functionality.
Text: TinyZBot包含屏幕捕捉功能

en_text: TinyZBot can install as a Windows service for persistence.
Text: TinyZBot可以安装为一个Windows服务，以实现持久性

en_text: TinyZBot can disable Avira anti-virus.
Text: TinyZBot可以使Avira防病毒软件失效

en_text: TinyZBot can create a shortcut in the Windows startup folder for persistence.
Text: TinyZBot可以在Windows的启动文件夹中创建一个快捷方式，以实现持久性

en_text: TinyZBot supports execution from the command-line.
Text: TinyZBot支持从命令行执行

en_text: Tor encapsulates traffic in multiple layers of encryption, using TLS by default.
Text: Tor对流量进行多层加密封装，默认使用TLS

en_text: TrickBot has attempted to get users to launch malicious documents to deliver its payload.
Text: TrickBot曾试图让用户启动恶意文件来传递其有效载荷

en_text: TrickBot collects email addresses from Outlook.
Text: TrickBot从Outlook收集电子邮件地址

en_text: TrickBot collects local files and information from the victim’s local machine.
Text: TrickBot从受害者的本地机器上收集本地文件和信息

en_text: TrickBot obtains the IP address, location, and other relevant network information from the victim’s machine.
Text: TrickBot从受害者的机器上获取IP地址、位置和其他相关网络信息

en_text: TrickBot decodes the configuration data and modules.
Text: TrickBot对配置数据和模块进行解码

en_text: TrickBot can obtain passwords stored in files from web browsers such as Chrome, Firefox, Internet Explorer, and Microsoft Edge, sometimes using esentutl.
Text: TrickBot可以从Chrome、Firefox、Internet Explorer和Microsoft Edge等网络浏览器中获取存储在文件中的密码，有时使用esentutl

en_text: TrickBot can steal passwords from the KeePass open source password manager.
Text: TrickBot可以从KeePass开源密码管理器中窃取密码

en_text: TrickBot can Base64-encode C2 commands.
Text: TrickBot可以对C2命令进行Base64编码

en_text: TrickBot can obtain passwords stored in files from several applications such as Outlook, Filezilla, OpenSSH, OpenVPN and WinSCP. Additionally, it searches for the ".vnc.lnk" affix to steal VNC credentials.
Text: TrickBot可以获取存储在Outlook、Filezilla、OpenSSH、OpenVPN和WinSCP等几个应用程序文件中的密码。此外，它还会搜索".vnc.lnk "标签以窃取VNC凭证。

en_text: TrickBot can enumerate computers and network devices.
Text: TrickBot可以列举计算机和网络设备

en_text: TrickBot can identify the groups the user on a compromised host belongs to.
Text: TrickBot可以识别被入侵主机上的用户所属的组

en_text: TrickBot can identify the user and groups the user belongs to on a compromised host.
Text: TrickBot可以识别用户和用户在被攻击主机上所属的组

en_text: TrickBot can disable Windows Defender.
Text: TrickBot可以使Windows Defender失效

en_text: TrickBot can gather information about domain trusts by utilizing Nltest.
Text: TrickBot可以通过利用Nltest来收集关于域名信任的信息

en_text: TrickBot can send information about the compromised host to a hardcoded C2 server.
Text: TrickBot可以向一个硬编码的C2服务器发送有关被攻击主机的信息

en_text: TrickBot can modify registry entries.
Text: TrickBot可以修改注册表项

en_text: TrickBot has used macros in Excel documents to download and deploy the malware on the user’s machine.
Text: TrickBot利用Excel文档中的宏来下载并在用户的机器上部署恶意软件

en_text: TrickBot leverages a custom packer to obfuscate its functionality.
Text: TrickBot利用了一个自定义的打包器来混淆其功能

en_text: TrickBot has used an email with an Excel sheet containing a malicious macro to deploy the malware
Text: TrickBot利用一封含有恶意宏的Excel表格的电子邮件来部署恶意软件

en_text: TrickBot uses HTTPS to communicate with its C2 servers, to get malware updates, modules that perform most of the malware logic and various configuration files.
Text: TrickBot使用HTTPS与它的C2服务器进行通信，以获得恶意软件更新、执行大部分恶意软件逻辑的模块和各种配置文件

en_text: TrickBot uses the Windows API call, CreateProcessW(), to manage execution flow.
Text: TrickBot使用Windows API调用，CreateProcessW()来管理执行流程

en_text: TrickBot uses non-descriptive names to hide functionality and uses an AES CBC (256 bits) encryption algorithm for its loader and configuration files.
Text: TrickBot使用非描述性的名称来隐藏功能，并对其加载器和配置文件使用AES CBC（256比特）加密算法

en_text: TrickBot uses web injects and browser redirection to trick the user into providing their login credentials on a fake or modified web page.
Text: TrickBot使用网页注入和浏览器重定向，欺骗用户在一个虚假或修改过的网页上提供他们的登录凭证

en_text: TrickBot uses a custom crypter leveraging Microsoft’s CryptoAPI to encrypt C2 traffic.
Text: TrickBot使用一个自定义加密器，利用微软的CryptoAPI对C2流量进行加密

en_text: TrickBot has been delivered via malicious links in phishing e-mails.
Text: TrickBot是通过钓鱼邮件中的恶意链接传递的

en_text: TrickBot gathers the OS version, machine name, CPU type, amount of RAM available from the victim’s machine.
Text: TrickBot收集了受害者机器的操作系统版本、机器名称、CPU类型、可用的RAM数量

en_text: TrickBot collects the users of the system.
Text: TrickBot收集了系统的用户

en_text: TrickBot collects a list of install programs and services on the system’s machine.
Text: TrickBot收集系统机器上的安装程序和服务清单

en_text: TrickBot has retrieved PuTTY credentials by querying the Software\SimonTatham\Putty\Sessions registry key
Text: TrickBot通过查询Software/SimonTatham/Putty/Sessions注册表键来检索PuTTY凭证

en_text: TrickBot establishes persistence by creating an autostart service that allows it to run whenever the machine boots.
Text: TrickBot通过创建一个自动启动服务来建立持久性，使其能够在机器启动时运行

en_text: TrickBot downloads several additional files and saves them to the victim's machine.
Text: TrickBot下载了几个额外的文件，并将它们保存在受害者的机器上

en_text: The TrickBot downloader has used an icon to appear as a Microsoft Word document.
Text: TrickBot下载器使用了一个图标，以微软Word文档的形式出现

en_text: TrickBot has come with a signed downloader component.
Text: TrickBot已经附带了一个签名的下载器组件

en_text: TrickBot has the ability to capture RDP credentials by capturing the CredEnumerateA API
Text: TrickBot有能力通过捕获CredEnumerateA的API来捕获RDP凭证

en_text: TrickBot can use secondary C2 servers for communication after establishing connectivity and relaying victim information to primary C2 servers.
Text: TrickBot在建立连接并将受害者信息转发给主C2服务器后，可以使用二级C2服务器进行通信

en_text: TrickBot creates a scheduled task on the system that provides persistence.
Text: TrickBot在系统上创建一个提供持久性的计划任务

en_text: TrickBot searches the system for all of the following file extensions: .avi, .mov, .mkv, .mpeg, .mpeg4, .mp4, .mp3, .wav, .ogg, .jpeg, .jpg, .png, .bmp, .gif, .tiff, .ico, .xlsx, and .zip. It can also obtain browsing history, cookies, and plug-in information.
Text: TrickBot在系统中搜索所有下列文件扩展名：.avi, .mov, .mkv, .mpeg, .mpeg4, .mp4, .mp3, .wav, .ogg, .jpeg, .jpg, .png, .bmp, .gif, .tiff, .ico, .xlsx, 和 .zip

en_text: TrickBot injects into the svchost.exe process.
Text: TrickBot注入到svchost.exe进程中

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can capture information regarding the victim's OS, security, and hardware configuration.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以捕获有关受害者的操作系统、安全和硬件配置的信息

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can create directories to store plugin output and stage data for exfiltration.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以创建目录来存储插件的输出和阶段性数据，以便渗出

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can steal data and credentials from browsers.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以从浏览器中窃取数据和凭证

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can take a desktop screenshot and save the file into \ProgramData\Mail\MailAg\shot.png.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以对桌面进行截图，并将文件保存到 \ProgramData\Mail\MailAg\shot.png中

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can monitor the titles of open windows to identify specific keywords.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以监控打开的窗口的标题，以识别特定的关键词

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can inject a suspended thread of its own process into a new process and initiate via the ResumeThread API.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以将自己进程中的一个暂停线程注入一个新的进程，并通过ResumeThread API启动

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can enumerate files and directories on a compromised host.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以列举被攻击主机上的文件和目录

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can use netstat to collect a list of network connections.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以使用netstat来收集网络连接的列表

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can use Tasklist to collect a list of running tasks.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以使用任务列表来收集正在运行的任务列表

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can gather information on the network configuration of a compromised host.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以收集被攻击主机的网络配置信息

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can perform reconnaissance commands on a victim machine via a cmd.exe process.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以通过cmd.exe进程在受害者机器上执行侦查命令

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can communicate with C2 via HTTP POST requests.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以通过HTTP POST请求与C2通信

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can secure C2 communications with SSL and TLS.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以用SSL和TLS保证C2通信的安全

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can capture keystrokes on a compromised host.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以在被攻击的主机上捕获键盘信息

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can gather information about the user on a compromised host.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以在被攻击的主机上收集有关用户的信息

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can base64 encode and AES-128-CBC encrypt data prior to transmission.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以在传输前对数据进行base64编码和AES-128-CBC加密

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can create a link to itself in the Startup folder to automatically start itself upon system restart.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以在启动文件夹中为自己创建一个链接，在系统重新启动时自动启动

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can upload, download, and execute files on the victim.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以在受害者身上上传、下载和执行文件

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can detect commonly used and generic virtualization platforms based primarily on drivers and file paths.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以主要根据驱动程序和文件路径来检测常用和通用的虚拟化平台

en_text: Trojan.Karagany can dump passwords and save them into \ProgramData\Mail\MailAg\pwds.txt.
Text: Trojan.Karagany可以转储密码并将其保存到\ProgramData\Mail\MailAg\pwds.txt中

en_text: Trojan.Karagany has used plugins with a self-delete capability.
Text: Trojan.Karagany使用了具有自我删除功能的插件

en_text: Trojan.Karagany samples sometimes use common binary packers such as UPX and Aspack on top of a custom Delphi binary packer.
Text: Trojan.Karagany样本有时会在自定义的Delphi二进制打包器上使用通用的二进制打包器，如UPX和Aspack

en_text: Trojan.Mebromi performs BIOS modification and can download and execute a file as well as protect itself from removal.
Text: Trojan.Mebromi执行BIOS修改，可以下载和执行文件，也可以保护自己不被删除

en_text: Tropic Trooper is capable of enumerating the running processes on the system using pslist.
Text: Tropic Trooper 能够使用 pslist 枚举系统上的运行进程

en_text: Tropic Trooper has installed a service pointing to a malicious DLL dropped to disk.
Text: Tropic Trooper安装了一个服务，指向一个丢到磁盘上的恶意DLL

en_text: Tropic Trooper delivered malicious documents with the XLSX extension, typically used by OpenXML documents, but the file itself was actually an OLE (XLS) document.
Text: Tropic Trooper传递的恶意文件带有XLSX扩展名，通常用于OpenXML文件，但文件本身实际上是一个OLE（XLS）文件

en_text: Tropic Trooper has created the Registry key HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon\Shell and sets the value to establish persistence.
Text: Tropic Trooper创建了注册表键HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon\Shell，并设置值以建立持久性

en_text: Tropic Trooper's backdoor could list the infected system's installed software.
Text: Tropic Trooper的后门可以列出被感染的系统所安装的软件

en_text: Tropic Trooper's backdoor has communicated to the C2 over the DNS protocol.
Text: Tropic Trooper的后门已经通过DNS协议与C2进行了沟通

en_text: Tropic Trooper sent spearphishing emails that contained malicious Microsoft Office and fake installer file attachments.
Text: Tropic Trooper发送了包含恶意的微软Office和虚假安装文件附件的鱼叉式钓鱼邮件

en_text: Tropic Trooper has monitored files' modified time.
Text: Tropic Trooper监控了文件的修改时间

en_text: Tropic Trooper has detected a target system’s OS version and system volume information.
Text: Tropic Trooper检测到目标系统的操作系统版本和系统容量信息

en_text: Tropic Trooper can search for anti-virus software running on the system.
Text: Tropic Trooper可以搜索系统上运行的反病毒软件

en_text: Tropic Trooper has exfiltrated data using USB storage devices.
Text: Tropic Trooper利用USB存储设备渗出了数据

en_text: Tropic Trooper has collected information automatically using the adversary's USBferry attack.
Text: Tropic Trooper利用对手的USBferry攻击自动收集信息

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used a copy function to automatically exfiltrate sensitive data from air-gapped systems using USB storage.
Text: Tropic Trooper利用复制功能，从使用USB存储的空中封锁系统中自动渗出敏感数据

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used base64 encoding to hide command strings delivered from the C2.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用base64编码来隐藏从C2交付的命令字符串

en_text: Tropic Trooper used letmein to scan for saved usernames on the target system.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用letmein来扫描目标系统上保存的用户名

en_text: Tropic Trooper used netview to scan target systems for shared resources.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用netview来扫描目标系统的共享资源

en_text: Tropic Trooper used pr and an openly available tool to scan for open ports on target systems.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用pr和一个公开的工具来扫描目标系统上的开放端口

en_text: Tropic Trooper used shellcode with an XOR algorithm to decrypt a payload. Tropic Trooper also decrypted image files which contained a payload.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用带有XOR算法的shellcode来解密一个有效载荷

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used JPG files with encrypted payloads to mask their backdoor routines and evade detection.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用带有加密有效载荷的JPG文件来掩盖其后门程序并逃避检测

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used multiple Windows APIs including HttpInitialize, HttpCreateHttpHandle, and HttpAddUrl.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用了多个Windows API，包括HttpInitialize、HttpCreateHttpHandle和HttpAddUrl

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used scripts to collect the host's network topology.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用了脚本来收集主机的网络拓扑结构

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used a delivered trojan to download additional files.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用了一个已交付的木马程序来下载更多的文件

en_text: Tropic Trooper has tested if the localhost network is available and other connection capability on an infected system using command scripts.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用命令脚本测试了受感染系统上的localhost网络是否可用以及其他连接能力

en_text: Tropic Trooper has deleted dropper files on an infected system using command scripts.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用命令脚本删除了受感染系统中的dropper文件

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used known administrator account credentials to execute the backdoor directly.
Text: Tropic Trooper使用已知的管理员账户凭证直接执行后门

en_text: Tropic Trooper has attempted to transfer USBferry from an infected USB device by copying an Autorun function to the target machine.
Text: Tropic Trooper试图通过将自动运行功能复制到目标机器上，从受感染的USB设备上转移USBferry

en_text: Tropic Trooper has lured victims into executing malware via malicious e-mail attachments.
Text: Tropic Trooper通过恶意的电子邮件附件诱使受害者执行恶意软件。

en_text: Tropic Trooper has executed commands through Microsoft security vulnerabilities, including CVE-2017-11882, CVE-2018-0802, and CVE-2012-0158.
Text: Tropic Trooper通过微软的安全漏洞执行命令，包括CVE-2017-11882、CVE-2018-0802和CVE-2012-0158

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used Windows command scripts.
Text: Tropic Trooper已经使用了Windows命令脚本

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used SSL to connect to C2 servers.
Text: Tropic Trooper已使用SSL连接到C2服务器

en_text: Tropic Trooper has encrypted configuration files.
Text: Tropic Trooper有加密的配置文件

en_text: Tropic Trooper has encrypted traffic with the C2 to prevent network detection.
Text: Tropic Trooper与C2进行了加密通信，以防止网络检测

en_text: Tropic Trooper has created a hidden directory under C:\ProgramData\Apple\Updates\ and C:\Users\Public\Documents\Flash\.
Text: Tropic Trooper在C:\ProgramData\Apple\Updates\和C:\Users\Public\Documents\Flash\下创建了一个隐藏目录

en_text: Tropic Trooper has injected a DLL backdoor into dllhost.exe and svchost.exe.
Text: Tropic Trooper在dllhost.exe和svchost.exe中注入了一个DLL后门

en_text: Tropic Trooper has hidden payloads in Flash directories and fake installer files.
Text: Tropic Trooper在Flash目录和假安装文件中隐藏了有效载荷

en_text: Tropic Trooper has started a web service in the target host and wait for the adversary to connect, acting as a web shell.
Text: Tropic Trooper在目标主机上启动了一个网络服务，并等待对手的连接，充当网络外壳

en_text: Tropic Trooper has created shortcuts in the Startup folder to establish persistence.
Text: Tropic Trooper在启动文件夹中创建了快捷方式以建立持久性

en_text: Tropic Trooper has used HTTP in communication with the C2.
Text: Tropic Trooper在与C2的通信中使用了HTTP

en_text: Truvasys adds a Registry Run key to establish persistence.
Text: Truvasys添加了一个注册表运行键来建立持久性

en_text: TSCookie can multiple protocols including HTTP and HTTPS in communication with command and control (C2) servers.
Text: TSCookie可以多种协议，包括HTTP和HTTPS，与指挥和控制（C2）服务器通信

en_text: TSCookie can use ICMP to receive information on the destination server.
Text: TSCookie可以使用ICMP来接收目标服务器的信息

en_text: TSCookie has been executed via malicious links embedded in e-mails spoofing the Ministries of Education, Culture, Sports, Science and Technology of Japan.
Text: TSCookie通过嵌入在欺骗日本教育、文化、体育、科学和技术部的电子邮件中的恶意链接被执行

en_text: TSCookie has encrypted network communications with RC4.
Text: TSCookie用RC4加密了网络通信

en_text: TSCookie has the ability to steal saved passwords from the Internet Explorer, Edge, Firefox, and Chrome browsers.
Text: TSCookie有能力从Internet Explorer、Edge、Firefox和Chrome浏览器中窃取保存的密码

en_text: TSCookie has the ability to proxy communications with command and control (C2) servers.
Text: TSCookie有能力代理与指挥和控制（C2）服务器的通信

en_text: TSCookie has the ability to discover drive information on the infected host.
Text: TSCookie有能力发现被感染主机上的驱动器信息

en_text: TSCookie has the ability to decrypt, load, and execute a DLL and its resources.
Text: TSCookie有能力解密、加载和执行一个DLL及其资源

en_text: TSCookie has the ability to list processes on the infected host.
Text: TSCookie有能力列出受感染主机上的进程

en_text: TSCookie has the ability to identify the IP of the infected host.
Text: TSCookie有能力识别受感染主机的IP

en_text: TSCookie has the ability to inject code into the svchost.exe, iexplorer.exe, explorer.exe, and default browser processes.
Text: TSCookie有能力向svchost.exe、iexplorer.exe、explorer.exe和默认浏览器进程注入代码

en_text: TSCookie has the ability to upload and download files to and from the infected host.
Text: TSCookie有能力向受感染的主机上传和下载文件

en_text: TSCookie has the ability to execute shell commands on the infected host.
Text: TSCookie有能力在受感染的主机上执行外壳命令

en_text: Turla RPC backdoors have included local UPnP RPC proxies.
Text: Turla RPC后门包括本地UPnP RPC代理

en_text: Turla RPC backdoors can collect files from USB thumb drives.
Text: Turla RPC后门可以从USB拇指驱动器收集文件

en_text: Turla RPC backdoors can upload files from victim machines.
Text: Turla RPC后门可以从受害者机器上传文件

en_text: Turla RPC backdoors can impersonate or steal process tokens before executing commands.
Text: Turla RPC后门可以在执行命令前冒充或窃取进程令牌

en_text: Turla RPC backdoors can be used to transfer files to/from victim machines on the local network.
Text: Turla RPC后门可用于将文件传输到 Turla RPC后门可以用来将文件传输到 Turla RPC后门可用于将文件传输至 Turla RPC后门可用于将文件传送到

en_text: Turla RPC backdoors have used cmd.exe to execute commands.
Text: Turla RPC后门已经使用cmd.exe来执行命令

en_text: Turla has used WebDAV to upload stolen USB files to a cloud drive. Turla has also exfiltrated stolen files to OneDrive and 4shared.
Text: Turla曾使用WebDAV将被盗的USB文件上传到云驱动器

en_text: Turla has also used PowerSploit's Invoke-ReflectivePEInjection.ps1 to reflectively load a PowerShell payload into a random process on the victim system.
Text: Turla还使用PowerSploit的Invoke-ReflectivePEInjection.ps1来反射性地将PowerShell有效载荷加载到受害者系统上的一个随机进程

en_text: Turla has obtained information on security software, including security logging information that may indicate whether their malware has been detected.
Text: Turla获得了安全软件的信息，包括可能表明其恶意软件是否被检测到的安全日志信息

en_text: Turla and its RPC backdoors have used APIs calls for various tasks related to subverting AMSI and accessing then executing commands through RPC and/or named pipes.
Text: Turla及其RPC后门使用API调用进行各种与颠覆AMSI有关的任务，通过RPC和RPC访问然后执行命令

en_text: Turla may attempt to connect to systems within a victim's network using net use commands and a predefined list or collection of passwords.
Text: Turla可能试图使用网络使用命令和预定义的密码列表或集合连接到受害者网络内的系统

en_text: Turla has used spearphishing emails to deliver BrainTest as a malicious attachment.
Text: Turla利用鱼叉式网络钓鱼邮件将BrainTest作为一个恶意附件发送

en_text: Turla has used the Registry to store encrypted payloads.
Text: Turla利用注册表来存储加密的有效载荷

en_text: Turla has used fsutil fsinfo drives to list connected drives.
Text: Turla使用fsutil fsinfo drives来列出连接的驱动器

en_text: Turla has used Metasploit to perform reflective DLL injection in order to escalate privileges.
Text: Turla使用Metasploit进行反射性DLL注入，以提升权限

en_text: Turla has used net localgroup and net localgroup Administrators to enumerate group information, including members of the local administrators group.
Text: Turla使用net localgroup和net localgroup Administrators来列举组信息，包括本地管理员组的成员

en_text: Turla has used net user to enumerate local accounts on the system.
Text: Turla使用net user来列举系统中的本地账户

en_text: Turla used net use commands to connect to lateral systems within a network.
Text: Turla使用net使用命令来连接网络中的横向系统

en_text: Turla has used PowerShell profiles to maintain persistence on an infected machine.
Text: Turla使用PowerShell配置文件在被感染的机器上保持持久性

en_text: Turla has used encryption (including salted 3DES via PowerSploit's Out-EncryptedScript.ps1), random variable names, and base64 encoding to obfuscate PowerShell commands and payloads.
Text: Turla使用加密（包括通过PowerSploit的Out-EncryptedScript.ps1的盐化3DES）、随机变量名称和base64编码来混淆PowerShell命令和有效载荷

en_text: Turla has used valid digital certificates from Sysprint AG to sign its Epic dropper.
Text: Turla使用来自Sysprint AG的有效数字证书来签署其Epic dropper

en_text: Turla has used PowerShell to execute commands/scripts, in some cases via a custom executable or code from Empire's PSInject. Turla has also used PowerShell scripts to load and execute malware in memory.
Text: Turla使用了PowerShell来执行命令 Turla使用了PowerShell来执行指令 Turla使用PowerShell来执行命令 Turla已经使用PowerShell执行命令

en_text: Turla has used net group "Domain Admins" /domain to identify domain administrators.
Text: Turla使用了网组 "域名管理员"

en_text: Turla has used a custom .NET tool to collect documents from an organization's internal central database.
Text: Turla使用了一个定制的.NET工具，从一个组织的内部中央数据库收集文件

en_text: Turla has used a custom decryption routine, which pulls key and salt values from other artifacts such as a WMI filter or PowerShell Profile, to decode encrypted PowerShell payloads.
Text: Turla使用了一个自定义的解密程序，它从其他工件（如WMI过滤器或PowerShell Profile）中提取密钥和盐值，以解码加密的PowerShell有效载荷

en_text: Turla attempted to trick targets into clicking on a link featuring a seemingly legitimate domain from Adobe.com to download their malware and gain initial access.
Text: Turla试图诱使目标点击一个具有Adobe.com的看似合法域名的链接，下载他们的恶意软件并获得初始访问权

en_text: Turla has used spearphishing via a link to get users to download and run their malware.
Text: Turla通过链接使用鱼叉式钓鱼，让用户下载并运行他们的恶意软件

en_text: Turla established persistence by adding a Shell value under the Registry key HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion]Winlogon.
Text: Turla通过在注册表键HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion]Winlogon下添加一个Shell值来建立持久性

en_text: Turla has gathered credentials from the Windows Credential Manager tool.
Text: Turla已经从Windows凭证管理器工具中收集了凭证

en_text: Turla has used HTTP and HTTPS for C2 communications.
Text: Turla已经使用HTTP和HTTPS进行C2通信

en_text: Turla has used WMI event filters and consumers to establish persistence.
Text: Turla已经使用WMI事件过滤器和消费者来建立持久性

en_text: Turla has used net accounts and net accounts /domain to acquire password policy information.
Text: Turla已经使用了净账户和净账户 Turla使用了净账户和净账户 图拉使用了净账户和净账户 Turla使用了净值账户和净值账户

en_text: Turla has used net user /domain to enumerate domain accounts.
Text: Turla已经使用了网友 Turla使用了网友 图拉使用了网友 Turla已经使用了网友的

en_text: Turla has used a AMSI bypass, which patches the in-memory amsi.dll, in PowerShell scripts to bypass Windows antimalware products.
Text: Turla在PowerShell脚本中使用了一个AMSI旁路，即修补内存中的amsi.dll，以绕过Windows反恶意软件产品

en_text: Turla surveys a system upon check-in to discover remote systems on a local network using the net view and net view /DOMAIN commands. Turla has also used net group "Domain Computers" /domain, net group "Domain Controllers" /domain, and net group "Exchange Servers" /domain to enumerate domain computers, including the organization's DC and Exchange Server.
Text: Turla在签到时调查系统，使用net view和net view /DOMAIN命令发现本地网络上的远程系统。Turla还使用net group "Domain Computers" /domain、net group "Domain Controllers" /domain和net group "Exchange Servers" /domain来列举域计算机，包括该组织的DC和Exchange服务器。

en_text: Turla surveys a system upon check-in to discover running processes using the tasklist /v command. Turla RPC backdoors have also enumerated processes associated with specific open ports or named pipes.
Text: Turla在签入时调查系统，使用任务列表/v命令发现正在运行的进程。Turla RPC后门还列举了与特定开放端口或命名管道相关的进程。

en_text: Turla surveys a system upon check-in to discover running services and associated processes using the tasklist /svc command.
Text: Turla在签到时调查系统，以发现正在运行的服务和使用任务列表的相关进程

en_text: Turla surveys a system upon check-in to discover information in the Windows Registry with the reg query command. Turla has also retrieved PowerShell payloads hidden in Registry keys as well as checking keys associated with null session named pipes .
Text: Turla在签到时调查系统，用reg查询命令发现Windows注册表中的信息。Turla还检索了隐藏在注册表键中的PowerShell有效载荷，以及检查与名为管道的空会话相关的键。

en_text: Turla surveys a system upon check-in to discover files in specific locations on the hard disk %TEMP% directory, the current user's desktop, the Program Files directory, and Recent. Turla RPC backdoors have also searched for files matching the lPH*.dll pattern.
Text: Turla在签入时调查系统，发现硬盘%TEMP%目录、当前用户的桌面、Program Files目录和Recent等特定位置的文件。Turla RPC后门还搜索符合lPH*.dll模式的文件。

en_text: Turla surveys a system upon check-in to discover network configuration details using the arp -a, nbtstat -n, nbtscan, net config, ipconfig /all, and route commands. Turla RPC backdoors have also retrieved registered RPC interface information from process memory.
Text: Turla在签入时调查系统，使用arp -a、nbtstat -n、nbtscan、net config、ipconfig /all和route命令发现网络配置细节。Turla RPC后门还从进程内存中检索注册的RPC接口信息。

en_text: Turla surveys a system upon check-in to discover active local network connections using the netstat -an, net use, net file, and net session commands. Turla RPC backdoors have also enumerated the IPv4 TCP connection table via the GetTcpTable2 API call.
Text: Turla在签入时调查系统，使用netstat -an、net use、net file和net session命令发现活跃的本地网络连接。Turla RPC后门还通过GetTcpTable2 API调用列举了IPv4 TCP连接表。

en_text: Turla surveys a system upon check-in to discover operating system configuration details using the systeminfo, gpresult, and set commands.
Text: Turla在签入时调查系统，使用systeminfo、gpresult和set命令发现操作系统的配置细节

en_text: Turla surveys a system upon check-in to discover the system time by using the net time command.
Text: Turla在签入时调查系统，通过使用net time命令发现系统时间

en_text: Turla has encrypted files stolen from connected USB drives into a RAR file before exfiltration.
Text: Turla在渗出前将从连接的USB驱动器中窃取的文件加密成一个RAR文件

en_text: Turla has used shellcode to download Meterpreter after compromising a victim.
Text: Turla在危害受害者后使用shellcode下载Meterpreter

en_text: Turla has used VBS scripts throughout its operations.
Text: Turla在整个运营过程中使用了VBS脚本

en_text: TURNEDUP is capable of creating a reverse shell.
Text: TURNEDUP能够创建一个反向外壳

en_text: TURNEDUP is capable of injecting code into the APC queue of a created Rundll32 process as part of an "Early Bird injection."
Text: TURNEDUP能够将代码注入创建的Rundll32进程的APC队列中，作为 "早鸟注入 "的一部分

en_text: TURNEDUP is capable of taking screenshots.
Text: TURNEDUP能够拍摄屏幕截图

en_text: TURNEDUP is capable of gathering system information.
Text: TURNEDUP能够收集系统信息

en_text: TURNEDUP is capable of downloading additional files.
Text: TURNEDUP能够下载其他文件

en_text: TURNEDUP is capable of writing to a Registry Run key to establish.
Text: TURNEDUP能够写入注册表运行键，建立

en_text: TYPEFRAME variants can add malicious DLL modules as new services.TYPEFRAME can also delete services from the victim’s machine.
Text: TYPEFRAME变种可以添加恶意的DLL模块作为新的服务。TYPEFRAME还可以从受害者的机器上删除服务。

en_text: TYPEFRAME has used ports 443, 8080, and 8443 with a FakeTLS method.
Text: TYPEFRAME采用了FakeTLS方法，使用了443、8080和8443端口

en_text: TYPEFRAME can open the Windows Firewall on the victim’s machine to allow incoming connections.
Text: TYPEFRAME可以打开受害者机器上的Windows防火墙，允许传入连接

en_text: TYPEFRAME can delete files off the system.
Text: TYPEFRAME可以删除系统中的文件

en_text: TYPEFRAME can uninstall malware components using a batch script. TYPEFRAME can execute commands using a shell.
Text: TYPEFRAME可以使用批处理脚本卸载恶意软件组件

en_text: TYPEFRAME can gather the disk volume information.
Text: TYPEFRAME可以收集磁盘卷信息

en_text: TYPEFRAME can upload and download files to the victim’s machine.
Text: TYPEFRAME可以向受害者的机器上传和下载文件

en_text: TYPEFRAME can search directories for files on the victim’s machine.
Text: TYPEFRAME可以在受害者的机器上搜索目录中的文件

en_text: TYPEFRAME can install encrypted configuration data under the Registry key HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\ShellCompatibility\Applications\laxhost.dll and HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\PrintConfigs.
Text: TYPEFRAME可以在注册表键HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\MicrosoftWindows\CurrentVersion\ShellCompatibility\Applications\laxhost.dll和HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\MicrosoftWindows\CurrentVersion\PrintConfigs之下安装加密的配置数据

en_text: TYPEFRAME has used a malicious Word document for delivery with VBA macros for execution.
Text: TYPEFRAME使用了一个带有VBA宏的恶意Word文档进行传递，以执行

en_text: UACMe contains many methods for bypassing Windows User Account Control on multiple versions of the operating system.
Text: UACMe包含许多绕过多个版本操作系统的Windows用户账户控制的方法

en_text: UBoatRAT checks for virtualization software such as VMWare, VirtualBox, or QEmu on the compromised machine.
Text: UBoatRAT检查被攻击机器上的虚拟化软件，如VMWare、VirtualBox或QEmu

en_text: UBoatRAT can list running processes on the system.
Text: UBoatRAT可以列出系统上的运行进程

en_text: UBoatRAT can start a command shell.
Text: UBoatRAT可以启动一个命令外壳

en_text: UBoatRAT can upload and download files to the victim’s machine.
Text: UBoatRAT可以向受害者的机器上传和下载文件

en_text: UBoatRAT takes advantage of the /SetNotifyCmdLine option in BITSAdmin to ensure it stays running on a system to maintain persistence.
Text: UBoatRAT利用了 UBoatRAT利用了以下优势 UBoatRAT利用的是 UBoatRAT充分利用了

en_text: UBoatRAT encrypts instructions in the payload using a simple XOR cipher.
Text: UBoatRAT使用一个简单的XOR密码对有效载荷中的指令进行加密

en_text: UBoatRAT has used GitHub and a public blog service in Hong Kong for C2 communications.
Text: UBoatRAT已经使用GitHub和香港的公共博客服务进行C2通信

en_text: UBoatRAT has used HTTP for C2 communications.
Text: UBoatRAT已经使用HTTP进行C2通信

en_text: Umbreon creates valid local users to provide access to the system.
Text: Umbreon创建有效的本地用户以提供对系统的访问

en_text: Umbreon provides additional access using its backdoor Espeon, providing a reverse shell upon receipt of a special packet.
Text: Umbreon利用其后门Espeon提供额外的访问，在收到一个特殊的数据包后提供一个反向外壳

en_text: Umbreon provides access using both standard facilities like SSH and additional access using its backdoor Espeon, providing a reverse shell upon receipt of a special packet
Text: Umbreon提供了使用SSH等标准设施的访问，以及使用其后门Espeon的额外访问，在收到一个特殊的数据包后提供一个反向外壳

en_text: Umbreon provides access to the system via SSH or any other protocol that uses PAM to authenticate.
Text: Umbreon提供通过SSH或任何其他使用PAM进行验证的协议来访问系统

en_text: Umbreon hides from defenders by hooking libc function calls, hiding artifacts that would reveal its presence, such as the user account it creates to provide access and undermining strace, a tool often used to identify malware.
Text: Umbreon通过钩住libc函数调用来躲避防御者，隐藏会暴露其存在的人工制品，如它创建的用户账户提供访问，并破坏strace（一种经常用于识别恶意软件的工具）

en_text: Some versions of UPPERCUT have used the hard-coded string "this is the encrypt key" for Blowfish encryption when communicating with a C2. Later versions have hard-coded keys uniquely for each C2 address.
Text: UPPERCUT的一些版本在与C2通信时使用硬编码的字符串 "这是加密密钥 "进行Blowfish加密。后来的版本对每个C2地址都有独特的硬编码密钥。

en_text: UPPERCUT can capture desktop screenshots in the PNG format and send them to the C2 server.
Text: UPPERCUT可以捕获PNG格式的桌面截图，并将其发送到C2服务器

en_text: UPPERCUT can download and upload files to and from the victim’s machine.
Text: UPPERCUT可以从受害者的机器上下载和上传文件

en_text: UPPERCUT uses cmd.exe to execute commands on the victim’s machine.
Text: UPPERCUT使用cmd.exe在受害者的机器上执行命令

en_text: UPPERCUT has used HTTP for C2, including sending error codes in Cookie headers.
Text: UPPERCUT已将HTTP用于C2，包括在Cookie头中发送错误代码

en_text: UPPERCUT has the capability to collect the current logged on user’s username from a machine.
Text: UPPERCUT有能力从一台机器上收集当前登录的用户的用户名

en_text: UPPERCUT has the capability to obtain the time zone information and current timestamp of the victim’s machine.
Text: UPPERCUT有能力获得受害者机器的时区信息和当前时间戳。

en_text: UPPERCUT has the capability to gather the victim's proxy information.
Text: UPPERCUT有能力收集受害者的代理信息

en_text: UPPERCUT has the capability to gather the victim's current directory.
Text: UPPERCUT有能力收集受害者的当前目录

en_text: UPPERCUT has the capability to gather the system’s hostname and OS version.
Text: UPPERCUT有能力收集系统的主机名和操作系统版本

en_text: Uroburos uses a custom packer.
Text: Uroburos使用一个定制的包装器

en_text: Uroburos is a rootkit used by Turla.
Text: Uroburos是Turla使用的一个rootkit

en_text: Ursnif has injected HTML codes into banking sites to steal sensitive online banking information (ex: usernames and passwords).
Text: Ursnif将HTML代码注入银行网站，窃取敏感的网上银行信息（例如：用户名和密码）

en_text: Ursnif has dropped payload and configuration files to disk. Ursnif has also been used to download and execute additional payloads.
Text: Ursnif将有效载荷和配置文件丢到磁盘上。Ursnif还被用来下载和执行其他有效载荷。

en_text: Ursnif has used Registry modifications as part of its installation routine.
Text: Ursnif将注册表的修改作为其安装程序的一部分

en_text: Ursnif has used crypto key information stored in the Registry to decrypt Tor clients dropped to disk.
Text: Ursnif利用存储在注册表中的加密密钥信息来解密掉在磁盘上的Tor客户端

en_text: Ursnif has used Registry Run keys to establish automatic execution at system startup.
Text: Ursnif利用注册表运行键来建立系统启动时的自动执行

en_text: Ursnif has used a DGA to generate domain names for C2.
Text: Ursnif使用DGA为C2生成域名

en_text: Ursnif has used HTTP POSTs to exfil gathered information.
Text: Ursnif使用HTTP POSTs来渗出收集的信息

en_text: Ursnif has used Reg to query the Registry for installed programs.
Text: Ursnif使用Reg来查询注册表中的安装程序

en_text: Ursnif has used Systeminfo to gather system information.
Text: Ursnif使用Systeminfo来收集系统信息

en_text: Ursnif has used tmp files to stage gathered information.
Text: Ursnif使用tmp文件来存放收集的信息

en_text: Ursnif has used strings from legitimate system files and existing folders for its file, folder, and Registry entry names.
Text: Ursnif使用合法系统文件和现有文件夹的字符串作为其文件、文件夹和注册表项的名称

en_text: Ursnif has used CreateProcessW to create child processes.
Text: Ursnif使用了CreateProcessW来创建子进程

en_text: Ursnif has used a peer-to-peer (P2P) network for C2.
Text: Ursnif使用了点对点（P2P）网络进行C2

en_text: Ursnif has used hooked APIs to take screenshots.
Text: Ursnif使用了挂钩的API来拍摄屏幕截图

en_text: Ursnif has used process hollowing to inject into child processes.
Text: Ursnif使用了进程空心化来注入到子进程中

en_text: Ursnif has used an XOR-based algorithm to encrypt Tor clients dropped to disk. Ursnif droppers have also been delivered as password-protected zip files that execute base64 encoded PowerShell commands.
Text: Ursnif使用一种基于XOR的算法来加密投放到磁盘的Tor客户端。Ursnif的投放者也被当作密码保护的压缩文件，执行base64编码的PowerShell命令。

en_text: Ursnif has collected files from victim machines, including certificates and cookies.
Text: Ursnif收集了受害者机器上的文件，包括证书和cookies

en_text: Ursnif has gathered information about running processes.
Text: Ursnif收集了有关运行进程的信息

en_text: Ursnif has injected code into target processes via thread local storage callbacks.
Text: Ursnif通过线程本地存储回调将代码注入目标进程

en_text: Ursnif droppers have used COM objects to execute the malware's full executable payload.
Text: Ursnif投放器使用COM对象来执行恶意软件的全部可执行有效载荷

en_text: Ursnif droppers have used COM properties to execute malware in hidden windows.
Text: Ursnif投放者利用COM属性在隐藏窗口中执行恶意软件

en_text: Ursnif droppers have used VBA macros to download and execute the malware's full executable payload.
Text: Ursnif投放者使用VBA宏来下载和执行恶意软件的完整可执行有效载荷

en_text: Ursnif droppers have used WMI classes to execute PowerShell commands.
Text: Ursnif投放者已经使用WMI类来执行PowerShell命令

en_text: Ursnif droppers have used PowerShell in download cradles to download and execute the malware's full executable payload.
Text: Ursnif投放者在下载摇篮中使用PowerShell来下载和执行该恶意软件的完整可执行有效载荷

en_text: Ursnif has used HTTPS for C2.
Text: Ursnif已将HTTPS用于C2

en_text: Ursnif has copied itself to and infected removable drives for propagation.
Text: Ursnif已将自己复制到并感染了可移动驱动器进行传播

en_text: Ursnif has copied itself to and infected files in network drives for propagation.
Text: Ursnif已将自己复制到并感染了网络驱动器中的文件，以便传播

en_text: Ursnif has used Tor for C2.
Text: Ursnif已经将Tor用于C2

en_text: Ursnif has gathered information about running services.
Text: Ursnif已经收集了有关运行服务的信息

en_text: Ursnif has registered itself as a system service in the Registry for automatic execution at system startup.
Text: Ursnif已经在注册表中将自己注册为系统服务，以便在系统启动时自动执行

en_text: Ursnif has hooked APIs to perform a wide variety of information theft, such as monitoring traffic from browsers.
Text: Ursnif有挂钩的API来执行各种信息窃取，如监测浏览器的流量

en_text: Ursnif has used encoded data in HTTP URLs for C2.
Text: Ursnif在HTTP URLs中使用编码数据进行C2

en_text: Ursnif has deleted data staged in tmp files after exfiltration.
Text: Ursnif在渗透后删除了缓存在tmp文件中的数据

en_text: Ursnif has used a 30 minute delay after execution to evade sandbox monitoring tools.
Text: Ursnif在执行后使用了30分钟的延迟，以躲避沙盒监控工具

en_text: USBferry can detect the victim's file or folder list.
Text: USBferry可以检测受害者的文件或文件夹列表

en_text: USBferry can check for connected USB devices.
Text: USBferry可以检查连接的USB设备

en_text: USBferry can copy its installer to attached USB storage devices.
Text: USBferry可以将其安装程序复制到连接的USB存储设备

en_text: USBferry can detect the infected machine's network topology using ipconfig and arp.
Text: USBferry可以使用ipconfig和arp检测被感染机器的网络拓扑结构

en_text: USBferry can use net view to gather information about remote systems.
Text: USBferry可以使用net view来收集远程系统的信息

en_text: USBferry can use netstat and nbtstat to detect active network connections.
Text: USBferry可以使用netstat和nbtstat来检测活动的网络连接

en_text: USBferry can use net user to gather information about local accounts.
Text: USBferry可以使用net用户来收集本地账户的信息

en_text: USBferry can use tasklist to gather information about the process running on the infected system.
Text: USBferry可以使用任务列表来收集受感染系统上运行的进程信息

en_text: USBferry can collect information from an air-gapped host machine.
Text: USBferry可以收集来自空气加压主机的信息

en_text: USBferry can execute rundll32.exe in memory to avoid detection.
Text: USBferry可以在内存中执行rundll32.exe以逃避检测

en_text: USBferry can execute various Windows commands.
Text: USBferry可以执行各种Windows命令

en_text: USBStealer collects files matching certain criteria from the victim and stores them in a local directory for later exfiltration.
Text: USBStealer从受害者那里收集符合某些标准的文件，并将它们存储在本地目录中，以便以后渗出

en_text: USBStealer monitors victims for insertion of removable drives. When dropped onto a second victim, it also enumerates drives connected to the system.
Text: USBStealer监控受害者是否插入了可移动驱动器。当投放到第二个受害者身上时，它也会列举连接到系统的驱动器。

en_text: USBStealer drops commands for a second victim onto a removable media drive inserted into the first victim, and commands are executed when the drive is inserted into the second victim.
Text: USBStealer将第二个受害者的命令放到插入第一个受害者的可移动媒体驱动器上，当该驱动器被插入第二个受害者时，命令被执行

en_text: USBStealer sets the timestamps of its dropper files to the last-access and last-write timestamps of a standard Windows library chosen on the system.
Text: USBStealer将其dropper文件的时间戳设置为系统上选择的标准Windows库的最后访问和最后写入的时间戳

en_text: USBStealer drops itself onto removable media and relies on Autorun to execute the malicious file when a user opens the removable media on another system.
Text: USBStealer将自己放置在可移动媒体上，当用户在另一个系统上打开可移动媒体时，依靠Autorun来执行恶意文件

en_text: USBStealer registers itself under a Registry Run key with the name "USB Disk Security."
Text: USBStealer将自己注册在一个名为 "USB Disk Security "的注册表运行键下

en_text: USBStealer mimics a legitimate Russian program called USB Disk Security.
Text: USBStealer模仿了一个名为USB Disk Security的俄罗斯合法程序

en_text: USBStealer searches victim drives for files matching certain extensions (".skr",".pkr" or ".key") or names.
Text: USBStealer搜索受害者的驱动器，寻找与某些扩展名（".skr"、".pkr "或".key"）或名称相匹配的文件

en_text: USBStealer exfiltrates collected files via removable media from air-gapped victims.
Text: USBStealer通过可移动媒体从被空中封锁的受害者那里渗出收集的文件

en_text: USBStealer has several commands to delete files associated with the malware from the victim.
Text: USBStealer有几个命令可以从受害者身上删除与恶意软件相关的文件

en_text: USBStealer automatically exfiltrates collected files via removable media when an infected device is connected to the second victim after receiving commands from the first victim.
Text: USBStealer在收到第一个受害者的命令后，当受感染的设备连接到第二个受害者时，会自动通过可移动媒体渗出收集的文件

en_text: Most strings in USBStealer are encrypted using 3DES and XOR and reversed.
Text: USBStealer中的大多数字符串都是用3DES和XOR加密的，并进行反转

en_text: Valak has the ability to decode and decrypt downloaded files.
Text: Valak具有解码和解密下载文件的能力

en_text: Valak has the ability to enumerate local admin accounts.
Text: Valak具有列举本地管理账户的能力

en_text: Valak has the ability to enumerate domain admin accounts.
Text: Valak具有列举域管理账户的能力

en_text: Valak can collect sensitive mailing information from Exchange servers, including credentials and the domain certificate of an enterprise.
Text: Valak可以从Exchange服务器上收集敏感的邮件信息，包括企业的凭证和域名证书

en_text: Valak can determine the Windows version and computer name on a compromised host.
Text: Valak可以确定被攻击主机上的Windows版本和计算机名称

en_text: Valak can determine if a compromised host has security products installed.
Text: Valak可以确定一个被破坏的主机是否安装了安全产品

en_text: Valak can use the clientgrabber module to steal e-mail credentials from the Registry.
Text: Valak可以使用clientgrabber模块从注册处窃取电子邮件凭证

en_text: Valak can use a .NET compiled module named exchgrabber to enumerate credentials from the Credential Manager.
Text: Valak可以使用一个名为exchgrabber的.NET编译模块来列举来自凭证管理器的凭证

en_text: Valak can use the Registry for code updates and to collect credentials.
Text: Valak可以使用注册表进行代码更新和收集凭证

en_text: Valak can gather information regarding the user.
Text: Valak可以收集有关用户的信息

en_text: Valak can execute tasks via OLE.
Text: Valak可以通过OLE执行任务

en_text: Valak can communicate over multiple C2 hosts.
Text: Valak可以通过多个C2主机进行通信

en_text: Valak can download additional modules and malware capable of using separate C2 channels.
Text: Valak可以下载额外的模块和恶意软件，能够使用单独的C2通道

en_text: Valak can download a module to search for and build a report of harvested credential data.
Text: Valak可以下载一个模块来搜索并建立一个收获的凭证数据报告

en_text: Valak can use wmic process call create in a scheduled task to launch plugins and for execution.
Text: Valak可以在计划任务中使用wmic进程调用创建来启动插件并进行执行

en_text: Valak can execute JavaScript containing configuration data for establishing persistence.
Text: Valak可以执行包含配置数据的JavaScript，以建立持久性

en_text: Valak has used scheduled tasks to execute additional payloads and to gain persistence on a compromised host.
Text: Valak利用计划任务来执行额外的有效载荷，并在被攻击的主机上获得持久性

en_text: Valak has used PowerShell to download additional modules.
Text: Valak使用PowerShell下载了额外的模块

en_text: Valak has used regsvr32.exe to launch malicious DLLs.
Text: Valak使用regsvr32.exe来启动恶意的DLLs

en_text: Valak has been delivered via spearphishing e-mails with password protected ZIP files.
Text: Valak是通过带有密码保护的ZIP文件的鱼叉式网络钓鱼电子邮件发送的

en_text: Valak has been delivered via malicious links in e-mail.
Text: Valak是通过电子邮件中的恶意链接传递的

en_text: Valak has been executed via Microsoft Word documents containing malicious macros.
Text: Valak是通过含有恶意宏的微软Word文档执行的

en_text: Valak has downloaded a variety of modules and payloads to the compromised host, including IcedID and NetSupport Manager RAT-based malware.
Text: Valak向被攻击的主机下载了各种模块和有效载荷，包括基于IcedID和NetSupport Manager RAT的恶意软件

en_text: Valak has returned C2 data as encoded ASCII.
Text: Valak已将C2数据作为编码的ASCII返回

en_text: Valak has used packed DLL payloads.
Text: Valak已经使用了打包的DLL有效载荷

en_text: Valak has the ability to base64 encode and XOR encrypt strings.
Text: Valak有对字符串进行base64编码和XOR加密的能力

en_text: Valak has the ability save and execute files as alternate data streams (ADS).
Text: Valak有能力将文件作为备用数据流（ADS）保存和执行

en_text: Valak has the ability to enumerate running processes on a compromised host.
Text: Valak有能力列举被入侵主机上的运行进程

en_text: Valak has the ability to identify the domain and the MAC and IP addresses of an infected machine.
Text: Valak有能力识别受感染机器的域名、MAC和IP地址

en_text: Valak has the ability to modify the Registry key HKCU\Software\ApplicationContainer\Appsw64 to store information regarding the C2 server and downloads.
Text: Valak有能力修改注册表键HKCU\Software\ApplicationContainer\Appsw64，以存储有关C2服务器和下载的信息

en_text: Valak has the ability to take screenshots on a compromised host.
Text: Valak有能力在被入侵的主机上进行屏幕截图

en_text: Valak has used HTTP in communications with C2.
Text: Valak在与C2的通信中使用了HTTP

en_text: Vasport copies itself to disk and creates an associated run key Registry entry to establish.
Text: Vasport将自己复制到磁盘上，并创建一个相关的运行键注册表条目来建立

en_text: Vasport can download files.
Text: Vasport可以下载文件

en_text: Vasport is capable of tunneling though a proxy.
Text: Vasport能够通过代理进行隧道传输

en_text: Vasport creates a backdoor by making a connection using a HTTP POST.
Text: Vasport通过使用HTTP POST进行连接来创建一个后门

en_text: VBShower has the ability to execute VBScript files.
Text: VBShower具有执行VBScript文件的能力

en_text: VBShower used HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\[a-f0-9A-F]{{8}} to maintain persistence.
Text: VBShower使用HKCUSoftware\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\[a-f0-9A-F]{{8}}来维护持久性

en_text: VBShower has attempted to obtain a VBS script from command and control (C2) nodes over HTTP.
Text: VBShower试图通过HTTP从命令和控制（C2）节点获得一个VBS脚本

en_text: VBShower has attempted to complicate forensic analysis by deleting all the files contained in %APPDATA%..\Local\Temporary Internet Files\Content.Word and %APPDATA%..\Local Settings\Temporary Internet Files\Content.Word\.
Text: VBShower试图通过删除%APPDATA%.\Local\Temporary Internet Files\Content.Word和%APPDATA%.\Local Settings\Temporary Internet Files\Content.Word\中包含的所有文件来使取证分析复杂化

en_text: VBShower has the ability to download VBS files to the target computer.
Text: VBShower有能力将VBS文件下载到目标计算机

en_text: VERMIN gathers the username from the victim’s machine.
Text: VERMIN从受害者的机器上收集用户名

en_text: VERMIN decrypts code, strings, and commands to use once it's on the victim's machine.
Text: VERMIN对代码、字符串和命令进行解密，以便在受害者的机器上使用

en_text: VERMIN can perform screen captures of the victim’s machine.
Text: VERMIN可以对受害者的机器进行屏幕抓拍

en_text: VERMIN can get a list of the processes and running tasks on the system.
Text: VERMIN可以获得系统中的进程和运行任务的列表

en_text: VERMIN can perform audio capture.
Text: VERMIN可以进行音频采集

en_text: VERMIN can delete files on the victim’s machine.
Text: VERMIN可以删除受害者机器上的文件

en_text: VERMIN can download and upload files to the victim's machine.
Text: VERMIN可以下载和上传文件到受害者的机器

en_text: VERMIN encrypts the collected files using 3-DES.
Text: VERMIN使用3-DES对收集的文件进行加密

en_text: VERMIN uses HTTP for C2 communications.
Text: VERMIN使用HTTP进行C2通信

en_text: VERMIN uses WMI to check for anti-virus software installed on the system.
Text: VERMIN使用WMI来检查系统上安装的反病毒软件

en_text: VERMIN is obfuscated using the obfuscation tool called ConfuserEx.
Text: VERMIN是使用名为ConfuserEx的混淆工具进行混淆的

en_text: VERMIN collects the OS name, machine name, and architecture information.
Text: VERMIN收集操作系统名称、机器名称和架构信息

en_text: VERMIN collects data stored in the clipboard.
Text: VERMIN收集存储在剪贴板上的数据

en_text: VERMIN gathers the local IP address.
Text: VERMIN收集了本地的IP地址

en_text: VERMIN collects keystrokes from the victim machine.
Text: VERMIN收集受害者机器上的按键信息

en_text: VERMIN saves each collected file with the automatically generated format {{0:dd-MM-yyyy}}.txt .
Text: VERMIN以自动生成的格式{{0:dd-MM-yyyy}}.txt保存每个收集的文件

en_text: VERMIN is initially packed.
Text: VERMIN最初被包装

en_text: Volgmer checks the system for certain Registry keys.
Text: Volgmer检查系统的某些注册表键

en_text: Volgmer stores the encoded configuration file in the Registry key HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\WMI\Security.
Text: Volgmer将编码后的配置文件存储在注册表键HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\ControlWMI\Security

en_text: Volgmer can gather the IP address from the victim's machine.
Text: Volgmer可以从受害者的机器上收集IP地址

en_text: Volgmer can gather system information, the computer name, OS version, drive and serial information from the victim's machine.
Text: Volgmer可以从受害者的机器上收集系统信息、计算机名称、操作系统版本、驱动器和序列信息

en_text: Volgmer can list directories on a victim.
Text: Volgmer可以列出受害者的目录

en_text: Volgmer can gather information about TCP connection state.
Text: Volgmer可以收集关于TCP连接状态的信息

en_text: Volgmer can download remote files and additional payloads to the victim's machine.
Text: Volgmer可以下载远程文件和额外的有效载荷到受害者的机器上

en_text: Volgmer can execute commands on the victim's machine.
Text: Volgmer可以在受害者的机器上执行命令

en_text: Volgmer executes payloads using the Windows API call CreateProcessW().
Text: Volgmer使用Windows API调用CreateProcessW()来执行有效载荷

en_text: Volgmer uses a simple XOR cipher to encrypt traffic and files.
Text: Volgmer使用一个简单的XOR密码来加密流量和文件

en_text: Volgmer deobfuscates its strings and APIs once its executed.
Text: Volgmer一旦被执行就会对其字符串和API进行解密

en_text: Volgmer can delete files and itself after infection to avoid analysis.
Text: Volgmer在感染后可以删除文件和自己，以避免分析

en_text: Volgmer installs a copy of itself in a randomly selected service, then overwrites the ServiceDLL entry in the service's Registry entry. Some Volgmer variants also install .dll files as services with names generated by a list of hard-coded strings.
Text: Volgmer在一个随机选择的服务中安装自己的副本，然后在服务的注册表条目中覆盖ServiceDLL条目。一些Volgmer变种还将.dll文件安装为服务，其名称由一系列硬编码的字符串生成。

en_text: WannaCry contains a thread that will attempt to scan for new attached drives every few seconds. If one is identified, it will encrypt the files on the attached device.
Text: WannaCry包含一个线程，每隔几秒钟就会尝试扫描新的连接驱动器。如果发现了一个，它将对连接的设备上的文件进行加密。

en_text: WannaCry creates the service "mssecsvc2.0" with the display name "Microsoft Security Center (2.0) Service."
Text: WannaCry创建了 "mssecsvc2.0 "服务，显示名称为 "微软安全中心（2.0）服务"

en_text: WannaCry encrypts user files and demands that a ransom be paid in Bitcoin to decrypt those files.
Text: WannaCry加密了用户文件，并要求以比特币支付赎金来解密这些文件

en_text: WannaCry will attempt to determine the local network segment it is a part of.
Text: WannaCry将试图确定它所属于的本地网段

en_text: WannaCry uses an exploit in SMBv1 to spread itself to other remote systems on a network.
Text: WannaCry利用SMBv1的一个漏洞，将自己传播到网络上的其他远程系统

en_text: WannaCry utilizes wmic to delete shadow copies.
Text: WannaCry利用wmic来删除影子副本

en_text: WannaCry enumerates current remote desktop sessions and tries to execute the malware on each session.
Text: WannaCry列举了当前的远程桌面会话，并试图在每个会话上执行恶意软件

en_text: WannaCry scans its local network segment for remote systems to try to exploit and copy itself to.
Text: WannaCry扫描其本地网段，以试图利用和复制自己的远程系统

en_text: WannaCry uses attrib +h and icacls . /grant Everyone:F /T /C /Q to make some of its files hidden and grant all users full access controls.
Text: WannaCry使用attrib +h和icacls . /grant Everyone:F /T /C /Q，使其一些文件被隐藏，并授予所有用户完全的访问控制。

en_text: WannaCry uses attrib +h to make some of its files hidden.
Text: WannaCry使用attrib h使其一些文件被隐藏

en_text: WannaCry uses Tor for command and control traffic and routes a custom cryptographic protocol over the Tor circuit.
Text: WannaCry使用Tor进行命令和控制通信，并通过Tor电路路由一个自定义加密协议

en_text: WannaCry uses Tor for command and control traffic.
Text: WannaCry使用Tor进行指挥和控制通信

en_text: WannaCry uses vssadmin, wbadmin, bcdedit, and wmic to delete and disable operating system recovery features.
Text: WannaCry使用vssadmin、wbadmin、bcdedit和wmic来删除和禁用操作系统恢复功能

en_text: WannaCry attempts to kill processes associated with Exchange, Microsoft SQL Server, and MySQL to make it possible to encrypt their data stores.
Text: WannaCry试图杀死与Exchange、Microsoft SQL Server和MySQL相关的进程，以便有可能对其数据存储进行加密

en_text: WannaCry attempts to copy itself to remote computers after gaining access via an SMB exploit.
Text: WannaCry试图在通过SMB漏洞获得访问权后将自己复制到远程计算机上

en_text: WannaCry searches for variety of user files by file extension before encrypting them using RSA and AES, including Office, PDF, image, audio, video, source code, archive/compression format, and key and certificate files.
Text: WannaCry在使用RSA和AES进行加密之前，会根据文件扩展名搜索各种用户文件，包括Office、PDF、图像、音频、视频、源代码、档案等

en_text: Variants of WEBC2 achieve persistence by using DLL search order hijacking, usually by copying the DLL file to %SYSTEMROOT% (C:\WINDOWS\ntshrui.dll).
Text: WEBC2的变种通过使用DLL搜索顺序劫持来实现持久性，通常是将DLL文件复制到%SYSTEMROOT%（C:\WINDOWS\ntshrui.dll）

en_text: WEBC2 can open an interactive command shell.
Text: WEBC2可以打开一个交互式命令外壳

en_text: WEBC2 can download and execute a file.
Text: WEBC2可以下载并执行一个文件

en_text: WellMail can exfiltrate files from the victim machine.
Text: WellMail可以从受害者的机器上渗出文件

en_text: WellMail can decompress scripts received from C2.
Text: WellMail可以对从C2收到的脚本进行解压

en_text: WellMail can receive data and executable scripts from C2.
Text: WellMail可以接收来自C2的数据和可执行脚本

en_text: WellMail can identify the IP address of the victim system.
Text: WellMail可以识别受害者系统的IP地址。

en_text: WellMail can identify the current username on the victim system.
Text: WellMail可以识别受害者系统中的当前用户名

en_text: WellMail can use TCP for C2 communications.
Text: WellMail可以使用TCP进行C2通信

en_text: WellMail can use hard coded client and certificate authority certificates to communicate with C2 over mutual TLS.
Text: WellMail可以使用硬编码的客户和证书机构的证书，通过相互的TLS与C2通信

en_text: WellMail can archive files on the compromised host.
Text: WellMail可以在被攻击的主机上归档文件

en_text: WellMess can decode and decrypt data received from C2.
Text: WellMess可以对从C2收到的数据进行解码和解密

en_text: WellMess can send files from the victim machine to C2.
Text: WellMess可以将文件从受害者的机器发送到C2

en_text: WellMess can write files to a compromised host.
Text: WellMess可以将文件写到被攻击的主机上

en_text: WellMess can identify the computer name of a compromised host.
Text: WellMess可以识别被攻击的主机的计算机名称

en_text: WellMess can identify domain group membership for the current user.
Text: WellMess可以识别当前用户的域组成员资格

en_text: WellMess can identify the IP address and user domain on the target machine.
Text: WellMess可以识别目标机器上的IP地址和用户域

en_text: WellMess can use junk data in the Base64 string for additional obfuscation.
Text: WellMess可以使用Base64字符串中的垃圾数据进行额外的模糊处理

en_text: WellMess can encrypt HTTP POST data using RC6 and a dynamically generated AES key encrypted with a hard coded RSA public key.
Text: WellMess可以使用RC6和动态生成的AES密钥对HTTP POST数据进行加密，并使用硬编码的RSA公共密钥进行加密

en_text: WellMess can collect the username on the victim machine to send to C2.
Text: WellMess可以收集受害者机器上的用户名，并将其发送给C2

en_text: WellMess can communicate to C2 with mutual TLS where client and server mutually check certificates.
Text: WellMess可以通过客户和服务器相互检查证书的相互TLS与C2通信

en_text: WellMess can use HTTP and HTTPS in C2 communications.
Text: WellMess可以在C2通信中使用HTTP和HTTPS

en_text: WellMess can execute PowerShell scripts received from C2.
Text: WellMess可以执行从C2收到的PowerShell脚本

en_text: WellMess can execute command line scripts received from C2.
Text: WellMess可以执行从C2收到的命令行脚本

en_text: WellMess has used Base64 encoding to uniquely identify communication to and from the C2.
Text: WellMess使用Base64编码来唯一地识别进出C2的通信

en_text: WellMess has the ability to use DNS tunneling for C2 communications.
Text: WellMess有能力使用DNS隧道进行C2通信

en_text: Whitefly has named the malicious DLL the same name as DLLs belonging to legitimate software from various security vendors.
Text: Whitefly将恶意DLL与属于各安全厂商合法软件的DLL命名相同

en_text: Whitefly has used Mimikatz to obtain credentials.
Text: Whitefly利用Mimikatz获取证书

en_text: Whitefly has used search order hijacking to run the loader Vcrodat.
Text: Whitefly利用搜索顺序劫持来运行加载器Vcrodat

en_text: Whitefly has used an open-source tool to exploit a known Windows privilege escalation vulnerability (CVE-2016-0051) on unpatched computers.
Text: Whitefly利用一个开源工具，在未打补丁的计算机上利用一个已知的Windows特权升级漏洞（CVE-2016-0051）

en_text: Whitefly has used malicious .exe or .dll files disguised as documents or images.
Text: Whitefly使用恶意的.exe或.dll文件伪装成文档或图像

en_text: Whitefly has used a simple remote shell tool that will call back to the C2 server and wait for commands.
Text: Whitefly使用了一个简单的远程shell工具，将回调到C2服务器并等待命令

en_text: Whitefly has encrypted the payload used for C2.
Text: Whitefly已经加密了用于C2的有效载荷

en_text: Wiarp creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can create a service.
Text: Wiarp创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它创建一个服务

en_text: Wiarp creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can open a command line interface.
Text: Wiarp创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它打开一个命令行界面

en_text: Wiarp creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can inject files into running processes.
Text: Wiarp创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它将文件注入正在运行的进程

en_text: Wiarp creates a backdoor through which remote attackers can download files.
Text: Wiarp创建了一个后门，远程攻击者可以通过它下载文件

en_text: Windows Credential Editor can dump credentials.
Text: Windows凭证编辑器可以转储凭证

en_text: WINDSHIELD C2 traffic can communicate via TCP raw sockets.
Text: WINDSHIELD C2流量可以通过TCP原始套接字进行通信

en_text: WINDSHIELD can gather the victim computer name.
Text: WINDSHIELD可以收集受害者的计算机名称

en_text: WINDSHIELD can gather the victim user name.
Text: WINDSHIELD可以收集受害者的用户名

en_text: WINDSHIELD can gather Registry values.
Text: WINDSHIELD可以收集注册表的值

en_text: WINDSHIELD is capable of file deletion along with other file system interaction.
Text: WINDSHIELD能够在删除文件的同时进行其他文件系统互动

en_text: Windshift has sent spearphishing emails with attachment to harvest credentials and deliver malware.
Text: Windshift发送了带有附件的鱼叉式网络钓鱼邮件，以获取证书和传递恶意软件

en_text: Windshift has sent spearphishing emails with links to harvest credentials and deliver malware.
Text: Windshift发送了带有链接的鱼叉式钓鱼邮件，以获取证书和传递恶意软件

en_text: Windshift has used compromised websites to register custom URL schemes on a remote system.
Text: Windshift利用被攻击的网站在远程系统上注册自定义URL方案

en_text: Windshift has used e-mail attachments to lure victims into executing malicious code.
Text: Windshift利用电子邮件附件来引诱受害者执行恶意代码

en_text: Windshift has used icons mimicking MS Office files to mask malicious executables.
Text: Windshift利用模仿MS Office文件的图标来掩盖恶意的可执行文件。

en_text: Windshift has used links embedded in e-mails to lure victims into executing malicious code.
Text: Windshift利用嵌入电子邮件的链接来引诱受害者执行恶意代码

en_text: Windshift has used revoked certificates to sign malware.
Text: Windshift使用被撤销的证书来签署恶意软件

en_text: Windshift has used fake personas on social media to engage and target victims.
Text: Windshift在社交媒体上使用虚假的角色来吸引和锁定受害者

en_text: WindTail has the ability to receive and execute a self-delete command.
Text: WindTail具有接收和执行自我删除命令的能力

en_text: WindTail can invoke Apple APIs contentsOfDirectoryAtPath, pathExtension, and (string) compare.
Text: WindTail可以调用苹果公司的API contentsOfDirectoryAtPath、pathExtension和（字符串）比较

en_text: WindTail can identify and add files that possess specific file extensions to an array for archiving.
Text: WindTail可以识别并将拥有特定文件扩展名的文件添加到一个阵列中进行归档

en_text: WindTail can use the open command to execute an application.
Text: WindTail可以使用打开命令来执行一个应用程序

en_text: WindTail can instruct the OS to execute an application without a dock icon or menu.
Text: WindTail可以指示操作系统执行一个没有Dock图标或菜单的应用程序

en_text: WindTail can be delivered as a compressed, encrypted, and encoded payload.
Text: WindTail可作为压缩、加密和编码的有效载荷交付

en_text: WindTail has used icons mimicking MS Office files to mask payloads.
Text: WindTail使用模仿MS Office文件的图标来掩盖有效载荷

en_text: WindTail has been incompletely signed with revoked certificates.
Text: WindTail已被撤销的证书不完全签署

en_text: WindTail has the ability to enumerate the users home directory and the path to its own application bundle.
Text: WindTail有能力列举用户的主目录和它自己的应用程序包的路径

en_text: WindTail has the ability to generate the current date and time.
Text: WindTail有能力生成当前日期和时间

en_text: WindTail has the ability to use HTTP for C2 communications.
Text: WindTail有能力使用HTTP进行C2通信

en_text: WindTail has the ability to use the macOS built-in zip utility to archive files.
Text: WindTail有能力使用macOS内置的zip工具来归档文件

en_text: WindTail has the ability to automatically exfiltrate files using the macOS built-in utility /usr/bin/curl.
Text: WindTail有能力使用macOS内置工具自动渗出文件

en_text: WindTail has the ability to decrypt strings using hard-coded AES keys.
Text: WindTail有能力使用硬编码的AES密钥来解密字符串

en_text: WINERACK can create a reverse shell that utilizes statically-linked Wine cmd.exe code to emulate Windows command prompt commands.
Text: WINERACK可以创建一个反向外壳，利用静态链接的Wine cmd.exe代码来模拟Windows命令提示符命令

en_text: WINERACK can enumerate services.
Text: WINERACK可以列举服务

en_text: WINERACK can enumerate active windows.
Text: WINERACK可以列举活动窗口

en_text: WINERACK can enumerate processes.
Text: WINERACK可以列举进程

en_text: WINERACK can enumerate files and directories.
Text: WINERACK可以列举文件和目录

en_text: WINERACK can gather information about the host.
Text: WINERACK可以收集关于主机的信息

en_text: WINERACK can gather information on the victim username.
Text: WINERACK可以收集有关受害者用户名的信息

en_text: Winexe installs a service on the remote system, executes the command, then uninstalls the service.
Text: Winexe在远程系统上安装一个服务，执行命令，然后卸载该服务

en_text: Wingbird checks for the presence of Bitdefender security software.
Text: Wingbird检查是否存在Bitdefender安全软件

en_text: Wingbird exploits CVE-2016-4117 to allow an executable to gain escalated privileges.
Text: Wingbird利用CVE-2016-4117，允许一个可执行文件获得升级的权限

en_text: Wingbird uses services.exe to register a new autostart service named "Audit Service" using a copy of the local lsass.exe file.
Text: Wingbird使用services.exe来注册一个名为 "审计服务 "的新的自动启动服务，使用本地lsass.exe文件的副本

en_text: Wingbird drops a malicious file (sspisrv.dll) alongside a copy of lsass.exe, which is used to register a service that loads sspisrv.dll as a driver. The payload of the malicious driver (located in its entry-point function) is executed when loaded by lsass.exe before the spoofed service becomes unstable and crashes.
Text: Wingbird在lsass.exe的副本旁边投放了一个恶意文件（spisrv.dll），该文件用于注册一个加载spisrv.dll作为驱动程序的服务

en_text: Wingbird side loads a malicious file, sspisrv.dll, in part of a spoofed lssas.exe service.
Text: Wingbird在欺骗性的lssas.exe服务中侧面加载一个恶意文件sspisrv.dll

en_text: Wingbird deletes its payload along with the payload's parent process after it finishes copying files.
Text: Wingbird在完成复制文件后，将其有效载荷与有效载荷的父进程一起删除

en_text: Wingbird checks the victim OS version after executing to determine where to drop files based on whether the victim is 32-bit or 64-bit.
Text: Wingbird在执行后会检查受害者的操作系统版本，以根据受害者是32位还是64位来决定文件的投放位置

en_text: Wingbird performs multiple process injections to hijack system processes and execute malicious code.
Text: Wingbird执行多个进程注入，劫持系统进程并执行恶意代码

en_text: WinMM sets a WH_CBT Windows hook to search for and capture files on the victim.
Text: WinMM设置了一个WH_CBT Windows钩，以搜索和捕获受害者的文件

en_text: WinMM sets a WH_CBT Windows hook to collect information on process creation.
Text: WinMM设置了一个WH_CBT Windows钩子来收集进程创建的信息

en_text: WinMM uses HTTP for C2.
Text: WinMM使用HTTP进行C2

en_text: WinMM uses NetUser-GetInfo to identify that it is running under an "Admin" account on the local system.
Text: WinMM使用NetUser-GetInfo来识别它是在本地系统的 "管理员 "账户下运行

en_text: WinMM collects the system name, OS version including service pack, and system install date and sends the information to the C2 server.
Text: WinMM收集系统名称、操作系统版本（包括服务包）和系统安装日期，并将该信息发送到C2服务器

en_text: WinMM is usually configured with primary and backup domains for C2 communications.
Text: WinMM通常配置有主域和备份域用于C2通信

en_text: Winnti for Linux can encode its configuration file with single-byte XOR encoding.
Text: Winnti for Linux可以用单字节的XOR编码对其配置文件进行编码

en_text: Winnti for Linux has used a modified copy of the open-source userland rootkit Azazel, named libxselinux.so, to hide the malware's operations and network activity.
Text: Winnti for Linux使用了一个名为libxselinux.so的开源用户区rootkit Azazel的修改版本，以隐藏恶意软件的操作和网络活动

en_text: Winnti for Linux has used a passive listener, capable of identifying a specific magic value before executing tasking, as a secondary command and control (C2) mechanism.
Text: Winnti for Linux已经使用了一个被动监听器，能够在执行任务前识别一个特定的魔法值，作为二级命令和控制（C2）机制

en_text: Winnti for Linux has used a custom TCP protocol with four-byte XOR for command and control (C2).
Text: Winnti for Linux已经使用了一个自定义的TCP协议，用四字节的XOR来进行命令和控制（C2）

en_text: Winnti for Linux has used HTTP in outbound communications.
Text: Winnti for Linux已经在对外通信中使用了HTTP

en_text: Winnti for Linux has the ability to deploy modules directly from command and control (C2) servers, possibly for remote command execution, file exfiltration, and socks5 proxying on the infected host.
Text: Winnti for Linux有能力直接从命令和控制（C2）服务器部署模块，可能是为了在受感染的主机上进行远程命令执行、文件渗透和socks5代理

en_text: Winnti for Linux has used ICMP, custom TCP, and UDP in outbound communications.
Text: Winnti for Linux在对外通信中使用了ICMP、自定义TCP和UDP

en_text: Winnti for Linux has decoded XOR encoded strings holding its configuration upon execution.
Text: Winnti for Linux在执行时有解码的XOR编码字符串持有其配置

en_text: The Winnti for Windows installer loads a DLL using rundll32.
Text: Winnti for Windows安装程序使用rundll32加载一个DLL

en_text: Winnti for Windows sets its DLL file as a new service in the Registry to establish persistence.
Text: Winnti for Windows将其DLL文件设置为注册表中的一个新服务，以建立持久性

en_text: Winnti Group used stolen certificates to sign its malware.
Text: Winnti集团使用偷来的证书来签署其恶意软件

en_text: Winnti Group used a rootkit to modify typical server functionality.
Text: Winnti集团使用一个rootkit来修改典型的服务器功能

en_text: WIRTE has decoded a base64 encoded document which was embedded in a VBS script.
Text: WIRTE解码了一个base64编码的文件，该文件被嵌入到一个VBS脚本中

en_text: WIRTE has used Regsvr32.exe to trigger the execution of a malicious script.
Text: WIRTE利用Regsvr32.exe来触发一个恶意脚本的执行

en_text: WIRTE has used HTTP for network communication.
Text: WIRTE使用HTTP进行网络通信

en_text: WIRTE has downloaded PowerShell code from the C2 server to be executed.
Text: WIRTE已经从C2服务器下载了PowerShell代码来执行

en_text: WIRTE has used PowerShell for script execution.
Text: WIRTE已经使用PowerShell来执行脚本

en_text: WIRTE has used VBS scripts throughout its operation.
Text: WIRTE在其整个运作过程中使用了VBS脚本

en_text: Wizard Spider has installed TrickBot as a service named ControlServiceA in order to establish persistence.
Text: Wizard Spider将TrickBot安装为一个名为ControlServiceA的服务，以便建立持久性

en_text: Wizard Spider has used valid credentials for privileged accounts with the goal of accessing domain controllers.
Text: Wizard Spider将有效的凭证用于特权账户，目的是访问域控制器

en_text: Wizard Spider has exfiltrated victim information using FTP.
Text: Wizard Spider利用FTP渗出了受害者的信息

en_text: Wizard Spider has used services.exe to execute scripts and executables during lateral movement within a victim network.
Text: Wizard Spider利用services.exe在受害者网络内的横向移动中执行脚本和可执行文件

en_text: Wizard Spider has used SMB to drop Cobalt Strike Beacon on a domain controller for lateral movement.
Text: Wizard Spider利用SMB将Cobalt Strike Beacon投放到一个域控制器上进行横向移动

en_text: Wizard Spider has used Window Remote Management to move laterally through a victim network.
Text: Wizard Spider利用Window远程管理在受害者网络中横向移动

en_text: Wizard Spider has used scheduled tasks establish persistence for TrickBot and other malware.
Text: Wizard Spider利用计划任务为TrickBot和其他恶意软件建立了持久性

en_text: Wizard Spider has used spearphishing attachments to deliver Microsoft documents containing macros or PDFs containing malicious links to download either Emotet, Bokbot, TrickBot, or Bazar.
Text: Wizard Spider利用鱼叉式钓鱼附件提供含有宏的微软文件或含有恶意链接的PDF文件，以下载Emotet、Bokbot、TrickBot或Bazar

en_text: Wizard Spider has used "ipconfig" to identify the network configuration of a victim machine.
Text: Wizard Spider使用 "ipconfig "来识别受害者机器的网络配置

en_text: Wizard Spider has used "systeminfo" and similar commands to acquire detailed configuration information of a victim machine.
Text: Wizard Spider使用 "systeminfo "和类似的命令来获取受害者机器的详细配置信息

en_text: Wizard Spider has used "whoami" to identify the local user and their privileges.
Text: Wizard Spider使用 "whoami "来识别本地用户和他们的权限

en_text: Wizard Spider has used AdFind.exe to collect information about Active Directory organizational units and trust objects.
Text: Wizard Spider使用AdFind.exe来收集关于活动目录组织单元和信任对象的信息

en_text: Wizard Spider has used AdFind.exe to collect information about Active Directory groups and accounts.
Text: Wizard Spider使用AdFind.exe来收集有关活动目录组和账户的信息

en_text: Wizard Spider used Base64 encoding to obfuscate an Empire service and PowerShell commands.
Text: Wizard Spider使用Base64编码来混淆帝国服务和PowerShell命令

en_text: Wizard Spider has used cmd.exe to execute commands on a victim's machine.
Text: Wizard Spider使用cmd.exe在受害者的机器上执行命令

en_text: Wizard Spider has used the icacls command to modify access control to backup servers, providing them with full control of all the system folders.
Text: Wizard Spider使用icacls命令修改了对备份服务器的访问控制，使其能够完全控制所有系统文件夹

en_text: Wizard Spider has collected and staged credentials and network enumeration information, using  the networkdll and psfin TrickBot modules.
Text: Wizard Spider使用networkdll和psfin TrickBot模块，收集并储存了凭证和网络枚举信息

en_text: Wizard Spider has used Rubeus, MimiKatz Kerberos module, and the Invoke-Kerberoast cmdlet to steal AES hashes.
Text: Wizard Spider使用Rubeus、MimiKatz Kerberos模块和Invoke-Kerberoast cmdlet来窃取AES哈希值

en_text: Wizard Spider has used taskkill.exe and net.exe to stop backup, catalog, cloud, and other services prior to network encryption.
Text: Wizard Spider使用taskkill.exe和net.exe在网络加密前停止备份、目录、云和其他服务

en_text: Wizard Spider has used WMI to identify anti-virus products installed on a victim's machine.
Text: Wizard Spider使用WMI来识别安装在受害者机器上的防病毒产品

en_text: Wizard Spider has used administrative accounts, including Domain Admin, to move laterally within a victim network.
Text: Wizard Spider使用管理账户，包括域名管理，在受害者网络中横向移动

en_text: Wizard Spider has used macros to execute PowerShell scripts to download malware on victim's machines. It has also used PowerShell to execute commands and move laterally through a victim network.
Text: Wizard Spider使用宏来执行PowerShell脚本，在受害者的机器上下载恶意软件。它还使用PowerShell来执行命令，并在受害者网络中横向移动

en_text: Wizard Spider has used scheduled tasks to install TrickBot, using task names to appear legitimate such as WinDotNet, GoogleTask, or Sysnetsf. It has also used common document file names for other malware binaries.
Text: Wizard Spider使用计划任务来安装TrickBot，使用任务名称来显示合法，如WinDotNet、GoogleTask或Sysnetsf

en_text: Wizard Spider has used the "net view" command to locate mapped network shares.
Text: Wizard Spider使用了 "net view "命令来定位映射的网络共享

en_text: Wizard Spider has used the Invoke-Inveigh PowerShell cmdlets, likely for name service poisoning.
Text: Wizard Spider使用了Invoke-Inveigh PowerShell cmdlets，很可能用于名称服务中毒

en_text: Wizard Spider has used stolen credentials to copy tools into the %TEMP% directory of domain controllers.
Text: Wizard Spider使用偷来的凭证将工具复制到域控制器的%TEMP%目录中

en_text: Wizard Spider has used file deletion to remove some modules and configurations from an infected host after use.
Text: Wizard Spider使用文件删除的方式，在使用后从受感染的主机中删除一些模块和配置

en_text: Wizard Spider has gained access to credentials via exported copies of the ntds.dit Active Directory database.
Text: Wizard Spider通过导出的ntds.dit活动目录数据库副本获得了对证书的访问权

en_text: Wizard Spider has lured victims to execute malware with spearphishing attachments containing macros to download either Emotet, Bokbot, or TrickBot.
Text: Wizard Spider通过含有宏的鱼叉式附件诱使受害者执行恶意软件，以下载Emotet、Bokbot或TrickBot

en_text: Wizard Spider has exfiltrated domain credentials and network enumeration information over command and control (C2) channels.
Text: Wizard Spider通过命令和控制（C2）渠道渗出了域名凭证和网络枚举信息

en_text: Wizard Spider has identified domain admins through the use of "net group ‘Domain admins’" commands.
Text: Wizard Spider通过使用 "net group 'Domain admins'"命令来识别域管理员

en_text: Wizard Spider has accessed victim networks by using stolen credentials to access the corporate VPN infrastructure.
Text: Wizard Spider通过使用窃取的凭证访问公司的VPN基础设施来访问受害者网络

en_text: Wizard Spider has established persistence using Userinit by adding the Registry key HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon.
Text: Wizard Spider通过添加注册表键HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Winlogon，使用Userinit建立了持久性

en_text: Wizard Spider has modified the Registry key HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\SecurityProviders\WDigest by setting the UseLogonCredential registry value to 1 in order to force credentials to be stored in clear text in memory.
Text: Wizard Spider修改了注册表键HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\SecurityProviders\WDigest，将UseLogonCredential注册表值设置为1，以强制将证书以明文形式存储在内存中

en_text: Wizard Spider has used networkdll for network discovery and psfin specifically for financial and point of sale indicators. Wizard Spider has also used AdFind.exe and nltest/dclist to enumerate domain computers, including the domain controller.
Text: Wizard Spider将networkdll用于网络发现，将psfin专门用于金融和销售点指标。Wizard Spider还使用AdFind.exe和nltest/dclist来列举域计算机，包括域控制器。

en_text: Wizard Spider has acquired credentials from the SAM/SECURITY registry hives.
Text: Wizard Spider已经从SAM获得了证书

en_text: Wizard Spider has sent phishing emails containing a link to an actor-controlled Google Drive document or other free online file hosting services.
Text: Wizard Spider已经发送了钓鱼邮件，其中包含一个指向演员控制的Google Drive文件或其他免费在线文件托管服务的链接

en_text: Wizard Spider has shut down or uninstalled security applications on victim systems that might prevent ransomware from executing.
Text: Wizard Spider已经关闭或卸载了受害者系统上可能阻止勒索软件执行的安全应用程序

en_text: Wizard Spider has exploited or attempted to exploit Zerologon (CVE-2020-1472) and EternalBlue (MS17-010) vulnerabilities.
Text: Wizard Spider已经利用或试图利用Zerologon（CVE-2020-1472）和EternalBlue（MS17-010）漏洞

en_text: Wizard Spider has used WMI and LDAP queries for network discovery and to move laterally.
Text: Wizard Spider已经使用WMI和LDAP查询进行网络发现，并进行横向移动

en_text: Wizard Spider has has established persistence via the Registry key HKCU\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run and a shortcut within the startup folder.
Text: Wizard Spider已经通过注册表键HKCU\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run和启动文件夹中的一个快捷方式建立了持久性

en_text: Wizard Spider has used HTTP for network communications.
Text: Wizard Spider已使用HTTP进行网络通信

en_text: Wizard Spider has used RDP for lateral movement.
Text: Wizard Spider已使用RDP进行横向移动

en_text: Wizard Spider has lured victims into clicking a malicious link delivered through spearphishing.
Text: Wizard Spider诱使受害者点击通过鱼叉式网络钓鱼提供的恶意链接

en_text: Wizard Spider has injected malicious DLLs into memory with read, write, and execute permissions.
Text: Wizard Spider在内存中注入了具有读、写和执行权限的恶意DLLs

en_text: Wizard Spider has used Digicert code-signing certificates for some of its malware.
Text: Wizard Spider在其一些恶意软件中使用了Digicert代码签名证书

en_text: XAgentOSX contains the deletFileFromPath function to delete a specified file using the NSFileManager:removeFileAtPath method.
Text: XAgentOSX 包含 deletFileFromPath 函数，用于使用 NSFileManager:removeFileAtPath 方法删除一个指定的文件

en_text: XAgentOSX contains the ftpUpload function to use the FTPManager:uploadFile method to upload files from the target system.
Text: XAgentOSX 包含 ftpUpload 函数，用于使用 FTPManager:uploadFile 方法从目标系统上传文件

en_text: XAgentOSX contains the getFirefoxPassword function to attempt to locate Firefox passwords.
Text: XAgentOSX 包含 getFirefoxPassword 函数，用于尝试定位 Firefox 密码

en_text: XAgentOSX contains the getInfoOSX function to return the OS X version as well as the current user.
Text: XAgentOSX 包含 getInfoOSX 函数，用于返回 OS X 版本以及当前用户

en_text: XAgentOSX contains the takeScreenShot (along with startTakeScreenShot and stopTakeScreenShot) functions to take screenshots using the CGGetActiveDisplayList, CGDisplayCreateImage, and NSImage:initWithCGImage methods.
Text: XAgentOSX 包含 takeScreenShot（以及 startTakeScreenShot 和 stopTakeScreenShot）函数，用于使用 CGGetActiveDisplayList、CGDisplayCreateImage 和 NSImage:initWithCGImage 方法进行屏幕截图

en_text: XAgentOSX contains the execFile function to execute a specified file on the system using the NSTask:launch method.
Text: XAgentOSX包含execFile函数，用于使用NSTask:launch方法在系统中执行指定的文件

en_text: XAgentOSX contains the getInstalledAPP function to run ls -la /Applications to gather what applications are installed.
Text: XAgentOSX包含getInstalledAPP函数，用于运行ls -la

en_text: XAgentOSX contains the getProcessList function to run ps aux to get running processes.
Text: XAgentOSX包含getProcessList函数，用于运行ps aux以获得正在运行的进程

en_text: XAgentOSX contains the readFiles function to return a detailed listing (sometimes recursive) of a specified directory. XAgentOSX contains the showBackupIosFolder function to check for IOS device backups by running ls -la ~/Library/Application\ Support/MobileSync/Backup/.
Text: XAgentOSX包含readFiles函数，用于返回一个指定目录的详细列表（有时是递归）。XAgentOSX 包含 showBackupIosFolder 函数，用于通过运行 ls -la ~/Library/Application\ Support/MobileSync/Backup/来检查 IOS 设备的备份情况。

en_text: XAgentOSX contains keylogging functionality that will monitor for active application windows and write them to the log, it can handle special characters, and it will buffer by default 50 characters before sending them out over the C2 infrastructure.
Text: XAgentOSX包含键盘记录功能，它将监测活动的应用程序窗口并将其写入日志，它可以处理特殊字符，并且在通过C2基础设施发送之前，它将默认缓冲50个字符

en_text: Xbash has maliciously encrypted victim's database systems and demanded a cryptocurrency ransom be paid.
Text: Xbash恶意加密了受害者的数据库系统，并要求支付加密货币赎金
