en_text: Xbash can obtain a list of weak passwords from the C2 server to use for brute forcing as well as attempt to brute force services with open ports.
Text: Xbash可以从C2服务器上获得一个弱口令列表，用于暴力破解，并试图用开放的端口暴力破解服务

en_text: Xbash can download additional malicious files from its C2 server.
Text: Xbash可以从其C2服务器下载额外的恶意文件

en_text: Xbash can collect IP addresses and local intranet information from a victim’s machine.
Text: Xbash可以从受害者的机器上收集IP地址和本地内网信息

en_text: Xbash can perform port scanning of TCP and UDP ports.
Text: Xbash可以对TCP和UDP端口进行端口扫描

en_text: Xbash can obtain a webpage hosted on Pastebin to update its C2 domain list.
Text: Xbash可以获得一个托管在Pastebin上的网页，以更新其C2域名列表

en_text: Xbash can use mshta for executing scripts.
Text: Xbash可以使用mshta来执行脚本

en_text: Xbash can use regsvr32 for executing scripts.
Text: Xbash可以使用regsvr32来执行脚本

en_text: Xbash can use scripts to invoke PowerShell to download a malicious PE executable or PE DLL for execution.
Text: Xbash可以使用脚本调用PowerShell来下载恶意的PE可执行文件或PE DLL来执行

en_text: Xbash can execute malicious JavaScript payloads on the victim’s machine.
Text: Xbash可以在受害者的机器上执行恶意的JavaScript有效载荷

en_text: Xbash can execute malicious VBScript payloads on the victim’s machine.
Text: Xbash可以在受害者的机器上执行恶意的VBScript有效载荷

en_text: Xbash uses HTTP for C2 communications.
Text: Xbash使用HTTP进行C2通信

en_text: Xbash has destroyed Linux-based databases as part of its ransomware capabilities.
Text: Xbash已经破坏了基于Linux的数据库，作为其勒索软件能力的一部分

en_text: xCmd can be used to execute binaries on remote systems by creating and starting a service.
Text: xCmd可以用来通过创建和启动一个服务在远程系统上执行二进制文件

en_text: XTunnel is capable of accessing locally stored passwords on victims.
Text: XTunnel能够访问受害者的本地存储密码

en_text: XTunnel is capable of probing the network for open ports.
Text: XTunnel能够探测网络中的开放端口

en_text: XTunnel uses SSL/TLS and RC4 to encrypt traffic.
Text: XTunnel使用SSL XTunnel采用SSL XTunnel使用SSL

en_text: The C2 server used by XTunnel provides a port number to the victim to use as a fallback in case the connection closes on the currently used port.
Text: XTunnel使用的C2服务器为受害者提供了一个端口号，以便在当前使用的端口上关闭连接时作为备用

en_text: XTunnel has been used to execute remote commands.
Text: XTunnel已被用于执行远程命令

en_text: XTunnel relays traffic between a C2 server and a victim.
Text: XTunnel在C2服务器和受害者之间转发流量

en_text: YAHOYAH checks for the system’s Windows OS version and hostname.
Text: YAHOYAH检查系统的Windows操作系统版本和主机名

en_text: YAHOYAH checks for antimalware solution processes on the system.
Text: YAHOYAH检查系统中的反恶意软件解决方案进程

en_text: YAHOYAH uses HTTP GET requests to download other files that are executed in memory.
Text: YAHOYAH使用HTTP GET请求来下载在内存中执行的其他文件

en_text: YAHOYAH uses HTTP for C2.
Text: YAHOYAH使用HTTP进行C2

en_text: YAHOYAH encrypts its configuration file using a simple algorithm.
Text: YAHOYAH使用一种简单的算法对其配置文件进行加密

en_text: YAHOYAH decrypts downloaded files before execution.
Text: YAHOYAH在执行前对下载的文件进行解密

en_text: yty packs a plugin with UPX.
Text: yty打包了一个带有UPX的插件

en_text: yty uses the net view command for discovery.
Text: yty使用net view命令进行发现

en_text: yty gets an output of running processes using the tasklist command.
Text: yty使用tasklist命令获得运行进程的输出

en_text: yty uses a keylogger plugin to gather keystrokes.
Text: yty使用一个键盘记录器插件来收集键盘信息

en_text: yty gathers the computer name, the serial number of the main disk volume, CPU information, Microsoft Windows version, and runs the command systeminfo.
Text: yty收集计算机名称、主磁盘卷的序列号、CPU信息、Microsoft Windows版本，并运行systeminfo命令

en_text: yty collects the victim’s username.
Text: yty收集受害者的用户名

en_text: yty collects screenshots of the victim machine.
Text: yty收集受害者机器的屏幕截图

en_text: yty gathers information on victim’s drives and has a plugin for document listing.
Text: yty收集受害者硬盘上的信息，并有一个文件列表的插件

en_text: yty collects files with the following extensions: .ppt, .pptx, .pdf, .doc, .docx, .xls, .xlsx, .docm, .rtf, .inp, .xlsm, .csv, .odt, .pps, .vcf and sends them back to the C2 server.
Text: yty收集以下扩展名的文件：.ppt, .pptx, .pdf, .doc, .docx, .xls, .xlsx, .docm, .rtf, .inp, .xlsm, .csv, .odt, .pps, .vcf并将它们发回给C2服务器

en_text: yty communicates to the C2 server by retrieving a Google Doc.
Text: yty通过检索谷歌文档与C2服务器进行通信

en_text: yty establishes persistence by creating a scheduled task with the command SchTasks /Create /SC DAILY /TN BigData /TR " + path_file + "/ST 09:30".
Text: yty通过使用命令SchTasks创建一个计划任务来建立持久性

en_text: yty has some basic anti-sandbox detection that tries to detect Virtual PC, Sandboxie, and VMware.
Text: yty有一些基本的反沙盒检测，试图检测Virtual PC、Sandboxie和VMware

en_text: yty runs ipconfig /all and collects the domain name.
Text: yty运行ipconfig yty 运行 ipconfig yty 运行ipconfig yty运行ipconfig

en_text: yty contains junk code in its binary, likely to confuse malware analysts.
Text: yty在其二进制文件中包含垃圾代码，可能会混淆恶意软件分析人员

en_text: Zebrocy installs an application-defined Windows hook to get notified when a network drive has been attached, so it can then use the hook to call its RecordToFile file stealing method.
Text: Zebrocy安装了一个应用程序定义的Windows钩子，以便在网络驱动器被连接时得到通知，因此它可以使用钩子来调用其RecordToFile文件窃取方法

en_text: Zebrocy gets the username from the system.
Text: Zebrocy从系统中获得用户名

en_text: Zebrocy gathers the current time zone and date information from the system.
Text: Zebrocy从系统中收集了当前的时区和日期信息

en_text: Zebrocy's Delphi variant was packed with UPX.
Text: Zebrocy的Delphi变体被装入了UPX

en_text: One variant of Zebrocy uses WMI queries to gather information.
Text: Zebrocy的一个变体使用WMI查询来收集信息

en_text: A variant of Zebrocy captures screenshots of the victim’s machine in JPEG and BMP format.
Text: Zebrocy的一个变体以JPEG和BMP格式捕获受害者机器的屏幕截图

en_text: Zebrocy decodes its secondary payload and writes it to the victim’s machine. Zebrocy also uses AES and XOR to decrypt strings and payloads.
Text: Zebrocy对其二次有效载荷进行解码，并将其写入受害者的机器中。Zebrocy还使用AES和XOR来解密字符串和有效载荷。

en_text: Zebrocy obtains additional code to execute on the victim's machine, including the downloading of a secondary payload.
Text: Zebrocy获得额外的代码在受害者的机器上执行，包括下载一个二级有效载荷

en_text: Zebrocy enumerates information about connected storage devices.
Text: Zebrocy列举了有关连接的存储设备的信息

en_text: Zebrocy scans the system and automatically collects files with the following extensions: .doc, .docx, ,.xls, .xlsx, .pdf, .pptx, .rar, .zip, .jpg, .jpeg, .bmp, .tiff, .kum, .tlg, .sbx, .cr, .hse, .hsf, and .lhz.
Text: Zebrocy扫描系统并自动收集以下扩展名的文件：.doc, .docx, , .xls, .xlsx, .pdf, .pptx, .rar, .zip, .jpg, .jpeg, .bmp, .tiff, . kum, .tlg, .sbx, .cr, .hse, .hsf, and .lhz

en_text: Zebrocy uses cmd.exe to execute commands on the system.
Text: Zebrocy使用cmd.exe在系统上执行命令

en_text: Zebrocy has exfiltrated data to the designated C2 server using HTTP POST requests.
Text: Zebrocy使用HTTP POST请求将数据渗出到指定的C2服务器

en_text: Zebrocy uses HTTP for C2.
Text: Zebrocy使用HTTP进行C2

en_text: Zebrocy uses netstat -aon to gather network connection information.
Text: Zebrocy使用netstat -aon来收集网络连接信息

en_text: Zebrocy uses SMTP and POP3 for C2.
Text: Zebrocy使用SMTP和POP3进行C2

en_text: Zebrocy uses SSL and AES ECB for encrypting C2 communications.
Text: Zebrocy使用SSL和AES ECB对C2通信进行加密

en_text: Zebrocy uses the tasklist and wmic process get Capture, ExecutablePath commands to gather the processes running on the system.
Text: Zebrocy使用tasklist和wmic process get Capture, ExecutablePath命令来收集系统上运行的进程

en_text: Zebrocy has used URL/Percent Encoding on data exfiltrated via HTTP POST requests.
Text: Zebrocy使用了URL Zebrocy曾使用过URL Zebrocy曾使用过的URL Zebrocy使用过的URL

en_text: Zebrocy uses an encryption method similar to RC4 as well as AES to encrypt data before exfiltration.
Text: Zebrocy使用类似于RC4以及AES的加密方法，在渗出前对数据进行加密

en_text: Zebrocy collects the OS version, computer name and serial number for the storage volume C:. Zebrocy also runs the systeminfo command to gather system information.
Text: Zebrocy收集操作系统版本、计算机名称和存储卷C：的序列号

en_text: Zebrocy searches for files that are 60mb and less and contain the following extensions: .doc, .docx, .xls, .xlsx, .ppt, .pptx, .exe, .zip, and .rar. Zebrocy also runs the echo %APPDATA% command to list the contents of the directory. Zebrocy can obtain the current execution path as well as perform drive enumeration.
Text: Zebrocy搜索60mb及以下的文件，并包含以下扩展名：.doc、.docx、.xls、.xlsx、.ppt、.pptx、.exe、.zip和.rar。Zebrocy还运行echo %APPDATA%命令来列出目录的内容。Zebrocy可以获得当前的执行路径，以及执行驱动器枚举。

en_text: Zebrocy performs persistence with a logon script via adding to the Registry key HKCU\Environment\UserInitMprLogonScript.
Text: Zebrocy通过添加到注册表键HKCU\Environment\UserInitMprLogonScript，用登录脚本执行持久化

en_text: Zebrocy has the capability to upload dumper tools that extract credentials from web browsers and store them in database files.
Text: Zebrocy有能力上传从网络浏览器中提取凭证并将其存储在数据库文件中的翻转工具

en_text: Zebrocy has a command to delete files and directories.
Text: Zebrocy有一个删除文件和目录的命令

en_text: Zebrocy runs the ipconfig /all command.
Text: Zebrocy运行ipconfig Zebrocy运行了ipconfig Zebrocy运行的ipconfig Zebrocy运行ipconfig的时候

en_text: Zebrocy stores all collected information in a single file before exfiltration.
Text: Zebrocy在渗出前将所有收集的信息存储在一个文件中

en_text: Zebrocy creates an entry in a Registry Run key for the malware to execute on startup.
Text: Zebrocy在注册表运行键中创建了一个条目，以便恶意软件在启动时执行

en_text: Zebrocy executes the reg query command to obtain information in the Registry.
Text: Zebrocy执行reg查询命令以获得注册表中的信息

en_text: Zeroaccess is a kernel-mode rootkit.
Text: Zeroaccess是一个内核模式的rootkit

en_text: ZeroT shellcode decrypts and decompresses its RC4-encrypted payload.
Text: ZeroT shellcode对其RC4加密的有效载荷进行解密和解压

en_text: ZeroT has retrieved stage 2 payloads as Bitmap images that use Least Significant Bit (LSB) steganography.
Text: ZeroT将第二阶段的有效载荷检索为使用最小显著位（LSB）隐写术的位图图像

en_text: ZeroT can add a new service to ensure PlugX persists on the system when delivered as another payload onto the system.
Text: ZeroT可以添加一个新的服务，以确保PlugX在作为另一个有效载荷传递到系统上时能持续存在于系统中

en_text: ZeroT can download additional payloads onto the victim.
Text: ZeroT可以下载额外的有效载荷到受害者身上

en_text: ZeroT has used DLL side-loading to load malicious payloads.
Text: ZeroT利用DLL侧面加载来加载恶意的有效载荷

en_text: ZeroT has used RC4 to encrypt C2 traffic.
Text: ZeroT使用RC4对C2流量进行了加密

en_text: ZeroT has obfuscated DLLs and functions using dummy API calls inserted between real instructions.
Text: ZeroT使用插入真实指令之间的假API调用来混淆DLL和函数

en_text: ZeroT gathers the victim's IP address and domain information, and then sends it to its C2 server.
Text: ZeroT收集受害者的IP地址和域名信息，然后将其发送到其C2服务器

en_text: ZeroT gathers the victim's computer name, Windows version, and system language, and then sends it to its C2 server.
Text: ZeroT收集受害者的计算机名称、Windows版本和系统语言，然后将其发送到其C2服务器

en_text: ZeroT has used HTTP for C2.
Text: ZeroT已将HTTP用于C2

en_text: ZeroT has encrypted its payload with RC4.
Text: ZeroT用RC4对其有效载荷进行了加密

en_text: Zeus Panda checks to see if anti-virus, anti-spyware, or firewall products are installed in the victim’s environment.
Text: Zeus Panda检查受害者的环境中是否安装了反病毒、反间谍软件或防火墙产品

en_text: Zeus Panda checks for running processes on the victim’s machine.
Text: Zeus Panda检查受害者机器上的运行进程

en_text: Zeus Panda checks processes on the system and if they meet the necessary requirements, it injects into that process.
Text: Zeus Panda检查系统中的进程，如果它们符合必要的要求，它就会注入该进程中

en_text: Zeus Panda checks for the existence of a Registry key and if it contains certain values.
Text: Zeus Panda检查注册表键的存在以及它是否包含某些值

en_text: Zeus Panda can take screenshots of the victim’s machine.
Text: Zeus Panda可以对受害者的机器进行截图

en_text: Zeus Panda can launch an interface where it can execute several commands on the victim’s PC.
Text: Zeus Panda可以启动一个界面，在那里它可以在受害者的电脑上执行几个命令

en_text: Zeus Panda can perform keylogging on the victim’s machine by hooking the functions TranslateMessage and WM_KEYDOWN.
Text: Zeus Panda可以通过钩住TranslateMessage和WM_KEYDOWN函数在受害者的机器上进行键盘记录

en_text: Zeus Panda can download additional malware plug-in modules and execute them on the victim’s machine.
Text: Zeus Panda可以下载额外的恶意软件插件模块并在受害者的机器上执行

en_text: Zeus Panda can launch remote scripts on the victim’s machine.
Text: Zeus Panda可以在受害者的机器上启动远程脚本

en_text: Zeus Panda uses HTTP for C2 communications.
Text: Zeus Panda使用HTTP进行C2通信

en_text: Zeus Panda uses PowerShell to download and execute the payload.
Text: Zeus Panda使用PowerShell来下载和执行有效载荷

en_text: Zeus Panda collects the OS version, system architecture, computer name, product ID, install date, and information on the keyboard mapping to determine the language used on the system.
Text: Zeus Panda收集操作系统版本、系统结构、计算机名称、产品ID、安装日期和键盘映射信息，以确定系统使用的语言

en_text: Zeus Panda collects the current system time (UTC) and sends it back to the C2 server.
Text: Zeus Panda收集当前的系统时间（UTC）并将其发回给C2服务器

en_text: Zeus Panda adds persistence by creating Registry Run keys.
Text: Zeus Panda通过创建注册表运行键来增加持久性

en_text: Zeus Panda hooks processes by leveraging its own IAT hooked functions.
Text: Zeus Panda通过利用其自身的IAT挂钩功能来钩住流程

en_text: Zeus Panda modifies several Registry keys under HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\ PhishingFilter\ to disable phishing filters.
Text: Zeus Panda修改了HKCU/Software/Microsoft/Internet Explorer/PhishingFilter/下的几个注册表键，以禁用网络钓鱼过滤器

en_text: Zeus Panda encrypts strings with XOR and obfuscates the macro code from the initial payload. Zeus Panda also encrypts all configuration and settings in AES and RC4.
Text: Zeus Panda用XOR对字符串进行加密，并将宏代码与初始有效载荷混淆。Zeus Panda还以AES和RC4加密所有配置和设置。

en_text: Zeus Panda has a command to delete a file. It also can uninstall scripts and delete files to cover its track.
Text: Zeus Panda有一个删除文件的命令

en_text: Zeus Panda searches for specific directories on the victim’s machine.
Text: Zeus Panda在受害者的机器上搜索特定目录

en_text: ZLib creates Registry keys to allow itself to run as various services.
Text: ZLib创建注册表键，允许自己作为各种服务运行

en_text: The ZLib backdoor compresses communications using the standard Zlib compression library.
Text: ZLib后门使用标准的Zlib压缩库压缩通信

en_text: ZLib has the ability to discover and manipulate Windows services.
Text: ZLib具有发现和操作Windows服务的能力

en_text: ZLib has the ability to enumerate files and drives.
Text: ZLib具有列举文件和驱动器的能力

en_text: ZLib has the ability to enumerate system information.
Text: ZLib具有列举系统信息的能力

en_text: ZLib has the ability to download files.
Text: ZLib具有下载文件的能力

en_text: ZLib mimics the resource version information of legitimate Realtek Semiconductor, Nvidia, or Synaptics modules.
Text: ZLib模仿合法的Realtek Semiconductor、Nvidia或Synaptics模块的资源版本信息

en_text: ZLib communicates over HTTP for C2.
Text: ZLib通过HTTP进行C2通信

en_text: ZLib has the ability to obtain screenshots of the compromised system.
Text: ZLib有能力获得被入侵系统的屏幕截图

en_text: ZLib has the ability to execute shell commands.
Text: ZLib有执行shell命令的能力

en_text: zwShell can obtain the victim IP address.

en_text: zwShell can obtain the victim PC name and OS version.

en_text: zwShell has been copied over network shares to move laterally.
Text: zwShell已经通过网络共享复制了横向移动

en_text: zwShell has deleted itself after creating a service as well as deleted a temporary file when the system reboots.

en_text: ZxShell hooks several API functions to spawn system threads.
Text: ZxShell钩住了几个API函数来催生系统线程

en_text: ZxShell has remote desktop functionality.
Text: ZxShell具有远程桌面功能

en_text: ZxShell can capture screenshots.
Text: ZxShell可以捕获屏幕截图

en_text: ZxShell can query the netsvc group value data located in the svchost group Registry key.
Text: ZxShell可以查询位于svchost组注册表键中的netsvc组值数据

en_text: ZxShell can collect the owner and organization information from the target workstation.
Text: ZxShell可以从目标工作站收集所有者和组织信息

en_text: ZxShell can delete files from the system.
Text: ZxShell可以从系统中删除文件

en_text: ZxShell can check the services on the system.
Text: ZxShell可以检查系统上的服务

en_text: ZxShell can launch port scans.

en_text: ZxShell can launch a reverse command shell.

en_text: ZxShell can kill AV products' processes.

en_text: ZxShell can set up an HTTP or SOCKS proxy.
Text: ZxShell可以设置一个HTTP或SOCKS代理

en_text: ZxShell can create a new service using the service parser function ProcessScCommand.
Text: ZxShell可以使用服务解析器函数ProcessScCommand创建一个新的服务

en_text: ZxShell can collect the local hostname, operating system details, CPU speed, and total physical memory.
Text: ZxShell可以收集本地主机名、操作系统细节、CPU速度和总物理内存

en_text: ZxShell can disable the firewall by modifying the registry key HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\SharedAccess\Parameters\FirewallPolicy\StandardProfile.
Text: ZxShell可以通过修改注册表键HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\SharedAccess\Parameters\FirewallPolicy\StandardProfile禁用防火墙

en_text: ZxShell has used FTP for C2 connections.
Text: ZxShell已经使用FTP进行C2连接

en_text: ZxShell has used HTTP for C2 connections.
Text: ZxShell已经使用HTTP进行C2连接

en_text: ZxShell has used rundll32.exe to execute other DLLs and named pipes.
Text: ZxShell已经使用rundll32.exe来执行其他DLLs和命名的管道

Text: ZxShell有一个创建本地用户账户的功能

Text: ZxShell有一个对主机进行SYN泛滥攻击的功能

Text: ZxShell有一个功能，可以使用键盘记录器捕获远程计算机的击键

en_text: ZxShell has a command called RunAs, which creates a new process as another user or process context.
Text: ZxShell有一个叫RunAs的命令，它可以作为另一个用户或进程上下文创建一个新的进程

en_text: ZxShell has a command, ps, to obtain a listing of processes on the system.
Text: ZxShell有一个命令，ps，可以获得系统中的进程列表

en_text: ZxShell has a command to transfer files from a remote host.
Text: ZxShell有一个命令可以从远程主机传输文件

en_text: ZxShell has a command to perform video device spying.
Text: ZxShell有一个命令可以进行视频设备监视

en_text: ZxShell has a command to clear system event logs.
Text: ZxShell有一个命令可以清除系统事件日志

en_text: ZxShell has a command to open a file manager and explorer on the system.
Text: ZxShell有一个命令可以在系统上打开一个文件管理器和资源管理器

en_text: ZxShell supports functionality for VNC sessions.
Text: ZxShell支持VNC会话的功能

en_text: Octopus collects the username from the victim’s machine.

Text: 八达通可以捕获受害者机器的屏幕截图

Text: 八达通使用HTTP进行C2通信

en_text: Octopus collects system drive information, the computer name, and the size of the disk.
Text: 八达通收集系统驱动器信息、计算机名称和磁盘的大小

en_text: Octopus encodes C2 communications in Base64.
Text: 八达通以Base64编码C2通信

en_text: The White Company has obfuscated their payloads through packing.
Text: 白色公司通过包装使他们的有效载荷变得模糊不清

en_text: The White Company has the ability to delete its malware entirely from the target system.
Text: 白色公司有能力从目标系统中完全删除其恶意软件

en_text: Stolen Pencil has used tools that are capable of obtaining credentials from web browsers.
Text: 被盗的铅笔公司使用了能够从网络浏览器中获取凭证的工具

en_text: Stolen Pencil victims are prompted to install malicious Google Chrome extensions which gave the threat actor the ability to read data from any website accessed.
Text: 被盗铅笔的受害者被提示安装恶意的谷歌浏览器扩展程序，这使威胁行为者有能力从访问的任何网站读取数据

en_text: Poseidon Group tools attempt to spoof anti-virus processes as a means of self-defense.
Text: 波塞冬集团的工具试图欺骗反病毒程序，作为一种自卫手段

en_text: The Poseidon Group's Information Gathering Tool (IGT) includes PowerShell components.
Text: 波塞冬集团的信息收集工具（IGT）包括PowerShell组件

en_text: Poseidon Group conducts credential dumping on victims, with a focus on obtaining credentials belonging to domain and database servers.

en_text: BBK can extract a malicious Portable Executable (PE) from a photo.
Text: 步步高可以从照片中提取一个恶意的可移植执行文件（PE）

en_text: Operators deploying Netwalker have used psexec to copy the Netwalker payload across accessible systems.
Text: 部署Netwalker的运营商使用pexec在可访问系统中复制Netwalker有效载荷

en_text: Operators deploying Netwalker have used psexec and certutil to retrieve the Netwalker payload.
Text: 部署Netwalker的运营商已经使用pexec和certutil检索Netwalker的有效载荷

en_text: Operators deploying Netwalker have used batch scripts to retrieve the Netwalker payload.
Text: 部署Netwalker的运营商已经使用批处理脚本来检索Netwalker的有效载荷

en_text: OSX/Shlayer can base64-decode and AES-decrypt downloaded payloads.
Text: OSX/Shlayer可以对下载的有效载荷进行base64解码和AES解密。

en_text: OSX/Shlayer can collect the macOS version and IOPlatformUUID.
Text: OSX/Shlayer可以收集macOS版本和IOPlatformUUID。

en_text: OSX/Shlayer can escalate privileges to root by asking the user for credentials.
Text: OSX/Shlayer可以通过要求用户提供凭证将权限升级到root。

en_text: OSX/Shlayer can install malicious Safari browser extensions to serve ads.
Text: OSX/Shlayer可以安装恶意的Safari浏览器扩展以提供广告。

en_text: OSX/Shlayer can masquerade as a Flash Player update.
Text: OSX/Shlayer可以伪装成一个Flash Player的更新。

en_text: OSX/Shlayer can use bash scripts to check the macOS version and download payloads.
Text: OSX/Shlayer可以使用bash脚本来检查macOS版本并下载有效载荷。

en_text: OSX/Shlayer can use the chmod utility to set a .app file as executable, and the spctl application to disable Gatekeeper protection for a downloaded file..
Text: OSX/Shlayer可以使用chmod工具将一个.app文件设置为可执行文件，并使用spctl应用程序禁用下载文件的Gatekeeper保护。

en_text: OSX/Shlayer executes a .command script from a hidden directory in a mounted DMG.
Text: OSX/Shlayer从加载的DMG中的一个隐藏目录中执行.command脚本。

en_text: OSX/Shlayer relies on users mounting and executing a malicious DMG file.
Text: OSX/Shlayer依赖于用户安装和执行一个恶意的DMG文件。

en_text: Dust Storm has used Android backdoors capable of enumerating specific files on the infected devices.
Text: 尘暴使用了能够列举受感染设备上特定文件的安卓后门

en_text: Dust Storm has used Android backdoors capable of exfiltrating specific files directly from the infected devices.

Text: 丹尼斯进行了多次系统检查，寻找处理器和寄存器的特征，以逃避仿真和分析

en_text: Denis enumerates and collects the username from the victim’s machine.
Text: 丹尼斯列举并收集受害者机器上的用户名

en_text: Denis compressed collected data using zlib.
Text: 丹尼斯使用zlib压缩了收集的数据

en_text: Denis has a command to delete files from the victim’s machine.
Text: 丹尼斯有一个命令可以从受害者的机器上删除文件

en_text: Denis has used DNS tunneling for C2 communications.
Text: 丹尼斯在C2通信中使用了DNS隧道

en_text: Denis deploys additional backdoors and hacking tools to the system.
Text: 丹尼斯在系统中部署了额外的后门和黑客工具

en_text: When the Duqu command and control is operating over HTTP or HTTPS, Duqu uploads data to its controller by appending it to a blank JPG file.
Text: 当Duqu命令和控制通过HTTP或HTTPS操作时，Duqu通过将数据附加到一个空白的JPG文件中上传到其控制器

en_text: Xbash can attempt to exploit known vulnerabilities in Hadoop, Redis, or ActiveMQ when it finds those services running in order to conduct further execution.
Text: 当Xbash发现Hadoop、Redis或ActiveMQ的服务正在运行时，它可以尝试利用这些已知的漏洞，以进行进一步的执行

en_text: PipeMon can switch to an alternate C2 domain when a particular date has been reached.
Text: 当达到某个特定日期时，PipeMon可以切换到另一个C2域

en_text: When a document is found matching one of the extensions in the configuration, TINYTYPHON uploads it to the C2 server.
Text: 当发现一个文件与配置中的一个扩展名相匹配时，TINYTYPHON将它上传到C2服务器

en_text: Flame can take regular screenshots when certain applications are open that are sent to the command and control server.
Text: 当某些应用程序打开时，Flame可以定期进行截图，这些截图会被发送到命令和控制服务器

en_text: When it first starts, BADNEWS spawns a new thread to log keystrokes.
Text: 当它第一次启动时，BADNEWS会生成一个新的线程来记录击键

en_text: When it first starts, BADNEWS crawls the victim's local drives and collects documents with the following extensions: .doc, .docx, .pdf, .ppt, .pptx, and .txt.
Text: 当它第一次启动时，BADNEWS爬行受害者的本地驱动器并收集具有以下扩展名的文件：.doc、.docx、.pdf、.ppt、.pptx和.txt

en_text: When it first starts, BADNEWS crawls the victim's mapped drives and collects documents with the following extensions: .doc, .docx, .pdf, .ppt, .pptx, and .txt.
Text: 当它第一次启动时，BADNEWS爬行受害者的映射驱动器并收集具有以下扩展名的文件：.doc、.docx、.pdf、.ppt、.pptx和.txt

en_text: NotPetya uses rundll32.exe to install itself on remote systems when accessed via PsExec or wmic.
Text: 当通过PsExec或wmic访问时，NotPetya使用rundll32.exe在远程系统上安装自己

en_text: Zebrocy identifies network drives when they are added to victim systems.
Text: 当网络驱动器被添加到受害者系统时，Zebrocy会识别它们

en_text: SPACESHIP copies staged data to removable drives when they are inserted into the system.
Text: 当移动硬盘插入系统时，SPACESHIP会将分阶段的数据复制到移动硬盘上

en_text: Carberp has captured credentials when a user performs login through a SSL session.
Text: 当用户通过SSL会话执行登录时，Carberp已经捕获了凭据

en_text: Derusbi is capable of capturing video.
Text: 德鲁斯比能够捕捉到视频

en_text: Derusbi is capable of performing screen captures.
Text: 德鲁斯比能够进行屏幕抓取

en_text: Derusbi is capable of performing audio captures.
Text: 德鲁斯比能够进行音频捕捉

en_text: Derusbi uses a backup communication method with an HTTP beacon.
Text: 德鲁斯比使用的是一种带有HTTP信标的备份通信方法

en_text: Derusbi has used unencrypted HTTP on port 443 for C2.
Text: 德鲁斯比为C2使用了443端口的未加密的HTTP

en_text: Adversaries can direct BACKSPACE to upload files to the C2 Server.
Text: 敌方可以指示BACKSPACE将文件上传到C2服务器

en_text: Adversaries can instruct Duqu to spread laterally by copying itself to shares it has enumerated and for which it has obtained legitimate credentials (via keylogging or other means). The remote host is then infected by using the compromised credentials to schedule a task on remote machines that executes the malware.
Text: 敌方可以指示Duqu通过将自己复制到它所列举的、它已获得合法凭证（通过键盘记录或其他手段）的共享上进行横向传播。然后，远程主机通过使用被破坏的凭证在远程机器上安排一个执行恶意软件的任务而被感染。

en_text: Empire contains a variety of enumeration modules that have an option to use API calls to carry out tasks.
Text: 帝国包含各种枚举模块，这些模块有一个选项是使用API调用来执行任务

en_text: Empire contains modules that can discover and exploit search order hijacking vulnerabilities.
Text: 帝国包含可以发现和利用搜索顺序劫持漏洞的模块

en_text: Empire contains modules that can discover and exploit various DLL hijacking opportunities.
Text: 帝国包含能够发现和利用各种DLL劫持机会的模块

en_text: Empire contains an implementation of Mimikatz to gather credentials from memory.
Text: 帝国包含一个Mimikatz的实现，从内存中收集凭证

en_text: Empire includes keylogging capabilities for Windows, Linux, and macOS systems.
Text: 帝国包括Windows、Linux和macOS系统的键盘记录功能

en_text: Empire includes various modules to attempt to bypass UAC for escalation of privileges.
Text: 帝国包括各种模块，试图绕过UAC进行权限升级

en_text: Empire can perform port scans from an infected host.
Text: 帝国可以从受感染的主机上进行端口扫描

en_text: Empire can timestomp any files or payloads placed on a target machine to help them blend in.
Text: 帝国可以对放置在目标机器上的任何文件或有效载荷进行时间压缩，以帮助它们混入

en_text: Empire can perform pass the hash attacks.
Text: 帝国可以进行通过哈希攻击

en_text: Empire can use Dropbox for data exfiltration.
Text: 帝国可以利用Dropbox进行数据渗透

en_text: Empire can use GitHub for data exfiltration.
Text: 帝国可以利用GitHub进行数据渗透

en_text: Empire can utilize Invoke-DCOM to leverage remote COM execution for lateral movement.
Text: 帝国可以利用Invoke-DCOM来利用远程COM执行来进行横向移动

en_text: Empire can exploit vulnerabilities such as MS16-032 and MS16-135.
Text: 帝国可以利用MS16-032和MS16-135这样的漏洞

en_text: Empire can leverage WMI debugging to remotely replace binaries like sethc.exe, Utilman.exe, and Magnify.exe with cmd.exe.
Text: 帝国可以利用WMI调试，用cmd.exe远程替换sethc.exe、Utilman.exe和Magnify.exe等二进制文件

en_text: Empire can utilize built-in modules to modify service binaries and restore them to their original state.
Text: 帝国可以利用内置模块来修改服务二进制文件，并将其恢复到原来的状态

en_text: Empire can leverage its implementation of Mimikatz to obtain and use golden tickets.
Text: 帝国可以利用其对Mimikatz的实施来获得和使用金票

en_text: Empire can leverage its implementation of Mimikatz to obtain and use silver tickets.
Text: 帝国可以利用其对Mimikatz的实施来获得和使用银票

en_text: Empire can enumerate antivirus software on the target.
Text: 帝国可以列举出目标上的防病毒软件

en_text: Empire can enumerate the current network connections of a host.
Text: 帝国可以列举一个主机的当前网络连接

en_text: Empire can enumerate host system information like OS, architecture, applied patches, and more.
Text: 帝国可以列举主机系统信息，如操作系统、架构、应用的补丁等

en_text: Empire can use Dropbox and GitHub for C2.
Text: 帝国可以使用Dropbox和GitHub的C2

en_text: Empire can use Inveigh to conduct name service poisoning for credential theft and associated relay attacks.
Text: 帝国可以使用Inveigh进行名称服务中毒，以实现凭证盗窃和相关中继攻击

en_text: Empire can use Invoke-RunAs to make tokens.
Text: 帝国可以使用Invoke-RunAs来制作令牌

en_text: Empire can use New-GPOImmediateTask to modify a GPO that will install and execute a malicious Scheduled Task/Job.
Text: 帝国可以使用New-GPOImmediateTask来修改一个GPO，它将安装和执行一个恶意的计划任务

en_text: Empire can use PowerSploit's Invoke-TokenManipulation to manipulate access tokens.
Text: 帝国可以使用PowerSploit的Invoke-TokenManipulation来操纵访问令牌

en_text: Empire can use PsExec to execute a payload on a remote host.
Text: 帝国可以使用PsExec在远程主机上执行一个有效载荷

en_text: Empire can use TLS to encrypt its C2 channel.
Text: 帝国可以使用TLS对其C2通道进行加密

en_text: Empire can use modules that extract passwords from common web browsers such as Firefox and Chrome.
Text: 帝国可以使用从Firefox和Chrome等常见网络浏览器中提取密码的模块

en_text: Empire can use various modules to search for files containing passwords.
Text: 帝国可以使用各种模块来搜索含有密码的文件

en_text: Empire can use built-in modules to abuse trusted utilities like MSBuild.exe.
Text: 帝国可以使用内置模块来滥用受信任的实用程序，如MSBuild.exe

en_text: Empire can conduct command and control over protocols like HTTP and HTTPS.
Text: 帝国可以通过HTTP和HTTPS等协议进行指挥和控制

en_text: Empire can persist by modifying a .LNK file to include a backdoor.
Text: 帝国可以通过修改.LNK文件以包括一个后门而持续存在

en_text: Empire can send data gathered from a target through the command and control channel.
Text: 帝国可以通过指挥和控制通道发送从目标收集的数据

en_text: Empire can upload and download to and from a victim machine.
Text: 帝国可以向受害者的机器上传和下载

en_text: Empire can modify the registry run keys HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run and HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run for persistence.
Text: 帝国可以修改注册表运行键HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run和HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run的持久性

en_text: Empire can be used to conduct packet captures on target hosts.
Text: 帝国可以用来对目标主机进行数据包捕获

en_text: Empire can capture webcam data on Windows and macOS systems.
Text: 帝国可以在Windows和macOS系统上捕获网络摄像头数据

en_text: Empire can harvest clipboard data on both Windows and macOS systems.
Text: 帝国可以在Windows和macOS系统上收获剪贴板数据

en_text: Empire can find shared drives on the local system.
Text: 帝国可以在本地系统上找到共享驱动器

en_text: Empire can ZIP directories on the target system.
Text: 帝国可以在目标系统上的ZIP目录

en_text: Empire can find information about processes running on local and remote systems.
Text: 帝国可以找到有关在本地和远程系统上运行的进程的信息

en_text: Empire is capable of capturing screenshots on Windows and macOS systems.
Text: 帝国能够在Windows和macOS系统上抓取屏幕截图

en_text: Empire uses a command-line interface to interact with systems.
Text: 帝国使用命令行界面与系统进行交互

en_text: Empire has modules to interact with the Windows task scheduler.
Text: 帝国拥有与Windows任务调度器互动的模块

en_text: Empire has modules for enumerating domain trusts.
Text: 帝国有列举域名信任的模块

en_text: Empire has the ability to obfuscate commands using Invoke-Obfuscation.
Text: 帝国有能力使用Invoke-Obfuscation对命令进行混淆

en_text: Empire has the ability to gather browser data such as bookmarks and visited sites.
Text: 帝国有能力收集浏览器数据，如书签和访问过的网站

en_text: Empire has the ability to collect emails on a target system.
Text: 帝国有能力收集目标系统上的电子邮件

en_text: Empire has a limited number of built-in modules for exploiting remote SMB, JBoss, and Jenkins servers.
Text: 帝国有数量有限的内置模块，用于利用远程SMB、JBoss和Jenkins服务器

en_text: Empire has a module for creating a local user if permissions allow.
Text: 帝国有一个模块可以在权限允许的情况下创建一个本地用户

en_text: Empire has modules for executing scripts.
Text: 帝国有执行脚本的模块

en_text: Analysis of Daserf has shown that it regularly undergoes technical improvements to evade anti-virus detection.
Text: 对Daserf的分析表明，它经常进行技术改进，以躲避反病毒检测

en_text: For all non-removable drives on a victim, USBStealer executes automated collection of certain files for later exfiltration.
Text: 对于受害者的所有不可拆卸驱动器，USBStealer执行自动收集某些文件，以便以后渗出

en_text: For C2 over HTTP, Helminth encodes data with base64 and sends it via the "Cookie" field of HTTP requests. For C2 over DNS, Helminth converts ASCII characters into their hexadecimal values and sends the data in cleartext.
Text: 对于通过HTTP的C2，Helminth用base64编码数据，并通过HTTP请求的 "Cookie "字段进行发送。对于通过DNS的C2，Helminth将ASCII字符转换为其十六进制值，并以明文方式发送数据。

en_text: For early Gazer versions, the compilation timestamp was faked.
Text: 对于早期的Gazer版本，编译的时间戳是伪造的

en_text: Anchor can self delete its dropper after the malware is successfully deployed.
Text: 恶意软件成功部署后，Anchor可以自行删除其dropper

en_text: Epic uses the net view command on the victim’s machine.
Text: Epic在受害者的机器上使用net view命令。

en_text: Equation has used an encrypted virtual file system stored in the Windows Registry.
Text: 方程公司使用了存储在Windows注册表中的加密的虚拟文件系统

en_text: Equation has used tools with the functionality to search for specific information about the attached hard drive that could be used to identify and overwrite the firmware.
Text: 方程公司使用了具有搜索所附硬盘具体信息功能的工具，可用于识别和覆盖固件

en_text: Frankenstein has used Word documents that prompts the victim to enable macros and run a Visual Basic script.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦曾使用Word文档，提示受害者启用宏并运行Visual Basic脚本

en_text: Frankenstein has used CVE-2017-11882 to execute code on the victim's machine.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦利用CVE-2017-11882在受害者的机器上执行代码

en_text: Frankenstein has harvested credentials from the victim's machine using Empire.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦利用Empire从受害者的机器上获取了凭证

en_text: Frankenstein has used spearphishing emails to send trojanized Microsoft Word documents.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦利用鱼叉式网络钓鱼邮件发送木马化的微软Word文档

en_text: Frankenstein has enumerated hosts, looking to obtain a list of all currently running processes.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦列举了主机，希望获得所有当前运行进程的列表

en_text: Frankenstein has used PowerShell to run a series of base64-encoded commands, that acted as a stager and enumerated hosts.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦使用PowerShell运行了一系列base64编码的命令，这些命令充当了暂存器并枚举了主机

en_text: Frankenstein has used WMI queries to detect if virtualization environments or analysis tools were running on the system.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦使用WMI查询来检测系统上是否运行了虚拟化环境或分析工具

en_text: Frankenstein has used WMI queries to check if various security applications were running, including VMWare and Virtualbox.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦使用WMI查询来检查各种安全应用程序是否正在运行，包括VMWare和Virtualbox

en_text: Frankenstein has used WMI queries to check if various security applications were running, as well as the operating system version.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦使用WMI查询来检查各种安全应用程序是否正在运行，以及操作系统的版本

en_text: Frankenstein has used MSbuild to execute an actor-created file.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦使用了MSbuild来执行一个演员创建的文件

en_text: Frankenstein has used trojanized documents that retrieve remote templates from an adversary-controlled website.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦使用了木马文件，从对手控制的网站检索远程模板

en_text: Frankenstein has used trojanized Microsoft Word documents sent via email, which prompted the victim to enable macros.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦使用了通过电子邮件发送的木马化微软Word文档，这促使受害者启用宏

en_text: Frankenstein has enumerated hosts via Empire, gathering various local system information.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦通过帝国列举了主机，收集各种本地系统信息

en_text: Frankenstein has collected information via Empire, which is automatically sent the data back to the adversary's C2.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦通过帝国收集信息，自动将数据发回给对手的C2

en_text: Frankenstein has communicated with a C2 via an encrypted RC4 byte stream and AES-CBC.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦通过加密的RC4字节流和AES-CBC与C2进行了通信

en_text: Frankenstein has established persistence through a scheduled task using the command:  /Create /F /SC DAILY /ST 09:00 /TN WinUpdate /TR , named "WinUpdate".
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦通过一个使用命令的计划任务建立了持久性

en_text: Frankenstein has run encoded commands from the command line.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦已经从命令行中运行了编码的命令

en_text: Frankenstein has enumerated hosts, gathering username, machine name, and administrative permissions information.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦已经列举了主机，收集了用户名、机器名称和管理权限信息

en_text: Frankenstein has uploaded and downloaded files to utilize additional plugins.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦已上传和下载文件，以利用额外的插件

en_text: Frankenstein has run a command script to set up persistence as a scheduled task named "WinUpdate", as well as other encoded commands from the command-line.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦运行了一个命令脚本，将持久性设置为一个名为 "WinUpdate "的计划任务，以及来自命令行的其他编码命令

en_text: Frankenstein has deobfuscated base64-encoded commands following the execution of a malicious script, which revealed a small script designed to obtain an additional payload.
Text: 弗兰肯斯坦在执行一个恶意脚本后对base64编码的命令进行了解构，发现一个旨在获得额外有效载荷的小脚本

en_text: Avenger has the ability to XOR encrypt files to be sent to C2.
Text: 复仇者具有XOR加密文件的能力，可以将其发送到C2

en_text: Avenger has the ability to download files from C2 to a compromised host.
Text: 复仇者有能力从C2下载文件到被攻击的主机

en_text: Avenger has the ability to use HTTP in communication with C2.
Text: 复仇者有能力在与C2的通信中使用HTTP

en_text: Various Lazarus Group malware enumerates logged-on users.
Text: 各种Lazarus集团的恶意软件列举了登录的用户

en_text: Various Lazarus Group malware modifies the Windows firewall to allow incoming connections or disable it entirely using netsh.
Text: 各种Lazarus集团的恶意软件修改了Windows防火墙，以允许进入的连接或使用netsh完全禁用它

en_text: Based on comparison of Gazer versions, Turla made an effort to obfuscate strings in the malware that could be used as IoCs, including the mutex name and named pipe.
Text: 根据对Gazer版本的比较，Turla努力混淆恶意软件中可用作IoC的字符串，包括突变器名称和命名管道

en_text: Adversaries can also use NETEAGLE to establish an RDP connection with a controller over TCP/7519.
Text: 攻击者也可以使用NETEAGLE通过TCP与控制器建立RDP连接

en_text: Skeleton Key is used to patch an enterprise domain controller authentication process with a backdoor password. It allows adversaries to bypass the standard authentication system to use a defined password for all accounts authenticating to that domain controller.
Text: 骨架钥匙是用来修补企业域控制器认证过程中的后门密码。它允许对手绕过标准认证系统，对所有认证到该域控制器的账户使用一个定义的密码。

en_text: Cobalt Strike can use process hollowing for execution.
Text: 钴罢工可以使用工艺空心化来执行。

en_text: BlackTech has used right-to-left-override to obfuscate the filenames of malicious e-mail attachments.
Text: 黑科技公司利用从右到左的覆盖来混淆恶意电子邮件附件的文件名

en_text: BlackTech has used e-mails with malicious links to lure victims into installing malware.
Text: 黑科技公司利用带有恶意链接的电子邮件，引诱受害者安装恶意软件

en_text: BlackTech has used e-mails with malicious documents to lure victims into installing malware.
Text: 黑科技公司利用带有恶意文件的电子邮件，引诱受害者安装恶意软件

en_text: BlackTech has used spearphishing e-mails with malicious documents to deliver malware.
Text: 黑科技公司利用带有恶意文件的鱼叉式网络钓鱼电子邮件来传递恶意软件

en_text: BlackTech has used spearphishing e-mails with links to cloud services to deliver malware.
Text: 黑科技公司利用带有云服务链接的鱼叉式钓鱼邮件来传递恶意软件

en_text: BlackTech has exploited a buffer overflow vulnerability in Microsoft Internet Information Services (IIS) 6.0, CVE-2017-7269, in order to establish a new HTTP or command and control (C2) server.
Text: 黑科技公司利用微软互联网信息服务（IIS）6.0中的缓冲区溢出漏洞，CVE-2017-7269，以建立一个新的HTTP或命令和控制（C2）服务器

en_text: BlackTech has exploited multiple vulnerabilities for execution, including Microsoft Office vulnerabilities CVE-2012-0158, CVE-2014-6352, CVE-2017-0199, and Adobe Flash CVE-2015-5119.
Text: 黑科技利用了多个漏洞进行执行，包括微软Office漏洞CVE-2012-0158、CVE-2014-6352、CVE-2017-0199和Adobe Flash CVE-2015-5119

en_text: Lateral movement can be done with Net through net use commands to connect to the on remote systems.
Text: 横向移动可以通过net使用命令来连接到远程系统上

en_text: The White Company has checked for specific antivirus products on the target’s computer, including Kaspersky, Quick Heal, AVG, BitDefender, Avira, Sophos, Avast!, and ESET.
Text: 怀特公司检查了目标计算机上的特定防病毒产品，包括卡巴斯基、Quick Heal、AVG、BitDefender、Avira、Sophos、Avast！和ESET

en_text: The White Company has taken advantage of a known vulnerability in Microsoft Word (CVE 2012-0158) to execute code.
Text: 怀特公司利用微软Word的一个已知漏洞（CVE 2012-0158）执行代码

en_text: The White Company has used phishing lure documents that trick users into opening them and infecting their computers.
Text: 怀特公司使用钓鱼诱骗文件，诱使用户打开文件并感染他们的电脑

en_text: The White Company has sent phishing emails with malicious Microsoft Word attachments to victims.
Text: 怀特公司向受害者发送了带有恶意微软Word附件的网络钓鱼邮件

en_text: The White Company has checked the current date on the victim system.
Text: 怀特公司已经检查了受害者系统上的当前日期

en_text: Whitefly has the ability to download additional tools from the C2.
Text: 惠特飞有能力从C2下载额外的工具

en_text: MuddyWater has used malware that checked if the ProgramData folder had folders or files with the keywords "Kasper," "Panda," or "ESET."
Text: 浑水公司曾使用恶意软件，检查ProgramData文件夹中是否有关键词 "Kasper"、"Panda "或 "ESET "的文件夹或文件

en_text: MuddyWater has base64 encoded C2 communications.
Text: 浑水公司对C2通信进行了base64编码

en_text: MuddyWater has performed credential dumping with LaZagne.
Text: 浑水公司对拉扎尼进行了证书倾销

en_text: MuddyWater has used C2 infrastructure to receive exfiltrated data.
Text: 浑水公司利用C2基础设施接收外泄的数据

en_text: MuddyWater has used malware to obtain a list of running processes on the system.
Text: 浑水公司利用恶意软件获得了系统中正在运行的进程列表

en_text: MuddyWater has used malware to collect the victim’s IP address and domain name.
Text: 浑水公司利用恶意软件收集受害者的IP地址和域名

en_text: MuddyWater has compromised third parties and used compromised accounts to send spearphishing emails with targeted attachments to recipients.
Text: 浑水公司破坏了第三方，并利用被破坏的账户向收件人发送带有目标附件的鱼叉式钓鱼邮件

en_text: MuddyWater has used the .NET csc.exe tool to compile executables from downloaded C# code.
Text: 浑水公司使用.NET csc.exe工具，从下载的C语言中编译可执行文件

en_text: MuddyWater has used malware that can capture screenshots of the victim’s machine.
Text: 浑水公司使用的恶意软件可以捕获受害者机器的屏幕截图

en_text: MuddyWater has used malware that can collect the victim’s OS version and machine name.
Text: 浑水公司使用的恶意软件可以收集受害者的操作系统版本和机器名称

en_text: MuddyWater has used malware that can collect the victim’s username.
Text: 浑水公司使用的恶意软件可以收集受害者的用户名

en_text: MuddyWater has used malware that can upload additional files to the victim’s machine.
Text: 浑水公司使用的恶意软件可以向受害者的机器上传额外的文件

en_text: MuddyWater uses various techniques to bypass UAC.
Text: 浑水公司使用各种技术来绕过UAC

en_text: MuddyWater has used a Word Template, Normal.dotm, for persistence.
Text: 浑水公司使用了一个Word模板，Normal.dotm，用于持久性

en_text: MuddyWater has used the native Windows cabinet creation tool, makecab.exe, likely to compress stolen data to be uploaded.
Text: 浑水公司使用了原生的Windows机柜创建工具makecab.exe，可能是为了压缩要上传的被盗数据

en_text: MuddyWater has used one C2 to obtain enumeration scripts and monitor web logs, but a different C2 to send data back.
Text: 浑水公司使用一个C2来获取枚举脚本和监控网络日志，但使用另一个C2来发送数据

en_text: MuddyWater has attempted to get users to enable macros and launch malicious Microsoft Word documents delivered via spearphishing emails.
Text: 浑水公司试图让用户启用宏并启动通过鱼叉式网络钓鱼邮件发送的恶意微软Word文档

en_text: MuddyWater has used HTTP for C2 communications.
Text: 浑水公司已将HTTP用于C2通信

en_text: MuddyWater has used PowerShell for execution.
Text: 浑水公司已经使用PowerShell来执行

en_text: MuddyWater has used scheduled tasks to establish persistence.
Text: 浑水公司已经使用计划任务来建立持久性

en_text: MuddyWater has performed credential dumping with Mimikatz.
Text: 浑水公司已经用Mimikatz进行了凭证倾销

en_text: MuddyWater has run a tool that steals passwords saved in victim email.
Text: 浑水公司已经运行了一个工具，可以窃取保存在受害者电子邮件中的密码

en_text: MuddyWater has run a tool that steals passwords saved in victim web browsers.
Text: 浑水公司已经运行了一个工具，可以窃取受害者网络浏览器中保存的密码

en_text: MuddyWater has exploited the Office vulnerability CVE-2017-0199 for execution.
Text: 浑水公司已利用Office漏洞CVE-2017-0199进行执行

en_text: MuddyWater has used malware to check running processes against a hard-coded list of security tools often used by malware researchers.
Text: 浑水公司用恶意软件对照恶意软件研究人员经常使用的安全工具的硬编码清单，检查正在运行的进程

en_text: Flame can use MS10-061 to exploit a print spooler vulnerability in a remote system with a shared printer in order to move laterally.
Text: 火焰可以利用MS10-061，在一个有共享打印机的远程系统中利用打印ooler漏洞，以便横向移动

en_text: Several Ke3chang backdoors achieved persistence by adding a Run key.
Text: 几个Ke3chang的后门通过添加一个运行密钥实现了持久性

en_text: Several Lazarus Group malware families install themselves as new services on victims.
Text: 几个Lazarus集团的恶意软件家族将自己作为新服务安装在受害者身上

en_text: Several Lazarus Group malware families use timestomping, including modifying the last write timestamp of a specified Registry key to a random date, as well as copying the timestamp for legitimate .exe files (such as calc.exe or mspaint.exe) to its dropped files.
Text: 几个Lazarus集团的恶意软件家族使用时间戳，包括将指定注册表键的最后写入时间戳修改为随机日期，以及将合法的.exe文件（如calc.exe或mspaint.exe）的时间戳复制到其丢弃的文件

en_text: Newer variants of BACKSPACE will encode C2 communications with a custom system.
Text: 较新的BACKSPACE变体将用一个自定义系统对C2通信进行编码

en_text: Gold Dragon stores information gathered from the endpoint in a file named 1.hwp.
Text: 金龙公司将从端点收集的信息存储在一个名为1.hwp的文件中

en_text: Gold Dragon enumerates registry keys with the command regkeyenum and obtains information for the Registry key HKEY_CURRENT_USER\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run.
Text: 金龙公司用regkeyenum命令枚举注册表键，获得注册表键HKEY_CURRENT_USER\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run的信息

en_text: Gold Dragon deletes one of its files, 2.hwp, from the endpoint after establishing persistence.
Text: 金龙公司在建立持久性之后，从端点删除了它的一个文件2.hwp

en_text: Gold Dragon encrypts data using Base64 before being sent to the command and control server.
Text: 金龙公司在向指挥和控制服务器发送数据之前，使用Base64进行加密

en_text: Gold Dragon checks for anti-malware products and processes.
Text: 金龙检查反恶意软件产品和程序

en_text: Gold Dragon can download additional components from the C2 server.
Text: 金龙可以从C2服务器下载额外的组件

en_text: Gold Dragon lists the directories for Desktop, program files, and the user’s recently accessed files.
Text: 金龙列出了桌面、程序文件和用户最近访问的文件的目录

en_text: Gold Dragon uses HTTP for communication to the control servers.
Text: 金龙使用HTTP与控制服务器进行通信

en_text: Gold Dragon collects the endpoint victim's username and uses it as a basis for downloading additional components from the C2 server.
Text: 金龙收集终端受害者的用户名，并将其作为从C2服务器下载额外组件的基础

en_text: Gold Dragon establishes persistence in the Startup folder.
Text: 金龙在启动文件夹中建立了持久性

en_text: Adversaries can direct BACKSPACE to execute from the command line on infected hosts, or have BACKSPACE create a reverse shell.
Text: 进攻者可以指示BACKSPACE在受感染的主机上从命令行执行，或者让BACKSPACE创建一个反向外壳

en_text: The net accounts and net accounts /domain commands with Net can be used to obtain password policy information.
Text: 净账户和净账户 净账户和净账目 帐户净值和帐户净值 净账户和净账户的

en_text: Orangeworm has used HTTP for C2.
Text: 桔子虫已将HTTP用于C2

en_text: Axiom has been observed using SQL injection to gain access to systems.
Text: 据观察，Axiom公司使用SQL注入来获取系统的访问权

en_text: Emotet has been observed adding the downloaded payload to the HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run key to maintain persistence.
Text: 据观察，Emotet将下载的有效载荷添加到HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run键中以保持持久性

en_text: Emotet has been observed to hook network APIs to monitor network traffic.
Text: 据观察，Emotet可以勾住网络API来监控网络流量

en_text: Emotet has been observed leveraging a module that scrapes email data from Outlook.
Text: 据观察，Emotet利用了一个从Outlook刮取电子邮件数据的模块

en_text: Emotet has been observed leveraging a module that retrieves passwords stored on a system for the current logged-on user.
Text: 据观察，Emotet利用了一个模块，为当前登录的用户检索存储在系统中的密码

en_text: Emotet has been observed leveraging a module that can scrape email addresses from Outlook.
Text: 据观察，Emotet利用一个模块，可以从Outlook中刮取电子邮件地址

en_text: Emotet has been observed using a hard coded list of passwords to brute force user accounts.
Text: 据观察，Emotet使用硬编码的密码列表来破解用户账户

en_text: Emotet has been observed injecting in to Explorer.exe and other processes.
Text: 据观察，Emotet已被注入到Explorer.exe和其他进程中

en_text: Emotet has been observed creating new services to maintain persistence.
Text: 据观察，Emotet已经创建了新的服务以保持持久性

en_text: Emotet has been observed encrypting the data it collects before sending it to the C2 server.
Text: 据观察，Emotet在向C2服务器发送数据之前对其收集的数据进行了加密

en_text: HOPLIGHT has been observed collecting victim machine information like OS version, drivers, volume information and more.
Text: 据观察，HOPLIGHT已经收集了受害者的机器信息，如操作系统版本、驱动程序、音量信息等

en_text: JCry has been observed deleting shadow copies to ensure that data cannot be restored easily.
Text: 据观察，JCry已经删除了影子副本，以确保数据不能被轻易恢复

en_text: LockerGoga has been observed moving around the victim network via SMB, indicating the actors behind this ransomware are manually copying files form computer to computer instead of self-propagating.
Text: 据观察，LockerGoga通过SMB在受害者网络中移动，这表明该勒索软件背后的行为者正在手动将文件从计算机复制到计算机，而不是自我传播

en_text: LockerGoga has been observed changing account passwords and logging off current users.
Text: 据观察，LockerGoga已经改变了账户密码并注销了当前用户

en_text: LockerGoga has been observed shutting down infected systems.
Text: 据观察，LockerGoga已经关闭了被感染的系统

en_text: POWERSOURCE has been observed being used to download TEXTMATE and the Cobalt Strike Beacon payload onto victims.
Text: 据观察，POWERSOURCE被用来向受害者下载TEXTMATE和Cobalt Strike Beacon有效载荷

en_text: StoneDrill has been observed deleting the temporary files once they fulfill their task.
Text: 据观察，StoneDrill在完成任务后会删除临时文件

en_text: WellMail has been observed using TCP port 25, without using SMTP, to leverage an open port for secure command and control communications.
Text: 据观察，WellMail使用TCP 25端口，而不使用SMTP，利用一个开放的端口进行安全的命令和控制通信

en_text: The APT1 group is known to have used pass the hash.
Text: 据了解，APT1集团已经使用了传递哈希值

en_text: The APT1 group is known to have used RDP during operations.
Text: 据了解，APT1集团在行动中使用了RDP

en_text: APT3 has been known to create or enable accounts, such as support_388945a0.
Text: 据了解，APT3会创建或启用账户，如support_388945a0

en_text: APT3 has been known to remove indicators of compromise from tools.
Text: 据了解，APT3会从工具中移除受损的指标

en_text: APT3 has been known to add created accounts to local admin groups to maintain elevated access.
Text: 据了解，APT3将创建的账户添加到本地管理组，以保持高等级访问

en_text: APT3 has been known to stage files for exfiltration in a single location.
Text: 据了解，APT3将文件放置在一个地方进行渗透

en_text: APT3 has been known to use -WindowStyle Hidden to conceal PowerShell windows.
Text: 据了解，APT3使用-WindowStyle Hidden来掩盖PowerShell窗口

en_text: APT3 has been known to side load DLLs with a valid version of Chrome with one of their tools.
Text: 据了解，APT3用他们的一个工具在有效版本的Chrome浏览器上侧载DLLs

en_text: Axiom has been known to dump credentials.
Text: 据了解，Axiom公司一直在倾销凭证

en_text: The Axiom group is known to have used RDP during operations.
Text: 据了解，Axiom集团在行动中使用了RDP

en_text: HAMMERTOSS is known to use PowerShell.
Text: 据了解，HAMMERTOSS使用PowerShell

en_text: Ke3chang actors have been known to copy files to the network shares of other computers to move laterally.
Text: 据了解，Ke3chang的行为者会将文件复制到其他计算机的网络共享中，以便横向移动

en_text: The Ke3chang group has been known to compress data before exfiltration.
Text: 据了解，Ke3chang集团在渗出前会对数据进行压缩

en_text: Sykipot is known to contain functionality that enables targeting of smart card technologies to proxy authentication for connections to restricted network resources using detected hardware tokens.
Text: 据了解，Sykipot包含的功能能够针对智能卡技术，使用检测到的硬件令牌代理认证连接到受限制的网络资源

en_text: Sykipot has been known to establish persistence by adding programs to the Run Registry key.
Text: 据了解，Sykipot通过将程序添加到运行注册表键来建立持久性

en_text: Tropic Trooper has been known to side-load DLLs using a valid version of a Windows Address Book and Windows Defender executable with one of their tools.
Text: 据了解，Tropic Trooper利用其工具之一的有效版本的Windows地址簿和Windows Defender可执行文件，侧面加载DLLs

en_text: Some variants of the Zeroaccess Trojan have been known to store data in Extended Attributes.
Text: 据了解，Zeroaccess木马的一些变种在扩展属性中存储数据

en_text: Cleaver has been known to dump credentials using Mimikatz and Windows Credential Editor.
Text: 据了解，克利夫利用Mimikatz和Windows凭证编辑器转储凭证

en_text: It is believed that a patch management system for an anti-virus product commonly installed among targeted companies was used to distribute the Wiper malware.
Text: 据认为，目标公司中普遍安装的一个反病毒产品的补丁管理系统被用来分发Wiper恶意软件

en_text: Carbon enumerates values in the Registry.
Text: 卡本列举了注册表中的值

en_text: Cardinal RAT contains watchdog functionality that periodically ensures HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Windows\Load is set to point to its executable.
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT包含看门狗功能，定期确保HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Windows\Load被设置为指向其可执行文件

en_text: Cardinal RAT contains watchdog functionality that ensures its process is always running, else spawns a new instance.
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT包含看门狗功能，确保其进程一直在运行，否则会产生一个新的实例

en_text: Cardinal RAT encodes many of its artifacts and is encrypted (AES-128) when downloaded.
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT对其许多工件进行编码，并在下载时进行了加密（AES-128）

en_text: Cardinal RAT decodes many of its artifacts and is decrypted (AES-128) after being downloaded.
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT对其许多神器进行解码，并在下载后被解密（AES-128）

en_text: Cardinal RAT and its watchdog component are compiled and executed after being delivered to victims as embedded, uncompiled source code.
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT及其看门狗组件在作为嵌入式、未编译的源代码交付给受害者后被编译和执行

en_text: Cardinal RAT can collect the hostname, Microsoft Windows version, and processor architecture from a victim machine.
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT可以收集受害者机器的主机名、微软Windows版本和处理器架构

en_text: Cardinal RAT is downloaded using HTTP over port 443.
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT是通过443端口的HTTP下载的

en_text: Cardinal RAT lures victims into executing malicious macros embedded within Microsoft Excel documents.
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT诱使受害者执行嵌入在微软Excel文档中的恶意宏

en_text: Cardinal RAT checks its current working directory upon execution and also contains watchdog functionality that ensures its executable is located in the correct path (else it will rewrite the payload).
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT在执行时检查其当前工作目录，还包含看门狗功能，确保其可执行文件位于正确的路径中（否则将重写有效载荷）。

en_text: Cardinal RAT injects into a newly spawned process created from a native Windows executable.
Text: 卡迪纳尔RAT注入到一个由本地Windows可执行文件创建的新生成的进程中

en_text: Kazuar can delete files.
Text: 卡苏尔可以删除文件

en_text: Kasidet creates a Registry Run key to establish persistence.
Text: 卡西德特创建了一个注册表运行键来建立持久性

en_text: Kasidet can execute commands using cmd.exe.
Text: 卡西德特可以使用cmd.exe执行命令

en_text: Kasidet has the ability to change firewall settings to allow a plug-in to be downloaded.
Text: 卡西德特有能力改变防火墙设置，以允许下载一个插件

en_text: Kasidet has the ability to obtain a victim's system name and operating system version.
Text: 卡西德特有能力获得受害者的系统名称和操作系统版本

en_text: Kasidet has the ability to initiate keylogging.
Text: 卡西德特有能力启动键盘记录功能

en_text: Kasidet has the ability to initiate keylogging and screen captures.
Text: 卡西德特有能力启动键盘记录和屏幕捕捉功能

en_text: Kasidet has the ability to identify any anti-virus installed on the infected system.
Text: 卡西德特有能力识别被感染系统上安装的任何反病毒软件

en_text: Kasidet has the ability to search for a given filename on a victim.
Text: 卡西德特有能力搜索受害者身上的特定文件名

en_text: Kasidet has the ability to download and execute additional files.
Text: 卡西德特有能力下载和执行其他文件

en_text: Kasidet has the ability to search for a given process name in processes currently running in the system.
Text: 卡西德特有能力在系统中当前运行的进程中搜索到某个特定的进程名称

en_text: Kazuar captures screenshots of the victim’s screen.
Text: 卡祖尔捕获了受害者的屏幕截图

en_text: Kazuar captures images from the webcam.
Text: 卡祖尔从网络摄像头捕捉图像

en_text: Kazuar can sleep for a specific time and be set to communicate at specific intervals.
Text: 卡祖尔可以在特定的时间内睡觉，并被设置为在特定的时间间隔内进行通信

en_text: Kazuar has used compromised WordPress blogs as C2 servers.
Text: 卡祖尔利用被入侵的WordPress博客作为C2服务器

en_text: Kazuar uses /bin/bash to execute commands on the victim’s machine.
Text: 卡祖尔使用 卡苏尔使用 卡祖尔用 卡祖尔采用

en_text: Kazuar gathers information on users.
Text: 卡祖尔收集了用户的信息

en_text: Kazuar gathers information about local groups and members.
Text: 卡祖尔收集了有关当地团体和成员的信息

en_text: Kazuar gathers information about opened windows.
Text: 卡祖尔收集有关打开的窗口的信息

en_text: Kazuar gathers information about network adapters.
Text: 卡祖尔收集有关网络适配器的信息

en_text: Kazuar obtains a list of running processes through WMI querying and the ps command.
Text: 卡祖尔通过WMI查询和ps命令获得运行进程的列表

en_text: Kazuar obtains a list of running processes through WMI querying.
Text: 卡祖尔通过WMI查询获得运行进程的列表

en_text: Kazuar stages command output and collected data in files before exfiltration.
Text: 卡祖尔在渗出前将命令输出和收集的数据放在文件中

en_text: Machete renamed task names to masquerade as legitimate Google Chrome, Java, Dropbox, Adobe Reader and Python tasks.
Text: 砍刀重命名任务名称，伪装成合法的谷歌浏览器、Java、Dropbox、Adobe Reader和Python任务

en_text: Comnie uses blogs and third-party sites (GitHub, tumbler, and BlogSpot) to avoid DNS-based blocking of their communication to the command and control server.
Text: 康尼使用博客和第三方网站（GitHub、tumbler和BlogSpot）来避免基于DNS的对其与指挥和控制服务器的通信的封锁

en_text: can collect the victim user name.
Text: 可以收集受害者的用户名

en_text: can collect system information, including computer name, system manufacturer, IsDebuggerPresent state, and execution path.
Text: 可以收集系统信息，包括计算机名称、系统制造商、IsDebuggerPresent状态和执行路径

en_text: can download and execute a second-stage payload.
Text: 可以下载并执行第二级的有效载荷

en_text: Expand can be used to download or upload a file over a network share.
Text: 扩展可以用来通过网络共享下载或上传文件

en_text: Expand can be used to download or copy a file into an alternate data stream.
Text: 扩展可以用来下载或复制一个文件到另一个数据流中

en_text: Ramsay has masqueraded as a JPG image file.
Text: 拉姆塞伪装成一个JPG图像文件

en_text: Lazarus Group malware attempts to maintain persistence by saving itself in the Start menu folder or by adding a Registry Run key.
Text: 拉扎勒斯集团的恶意软件试图通过将自己保存在 "开始 "菜单文件夹中或添加注册表运行键来保持持久性

en_text: C2 traffic from ADVSTORESHELL is encrypted, then encoded with Base64 encoding.
Text: 来自ADVSTORESHELL的C2流量是经过加密的，然后用Base64编码进行编码

en_text: Responses from the Pisloader C2 server are base32-encoded.
Text: 来自Pisloader C2服务器的响应是base32编码的

en_text: Blue Mockingbird has obfuscated the wallet address in the payload binary.
Text: 蓝色知更鸟 "混淆了有效载荷二进制文件中的钱包地址

en_text: Blue Mockingbird has masqueraded their XMRIG payload name by naming it wercplsupporte.dll after the legitimate wercplsupport.dll file.
Text: 蓝色知更鸟公司在合法的wercplsupport.dll文件之后，通过将其命名为wercplsupporte.dll来伪装他们的XMRIG有效载荷名称

en_text: Leviathan has received C2 instructions from user profiles created on legitimate websites such as Github and TechNet.
Text: 利维坦从Github和TechNet等合法网站上创建的用户档案中收到了C2指令

en_text: Leviathan has downloaded additional scripts and files from adversary-controlled servers.
Text: 利维坦从对手控制的服务器上下载了额外的脚本和文件

en_text: Leviathan has sent spearphishing emails with malicious attachments, including .rtf, .doc, and .xls files.
Text: 利维坦发送了带有恶意附件的鱼叉式钓鱼邮件，包括.rtf、.doc和.xls文件

en_text: Leviathan has sent spearphishing emails with links, often using a fraudulent lookalike domain and stolen branding.
Text: 利维坦发送了带有链接的鱼叉式钓鱼邮件，经常使用欺诈性的相似域名和偷来的品牌

en_text: Leviathan has used JavaScript to create a shortcut file in the Startup folder that points to its main backdoor.
Text: 利维坦利用JavaScript在启动文件夹中创建了一个指向其主要后门的快捷方式文件

en_text: Leviathan has exploited multiple Microsoft Office and .NET vulnerabilities for execution, including CVE-2017-0199, CVE-2017-8759, and CVE-2017-11882.
Text: 利维坦利用了多个微软Office和.NET漏洞进行执行，包括CVE-2017-0199、CVE-2017-8759和CVE-2017-11882

en_text: Leviathan has used a DLL known as SeDll to decrypt and execute other JavaScript backdoors.
Text: 利维坦利用一个被称为SeDll的DLL来解密和执行其他JavaScript后门

en_text: Leviathan has used valid, compromised email accounts for defense evasion, including to send malicious emails to other victim organizations.
Text: 利维坦利用有效的、被破坏的电子邮件账户进行防御规避，包括向其他受害组织发送恶意电子邮件

en_text: Leviathan has obfuscated code using base64 and gzip compression.
Text: 利维坦使用base64和gzip压缩来混淆代码

en_text: Leviathan has used BITSAdmin to download additional tools.
Text: 利维坦使用BITSAdmin下载了额外的工具

en_text: Leviathan used ssh for internal reconnaissance.
Text: 利维坦使用ssh进行内部侦察

en_text: Leviathan has used publicly available tools to dump password hashes, including ProcDump and WCE.
Text: 利维坦使用公开可用的工具来转储密码哈希值，包括ProcDump和WCE

en_text: Leviathan has used PowerShell for execution.
Text: 利维坦使用了PowerShell来执行

en_text: Leviathan has used regsvr32 for execution.
Text: 利维坦使用了regsvr32来执行

en_text: Leviathan has used VBScript.
Text: 利维坦使用了VBScript

en_text: Leviathan has used an uploader known as LUNCHMONEY that can exfiltrate files to Dropbox.
Text: 利维坦使用了一个被称为LUNCHMONEY的上传器，可以将文件外流到Dropbox

en_text: Leviathan has used stolen code signing certificates to sign malware.
Text: 利维坦使用偷来的代码签名证书来签署恶意软件

en_text: Leviathan uses a backdoor known as BADFLICK that is is capable of generating a reverse shell, and has used multiple types of scripting for execution, including JavaScript and JavaScript Scriptlets in XML..
Text: 利维坦使用一个被称为BADFLICK的后门，它能够生成一个反向外壳，并使用多种类型的脚本执行，包括XML中的JavaScript和JavaScript Scriptlets

en_text: Leviathan relies on web shells for an initial foothold as well as persistence into the victim's systems.
Text: 利维坦依靠网络外壳获得最初的立足点，并在受害者的系统中持久存在

en_text: Leviathan has sent spearphishing email links attempting to get a user to click.
Text: 利维坦已发送鱼叉式钓鱼电子邮件链接，试图让用户点击

en_text: Leviathan has sent spearphishing attachments attempting to get a user to click.
Text: 利维坦已经发送了鱼叉式钓鱼附件，试图让用户点击

en_text: Leviathan has used publicly available tools to dump password hashes, including HOMEFRY.
Text: 利维坦已经使用公开的工具来转储密码哈希值，包括HOMEFRY

en_text: Leviathan has targeted RDP credentials and used it to move through the victim environment.
Text: 利维坦以RDP凭证为目标，利用它在受害者环境中移动

en_text: Leviathan has inserted garbage characters into code, presumably to avoid anti-virus detection.
Text: 利维坦在代码中插入了垃圾字符，据推测是为了避免反病毒检测

en_text: route can be used to discover routing configuration information.
Text: 路由可以用来发现路由配置信息

en_text: Rocke's miner, "TermsHost.exe", evaded defenses by injecting itself into Windows processes, including Notepad.exe.
Text: 罗克的矿工 "TermsHost.exe "通过将自己注入Windows进程，包括Notepad.exe，逃避了防御措施

en_text: Helminth establishes persistence by creating a shortcut.
Text: 螺旋体通过创造一条捷径来建立持久性

en_text: Matroyshka uses DNS for C2.
Text: 马特罗伊什卡使用DNS进行C2

en_text: Anchor has come with a packed payload.
Text: 锚的到来，带来了满满的收获

en_text: Anchor can download additional payloads.
Text: 锚点可以下载额外的有效载荷

en_text: Anchor can create and execute services to load its payload.
Text: 锚可以创建和执行服务以加载其有效载荷

en_text: Anchor has been signed with valid certificates to evade detection by security tools.
Text: 锚已经用有效的证书签署，以躲避安全工具的检测

en_text: Maze operators have created scheduled tasks masquerading as "Windows Update Security", "Windows Update Security Patches", and "Google Chrome Security Update" designed to launch the ransomware.
Text: 迷宫操作员创建了伪装成 "Windows Update Security"、"Windows Update Security Patches "和 "Google Chrome Security Update "的计划任务，旨在启动勒索软件

en_text: Modules can be pushed to and executed by Duqu that copy data to a staging area, compress it, and XOR encrypt it.
Text: 模块可以被推送到并由Duqu执行，它将数据复制到一个暂存区，对其进行压缩，并进行XOR加密

en_text: Magic Hound malware has used IRC for C2.
Text: 魔法猎犬恶意软件已经使用IRC进行C2

en_text: Magic Hound has deleted and overwrote files to cover tracks.
Text: 魔法猎犬已经删除和重写了文件以掩盖痕迹

en_text: APIs and strings in some TYPEFRAME variants are RC4 encrypted. Another variant is encoded with XOR.
Text: 某些TYPEFRAME变体中的API和字符串是用RC4加密的

en_text: Naid creates Registry entries that store information about a created service and point to a malicious DLL dropped to disk.
Text: 奈德创建的注册表项存储了关于已创建服务的信息，并指向丢到磁盘上的恶意DLL

en_text: Naid creates a new service to establish.
Text: 奈德创建了一项新的服务，以建立

en_text: Naid collects a unique identifier (UID) from a compromised host.
Text: 奈德从被攻击的主机上收集一个唯一的标识符（UID）

en_text: Naid collects the domain name from a compromised host.
Text: 奈德从被破坏的主机上收集域名

en_text: Pupy can also perform pass-the-ticket.
Text: 普比也能进行传球

en_text: A module in Prikormka gathers logins and passwords stored in applications on the victims, including Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, and several other browsers.
Text: 普里科姆卡的一个模块收集存储在受害者的应用程序中的登录和密码，包括谷歌浏览器、Mozilla Firefox和其他几个浏览器

en_text: Chimera has used modified RAR software to archive data with a password.
Text: 奇美拉公司使用了修改过的RAR软件，用密码将数据存档

en_text: Chimera has has used net user /dom to enumerate domain accounts.
Text: 奇美拉已经使用了净用户 奇美拉已经使用了网友 奇美拉公司已经使用了净用户 奇美拉公司已经使用了网友

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 manipulated .lnk files to gather user credentials in conjunction with Forced Authentication.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0操纵.lnk文件，与强制认证一起收集用户凭证

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 queried the Registry to identify victim information.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0查询了登记处，以确定受害者信息

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 created accounts disguised as legitimate backup and service accounts as well as an email administration account.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0创建的账户伪装成合法的备份和服务账户以及一个电子邮件管理账户

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 collected data from local victim systems.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0从本地受害者系统收集数据

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 dropped and executed SecretsDump to dump password hashes. They also obtained ntds.dit from domain controllers.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0丢弃并执行SecretsDump以转储密码哈希值

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 has performed screen captures of victims, including by using a tool, scr.exe (which matched the hash of ScreenUtil).
Text: 蜻蜓2.0对受害者进行了屏幕捕捉，包括使用一个工具scr.exe（与ScreenUtil的哈希值相匹配）

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 dropped and executed SecretsDump to dump password hashes.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0放弃并执行SecretsDump以转储密码哈希值

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 has injected SMB URLs into malicious Word spearphishing attachments to initiate Forced Authentication.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0将SMB URL注入恶意的Word鱼叉式钓鱼附件中，以启动强制认证

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 added newly created accounts to the administrators group to maintain elevated access.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0将新创建的账户加入管理员组，以保持高等级访问

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 likely obtained a list of hosts in the victim environment.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0可能获得了受害者环境中的主机列表

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 has used various forms of spearphishing in attempts to get users to open attachments.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0利用各种形式的鱼叉式网络钓鱼，试图让用户打开附件

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used spearphishing with PDF attachments containing malicious links that redirected to credential harvesting websites.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0利用含有恶意链接的PDF附件进行鱼叉式网络钓鱼，该附件可重定向至凭证采集网站

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used spearphishing with Microsoft Office attachments to target victims.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0利用微软办公室的附件进行鱼叉式钓鱼，以受害者为目标

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 compromised legitimate organizations' websites to create watering holes to compromise victims.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0破坏了合法组织的网站，以创造水坑来危害受害者

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 deleted many of its files used during operations as part of cleanup, including removing applications and deleting screenshots.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0删除了许多操作过程中使用的文件，作为清理的一部分，包括删除应用程序和删除屏幕截图

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 identified and browsed file servers in the victim network, sometimes , viewing files pertaining to ICS or Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition (SCADA) systems.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0识别并浏览受害者网络中的文件服务器，有时查看与ICS或监督控制和数据采集（SCADA）系统有关的文件

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used PowerShell scripts for execution.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0使用PowerShell脚本来执行

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used SMB for C2.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0使用SMB进行C2

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used VPNs and Outlook Web Access (OWA) to maintain access to victim networks.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0使用VPN和Outlook Web Access（OWA）来维持对受害者网络的访问

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used various types of scripting to perform operations, including Python scripts. The group was observed installing Python 2.7 on a victim.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0使用各种类型的脚本来执行操作，包括Python脚本

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used various types of scripting to perform operations, including batch scripts.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0使用各种类型的脚本来执行操作，包括批处理脚本

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used scheduled tasks to automatically log out of created accounts every 8 hours as well as to execute malicious files.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0使用计划任务，每8小时自动注销创建的账户，并执行恶意文件

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 has used various forms of spearphishing in attempts to get users to open links.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0使用了各种形式的鱼叉式钓鱼，试图让用户打开链接

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used command line for execution.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0使用命令行来执行

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used a batch script to gather folder and file names from victim hosts.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0使用一个批处理脚本来收集受害者主机的文件夹和文件名

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 commonly created Web shells on victims' publicly accessible email and web servers, which they used to maintain access to a victim network and download additional malicious files.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0通常在受害者可公开访问的电子邮件和网络服务器上创建Web shells，它们用来保持对受害者网络的访问并下载额外的恶意文件

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 moved laterally via RDP.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0通过RDP横向移动

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 has gathered hashed user credentials over SMB using spearphishing attachments with external resource links and by modifying .LNK file icon resources to collect credentials from virtualized systems.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0通过SMB收集散列的用户凭证，使用带有外部资源链接的鱼叉式钓鱼附件，并通过修改.LNK文件图标资源，从虚拟化系统收集凭证

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 dropped and executed tools used for password cracking, including Hydra and CrackMapExec.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0投放并执行了用于密码破解的工具，包括Hydra和CrackMapExec

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 compromised user credentials and used valid accounts for operations.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0泄露了用户凭证，并使用有效账户进行操作

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 modified the Registry to perform multiple techniques through the use of Reg.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0修改了注册表，通过使用Reg.Ltd.来执行多种技术

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 has disabled host-based firewalls. The group has also globally opened port 3389.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0已禁用基于主机的防火墙

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 compressed data into .zip files prior to exfiltrating it.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0在渗出数据之前将其压缩成.zip文件

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 copied and installed tools for operations once in the victim environment.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0在受害者环境中复制并安装了操作的工具

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 created accounts on victims, including administrator accounts, some of which appeared to be tailored to each individual staging target.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0在受害者身上创建了账户，包括管理员账户，其中一些账户似乎是为每个单独的集结目标量身定做的

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 used the command query user on victim hosts.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0在受害者主机上使用查询用户的命令

en_text: Dragonfly 2.0 added the registry value ntdll to the Registry Run key to establish persistence.
Text: 蜻蜓2.0在注册表运行键中增加了注册表值ntdll，以建立持久性

en_text: Dragonfly has used spearphising campaigns to gain access to victims.
Text: 蜻蜓公司利用鱼叉式营销活动来获得受害者

en_text: Dragonfly has has compromised targets via strategic web compromise (SWC) utilizing a custom exploit kit.
Text: 蜻蜓公司通过战略网络妥协（SWC）利用一个定制的漏洞工具包入侵了目标

en_text: Dragonfly has placed trojanized installers on legitimate vendor app stores.
Text: 蜻蜓公司在合法的供应商应用商店中放置了木马安装程序

en_text: SQLRat has used been observed deleting scripts once used.
Text: 人们曾观察到SQLRat删除了曾经使用过的脚本

en_text: APT39 has been seen using RDP for lateral movement and persistence, in some cases employing the rdpwinst tool for mangement of multiple sessions.
Text: 人们看到APT39使用RDP进行横向移动和持久性，在某些情况下采用rdpwinst工具来管理多个会话

en_text: Emotet has been seen exfiltrating system information stored within cookies sent within an HTTP GET request back to its C2 servers.
Text: 人们看到Emotet将存储在HTTP GET请求中的cookie中的系统信息渗透回其C2服务器

en_text: Okrum was seen using MimikatzLite to perform credential dumping.
Text: 人们看到Okrum使用MimikatzLite来进行凭证转储

en_text: Okrum was seen using NetSess to discover NetBIOS sessions.
Text: 人们看到Okrum使用NetSess来发现NetBIOS会话

en_text: Okrum was seen using modified Quarks PwDump to perform credential dumping.
Text: 人们看到Okrum使用修改过的Quarks PwDump来进行凭证转储

en_text: SamSam has been seen deleting its own files and payloads to make analysis of the attack more difficult.
Text: 人们看到SamSam删除了自己的文件和有效载荷，使攻击的分析更加困难

en_text: SamSam has been seen using AES or DES to encrypt payloads and payload components.
Text: 人们已经看到SamSam使用AES或DES来加密有效载荷和有效载荷组件

en_text: Shamoon has been seen overwriting features of disk structure such as the MBR.
Text: 人们已经看到Shamoon覆盖了磁盘结构的特征，如MBR

en_text: Tasklist can be used to discover services running on a system.
Text: 任务列表可以用来发现系统上运行的服务

en_text: Tasklist can be used to discover processes running on a system.
Text: 任务列表可以用来发现系统上运行的进程

en_text: Tasklist can be used to enumerate security software currently running on a system by process name of known products.
Text: 任务列表可用于按已知产品的进程名称列举当前在系统上运行的安全软件

en_text: RDAT has used HTTP if DNS C2 communications were not functioning.
Text: 如果DNS C2通信不正常，RDAT曾使用HTTP

en_text: Machete has sent data over HTTP if FTP failed, and has also used a fallback server.
Text: 如果FTP失败，Machete已经通过HTTP发送数据，并且还使用了一个回退服务器

en_text: If NETEAGLE does not detect a proxy configured on the infected machine, it will send beacons via UDP/6000. Also, after retrieving a C2 IP address and Port Number, NETEAGLE will initiate a TCP connection to this socket. The ensuing connection is a plaintext C2 channel in which commands are specified by DWORDs.
Text: 如果NETEAGLE没有检测到被感染机器上配置的代理，它将通过UDP/6000发送信标。此外，在检索到C2的IP地址和端口号后，NETEAGLE将启动一个TCP连接到这个套接字。随后的连接是一个明文C2通道，其中的命令是由DWORD指定的。

en_text: SDBot has the ability to use image file execution options for persistence if it detects it is running with admin privileges on a Windows version newer than Windows 7.
Text: 如果SDBot检测到它是以管理员权限在比Windows 7更新的Windows版本上运行，它就有能力使用图像文件执行选项来实现持久性

en_text: SDBot has the ability to add a value to the Registry Run key to establish persistence if it detects it is running with regular user privilege.
Text: 如果SDBot检测到它是以普通用户权限运行的，它有能力向注册表运行键添加一个值以建立持久性

en_text: SDBot has the ability to use application shimming for persistence if it detects it is running as admin on Windows XP or 7, by creating a shim database to patch services.exe.
Text: 如果SDBot检测到它在Windows XP或7上以管理员身份运行，它就有能力使用应用程序修饰来实现持久性，方法是创建一个修饰数据库来修补services.exe

en_text: If Shamoon cannot access shares using current privileges, it attempts access using hard coded, domain-specific credentials gathered earlier in the intrusion.
Text: 如果Shamoon不能使用当前的权限访问共享，它就会尝试使用在入侵过程中早期收集的硬编码的、特定于域的凭证进行访问

en_text: GravityRAT steals files based on an extension list if a USB drive is connected to the system.
Text: 如果USB驱动器连接到系统，GravityRAT会根据扩展列表窃取文件

en_text: Xbash can create a cronjob for persistence if it determines it is on a Linux system.
Text: 如果Xbash确定它是在Linux系统上，它可以创建一个cronjob来进行持久化

en_text: Xbash can create a Startup item for persistence if it determines it is on a Windows system.
Text: 如果Xbash确定它是在一个Windows系统上，它可以创建一个用于持久化的启动项

en_text: Anchor can terminate itself if specific execution flags are not present.
Text: 如果不存在特定的执行标志，Anchor可以自行终止

en_text: CHOPSTICK can switch to a new C2 channel if the current one is broken.
Text: 如果当前的C2通道被破坏，CHOPSTICK可以切换到一个新的C2通道

en_text: An APT28 loader Trojan will enumerate the victim's processes searching for explorer.exe if its current process does not have necessary permissions.
Text: 如果当前进程没有必要的权限，APT28加载器木马将列举受害者的进程来搜索explorer.exe

en_text: Gold Dragon terminates anti-malware processes if they’re found running on the system.
Text: 如果发现反恶意软件进程在系统上运行，金龙会终止它们

en_text: gh0st RAT can execute its service if the Service key exists. If the key does not exist, gh0st RAT will create and run the service.
Text: 如果服务密钥存在，gh0st RAT可以执行其服务

en_text: PoetRAT has the ability to overwrite scripts and delete itself if a sandbox environment is detected.
Text: 如果检测到沙盒环境，PoetRAT有能力覆盖脚本并删除自己

en_text: If installing itself as a service fails, Elise instead writes itself as a file named svchost.exe saved in %APPDATA%\Microsoft\Network.
Text: 如果将自己作为服务安装失败，Elise会将自己写成一个名为svchost.exe的文件，保存在%APPDATA%\Microsoft/Network

en_text: Exaramel for Linux uses crontab for persistence if it does not have root privileges.
Text: 如果没有root权限，Linux的Exaramel使用crontab进行持久化

en_text: Duqu can be configured to have commands relayed over a peer-to-peer network of infected hosts if some of the hosts do not have Internet access.
Text: 如果某些主机没有互联网接入，Duqu可以被配置为让命令通过受感染主机的对等网络转发

en_text: MiniDuke uses Google Search to identify C2 servers if its primary C2 method via Twitter is not working.
Text: 如果其通过Twitter的主要C2方法不起作用，MiniDuke使用谷歌搜索来识别C2服务器

en_text: Empire has a module for creating a new domain user if permissions allow.
Text: 如果权限允许，Empire有一个模块可以创建一个新的域用户

en_text: If a victim meets certain criteria, T9000 uses the AppInit_DLL functionality to achieve persistence by ensuring that every user mode process that is spawned will load its malicious DLL, ResN32.dll. It does this by creating the following Registry keys: HKLM\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Windows\AppInit_DLLs C %APPDATA%\Intel\ResN32.dll and HKLM\Software\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Windows\LoadAppInit_DLLs C 0x1.
Text: 如果受害者符合某些条件，T9000就会使用AppInit_DLL功能来实现持久性，确保生成的每个用户模式进程都会加载其恶意的DLL，ResN32.dll。它通过创建以下注册表键来实现这一目的。HKLM\Software\MicrosoftWindows NT\CurrentVersion\Windows\AppInit_DLLs - %APPDATA%\Intel\ResN32.dll和HKLM\Software\MicrosoftWindows NT\CurrentVersion\WindowsLoadAppInit_DLLs - 0x1。

en_text: If the victim is using PowerShell 3.0 or later, POWERSOURCE writes its decoded payload to an alternate data stream (ADS) named kernel32.dll that is saved in %PROGRAMDATA%\Windows\.
Text: 如果受害者使用PowerShell 3.0或更高版本，POWERSOURCE将其解码后的有效载荷写入一个名为kernel32.dll的备用数据流（ADS），该数据流被保存在%PROGRAMDATA%/Windows/

en_text: If establishing persistence by installation as a new service fails, one variant of Elise establishes persistence for the created .exe file by setting the following Registry key: HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\svchost : %APPDATA%\Microsoft\Network\svchost.exe. Other variants have set the following Registry keys for persistence: HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\imejp : [self] and HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\IAStorD.
Text: 如果通过安装为新服务建立持久性失败，Elise的一个变种通过设置以下注册表键为创建的.exe文件建立持久性： HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\svchost : %APPDATA%\Microsoft\Network\svchost.exe。其他变种设置了以下注册表键值用于持久化。HKCU\Software\MicrosoftWindows\CurrentVersion\Run\imejp 。[self] 和 HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\IAStorD.

en_text: Carbanak exfiltrates data in compressed chunks if a message is larger than 4096 bytes .
Text: 如果一个信息大于4096字节，Carbanak会以压缩块的形式渗出数据

en_text: If running as administrator, TDTESS installs itself as a new service named bmwappushservice to establish persistence.
Text: 如果以管理员身份运行，TDTESS将自己安装成一个名为bmwappushservice的新服务以建立持久性

en_text: Flame can create backdoor accounts with login "HelpAssistant" on domain connected systems if appropriate rights are available.
Text: 如果有适当的权限，Flame可以在域连接的系统上创建具有 "HelpAssistant "登录的后门账户

en_text: RedLeaves can communicate to its C2 over HTTP and HTTPS if directed.
Text: 如果有指示，RedLeaves可以通过HTTP和HTTPS与它的C2通信

en_text: CCBkdr can use a DGA for Fallback Channels if communications with the primary command and control server are lost.
Text: 如果与主命令和控制服务器的通信丢失，CCBkdr可以使用DGA作为回退通道

en_text: LoudMiner can automatically launch a Linux virtual machine as a service at startup if the AutoStart option is enabled in the VBoxVmService configuration file.
Text: 如果在 VBoxVmService 配置文件中启用了 AutoStart 选项，LoudMiner 可以在启动时自动将 Linux 虚拟机作为一项服务启动

en_text: If running in a Windows environment, Kazuar saves a DLL to disk that is injected into the explorer.exe process to execute the payload. Kazuar can also be configured to inject and execute within specific processes.
Text: 如果在Windows环境下运行，Kazuar会将一个DLL保存到磁盘上，然后注入explorer.exe进程以执行有效载荷

en_text: Kessel can use a proxy during exfiltration if set in the configuration.
Text: 如果在配置中设置，Kessel可以在渗出过程中使用代理

en_text: Empire can add a SID-History to a user if on a domain controller.
Text: 如果在域控制器上，帝国可以为一个用户添加一个SID-历史

en_text: Gazer stores configuration items in alternate data streams (ADSs) if the Registry is not accessible.
Text: 如果注册表无法访问，Gazer将配置项存储在备用数据流（ADS）中

en_text: If an initial connectivity check fails, pngdowner attempts to extract proxy details and credentials from Windows Protected Storage and from the IE Credentials Store. This allows the adversary to use the proxy credentials for subsequent requests if they enable outbound HTTP access.
Text: 如果最初的连接性检查失败，pngdowner会试图从Windows保护存储和IE凭证库中提取代理细节和凭证。这使得对手可以在随后的请求中使用代理凭证，如果他们启用了出站的HTTP访问。

en_text: Soft Cell used ipconfig /all to obtain information about the victim network configuration. The group also ran a modified version of nbtscan to identify available NetBIOS name servers.
Text: 软体细胞使用了ipconfig 软性细胞使用了ipconfig 软体细胞使用的是ipconfig 软性细胞使用的是ipconfig

en_text: Soft Cell used Web shells and HTRAN for C2 as well as to exfiltrate data.
Text: 软体细胞使用网络外壳和HTRAN进行C2以及渗出数据

en_text: Sandworm Team's BCS-server tool can create an internal proxy server to redirect traffic from the adversary-controlled C2 to internal servers which may not be connected to the internet, but are interconnected locally.
Text: 沙虫团队的BCS-服务器工具可以创建一个内部代理服务器，将流量从对手控制的C2重定向到内部服务器，这些服务器可能没有连接到互联网，但在本地是相互连接的

en_text: Sandworm Team has used intercepter-NG to sniff passwords in network traffic.
Text: 沙虫团队利用拦截器-NG来嗅探网络流量中的密码

en_text: Sandworm Team has used remote administration tools or remote industrial control system client software to maliciously release electricity breakers.
Text: 沙虫团队利用远程管理工具或远程工业控制系统客户端软件，恶意释放断电装置

en_text: Sandworm Team has sent system information to its C2 server using HTTP.
Text: 沙虫团队使用HTTP向其C2服务器发送系统信息

en_text: Sandworm Team has used port 6789 to accept connections on the group's SSH server.
Text: 沙虫团队使用了6789端口来接受该组织SSH服务器的连接

en_text: Sandworm Team used a backdoor to enumerate information about the infected system's operating system.
Text: 沙虫团队使用一个后门来列举被感染系统的操作系统信息

en_text: Sandworm Team has exploited vulnerabilities in Microsoft PowerPoint via OLE objects (CVE-2014-4114) and Microsoft Word via crafted TIFF images (CVE-2013-3906).
Text: 沙虫团队通过OLE对象（CVE-2014-4114）和微软Word通过制作的TIFF图像（CVE-2013-3906）利用了微软PowerPoint中的漏洞

en_text: Sandworm Team has created VBScripts to run an SSH server.
Text: 沙虫团队已经创建了VBS脚本来运行SSH服务器

en_text: Sandworm Team have used previously acquired legitimate credentials prior to attacks.
Text: 沙虫团队在攻击前使用了之前获得的合法凭证
