en_text: Deep Panda uses net.exe to connect to network shares using net use commands with compromised credentials.
Text: 深度熊猫使用net.exe连接到网络共享，使用net使用命令与被破坏的凭证

en_text: Deep Panda uses Web shells on publicly accessible Web servers to access victim networks.
Text: 深度熊猫使用公开访问的网络服务器上的Web shells来访问受害者网络

en_text: Net commands used with the /domain flag can be used to gather information about and manipulate user accounts on the current domain.
Text: 带有/domain标志的Net命令可以用来收集关于当前域的用户账户的信息并进行操作。

en_text: After data is collected by Stealth Falcon malware, it is exfiltrated over the existing C2 channel.
Text: 数据被Stealth Falcon恶意软件收集后，会通过现有的C2渠道流出

en_text: Data exfiltration is done by Okrum using the already opened channel with the C2 server.
Text: 数据渗出是由Okrum利用已经打开的C2服务器的通道完成的

en_text: TajMahal has the ability to capture webcam video.
Text: 泰姬玛哈有捕获网络摄像头视频的能力

en_text: Carbon uses the net view command.
Text: 碳使用net view命令

en_text: Agent Tesla has had its code obfuscated in an apparent attempt to make analysis difficult. Agent Tesla has used the Rijndael symmetric encryption algorithm to encrypt strings.
Text: 特斯拉代理的代码被混淆了，显然是为了使分析变得困难

en_text: Agent Tesla can collect the timestamp from the victim’s machine.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以从受害者的机器上收集时间戳

en_text: Agent Tesla can collect the username from the victim’s machine.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以从受害者的机器上收集用户名

en_text: Agent Tesla can collect account information from the victim’s machine.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以从受害者的机器上收集账户信息

en_text: Agent Tesla can steal data from the victim’s clipboard.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以从受害者的剪贴板上窃取数据

en_text: Agent Tesla can log keystrokes on the victim’s machine.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以记录受害者机器上的击键

en_text: Agent Tesla can add itself to the Registry as a startup program to establish persistence.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以将自己添加到注册表中作为启动程序，以建立持久性

en_text: Agent Tesla can list the current running processes on the system.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以列出系统上当前运行的进程

en_text: Agent Tesla can collect the IP address of the victim machine.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以收集受害者机器的IP地址

en_text: Agent Tesla can collect the system's computer name and also has the capability to collect information on the processor, memory, OS, and video card from the system.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以收集系统的计算机名称，也有能力收集系统的处理器、内存、操作系统和显卡的信息

en_text: Agent Tesla can download additional files for execution on the victim’s machine.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以下载额外的文件，在受害者的机器上执行

en_text: Agent Tesla can encrypt data with 3DES before sending it over to a C2 server.
Text: 特斯拉代理可以在向C2服务器发送数据之前用3DES加密

en_text: Agent Tesla has used ProcessWindowStyle.Hidden to hide windows.
Text: 特斯拉代理已经使用ProcessWindowStyle.Hidden来隐藏窗口

en_text: Agent Tesla has used SMTP for C2 communications.
Text: 特斯拉代理已经使用SMTP进行C2通信

en_text: Agent Tesla has used HTTP for C2 communications.
Text: 特斯拉代理已使用HTTP进行C2通信。

en_text: Agent Tesla has been executed through malicious e-mail attachments
Text: 特斯拉代理已通过恶意的电子邮件附件被执行

en_text: Agent Tesla has the ability to steal credentials from FTP clients and wireless profiles.
Text: 特斯拉代理有能力从FTP客户端和无线配置文件中窃取凭证

en_text: Agent Tesla has the ability to decrypt strings encrypted with the Rijndael symmetric encryption algorithm.
Text: 特斯拉代理有能力解密用Rijndael对称加密算法加密的字符串

en_text: Agent Tesla has he ability to perform anti-sandboxing and anti-virtualization checks.
Text: 特斯拉代理有能力进行反沙盒化和反虚拟化检查

en_text: Agent Tesla has the capability to kill any running analysis processes and AV software.
Text: 特斯拉代理有能力杀死任何正在运行的分析进程和AV软件

en_text: Agent Tesla has the ability to use form-grabbing to extract data from web data forms.
Text: 特斯拉代理有能力使用表格抓取功能，从网络数据表格中提取数据

en_text: Agent Tesla has routines for exfiltration over SMTP, FTP, and HTTP.
Text: 特斯拉代理有通过SMTP、FTP和HTTP进行渗出的程序

en_text: Agent Tesla can capture screenshots of the victim’s desktop.
Text: 特斯拉特工可以捕获受害者桌面的屏幕截图

en_text: Agent Tesla can access the victim’s webcam and record video.
Text: 特斯拉特工可以进入受害者的网络摄像头并录制视频

en_text: Stolen Pencil gathers credentials using Mimikatz and Procdump.
Text: 偷来的铅笔 "使用Mimikatz和Procdump收集凭证

en_text: Stolen Pencil has used tools that are capable of obtaining credentials from saved mail.
Text: 偷来的铅笔 "使用了能够从保存的邮件中获取凭证的工具

en_text: Turla has infected victims using watering holes.
Text: 图拉利用浇水孔感染了受害者

en_text: Valak has the ability to exfiltrate data over the C2 channel.
Text: 瓦拉克有能力通过C2渠道渗出数据

en_text: Machete captures screenshots.
Text: 弯刀捕捉屏幕截图

en_text: Machete takes photos from the computer’s web camera.
Text: 弯刀从电脑的网络摄像头拍摄照片

en_text: Machete logs keystrokes from the victim’s machine.
Text: 弯刀记录了受害者机器上的按键

en_text: Machete uses HTTP for Command & Control.
Text: 弯刀使用HTTP进行指挥 弯刀使用HTTP来指挥 弯刀使用HTTP进行命令 弯刀使用HTTP进行指令

en_text: Machete used the startup folder for persistence.
Text: 弯刀使用启动文件夹进行持久化

en_text: Machete has been packed with NSIS.
Text: 弯刀已被装入NSIS

en_text: Net Crawler uses a list of known credentials gathered through credential dumping to guess passwords to accounts as it spreads throughout a network.
Text: 网络爬虫使用通过凭证转储收集的已知凭证列表，在整个网络中传播时猜测账户的密码

en_text: After compromising a victim, Poseidon Group lists all running processes.
Text: 危害受害者后，波塞冬集团会列出所有正在运行的进程

en_text: Threat Group-1314 actors used compromised domain credentials for the victim's endpoint management platform, Altiris, to move laterally.
Text: 威胁集团-1314行动者利用受害者的端点管理平台Altiris的受损域名凭证进行横向移动

en_text: Threat Group-1314 actors used a victim's endpoint management platform, Altiris, for lateral movement.
Text: 威胁集团-1314行动者利用受害者的端点管理平台Altiris进行横向移动

en_text: Threat Group-1314 actors spawned shells on remote systems on a victim network to execute commands.
Text: 威胁集团-1314行动者在受害者网络的远程系统上生成外壳，执行命令

en_text: Threat Group-1314 actors mapped network drives using net use.
Text: 威胁集团-1314行为者使用净使用映射了网络驱动器

en_text: Threat Group-3390 malware has used HTTP for C2.
Text: 威胁集团-3390恶意软件已使用HTTP进行C2

en_text: Threat Group-3390 actors have used gsecdump to dump credentials. They have also dumped credentials from domain controllers.
Text: 威胁集团--3390个行为者使用gsecdump转储凭证

en_text: Threat Group-3390 actors use nbtscan to discover vulnerable systems.
Text: 威胁集团-3390个行为者使用NBTScan来发现脆弱的系统

en_text: A Threat Group-3390 tool can create a new service, naming it after the config information, to gain persistence.
Text: 威胁集团-3390工具可以创建一个新的服务，用配置信息命名，以获得持久性

en_text: A Threat Group-3390 tool can spawn svchost.exe and inject the payload into that process.
Text: 威胁集团-3390工具可以催生svchost.exe并将有效载荷注入该进程

en_text: A Threat Group-3390 tool can read and decrypt stored Registry values.
Text: 威胁集团-3390工具可以读取和解密存储的注册表值

en_text: A Threat Group-3390 tool can add the binary’s path to the Registry key Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run to add persistence.
Text: 威胁集团-3390工具可以将二进制文件的路径添加到注册表键Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run中以增加持久性

en_text: A Threat Group-3390 tool can use WMI to execute a binary.
Text: 威胁集团-3390工具可以使用WMI来执行二进制

en_text: A Threat Group-3390 tool can use a public UAC bypass method to elevate privileges.
Text: 威胁集团-3390工具可以使用公共UAC绕过方法来提升权限

en_text: A Threat Group-3390 tool can create a new Registry key under HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Classes\.
Text: 威胁集团-3390工具可以在HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Classes/下创建一个新的注册表键

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has performed DLL search order hijacking to execute their payload.
Text: 威胁集团-3390进行了DLL搜索顺序劫持，以执行其有效载荷

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used net user to conduct internal discovery of systems.
Text: 威胁集团-3390利用网友对系统进行内部发现

en_text: Threat Group-3390 actors have split RAR files for exfiltration into parts.
Text: 威胁集团-3390名行为人将RAR文件分割成若干部分进行渗出

en_text: Threat Group-3390 actors have used a modified version of Mimikatz called Wrapikatz to dump credentials. They have also dumped credentials from domain controllers.
Text: 威胁集团--3390名行为人使用了名为Wrapikatz的Mimikatz修改版来转储凭证

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used PowerShell for execution.
Text: 威胁集团-3390使用了PowerShell进行执行

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used command-line interfaces for execution.
Text: 威胁集团-3390使用了命令行接口来执行

en_text: Threat Group-3390 actors obtain legitimate credentials using a variety of methods and use them to further lateral movement on victim networks.
Text: 威胁集团-3390行动者利用各种方法获得合法的证书，并利用它们在受害者网络上进一步横向移动

en_text: Threat Group-3390 actors use at to schedule tasks to run self-extracting RAR archives, which install HTTPBrowser or PlugX on other victims on a network.
Text: 威胁集团-3390行动者使用at来安排任务，运行自解压的RAR档案，在网络上的其他受害者身上安装HTTPBrowser或PlugX

en_text: Threat Group-3390 actors use the Hunter tool to conduct network service discovery for vulnerable systems.
Text: 威胁集团-3390行为者使用Hunter工具对脆弱系统进行网络服务发现

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has exploited MS17-101 to move laterally to other systems on the network.
Text: 威胁集团-3390已经利用MS17-101横向移动到网络上的其他系统

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has deleted existing logs and exfiltrated file archives from a victim.
Text: 威胁集团-3390已经删除了现有的日志，并从受害者那里渗出了文件档案

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used net use to conduct internal discovery of systems. The group has also used quser.exe to identify existing RDP sessions on a victim.
Text: 威胁集团-3390已经使用net use对系统进行内部发现

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used the net view command.
Text: 威胁集团-3390已经使用了net view命令

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used RAR to compress, encrypt, and password-protect files prior to exfiltration.
Text: 威胁集团-3390在渗出前使用RAR压缩、加密和密码保护文件

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has detached network shares after exfiltrating files, likely to evade detection.
Text: 威胁集团-3390在渗出文件后分离了网络共享，可能是为了逃避检测

en_text: Threat Group-3390 ran a command to compile an archive of file types of interest from the victim user's directories.
Text: 威胁小组-3390运行了一个命令，从受害者用户的目录中编译出一个感兴趣的文件类型的档案

en_text: A Threat Group-3390 tool can encrypt payloads using XOR. Threat Group-3390 malware is also obfuscated using Metasploit’s shikata_ga_nai encoder as well as compressed with LZNT1 compression.
Text: 威胁组织-3390工具可以使用XOR对有效载荷进行加密

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has extensively used strategic web compromises to target victims.
Text: 威胁组织-3390广泛地利用战略性的网络妥协来锁定受害者

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used CVE-2014-6324 to escalate privileges.
Text: 威胁组织-3390利用CVE-2014-6324升级了权限

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used WinRM to enable remote execution.
Text: 威胁组织-3390利用WinRM来实现远程执行

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used appcmd.exe to disable logging on a victim server.
Text: 威胁组织-3390使用appcmd.exe禁用受害者服务器上的日志记录

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used DLL side-loading, including by using legitimate Kaspersky antivirus variants in which the DLL acts as a stub loader that loads and executes the shell code.
Text: 威胁组织-3390使用了DLL侧面加载，包括使用合法的卡巴斯基杀毒软件变种，其中DLL作为存根加载器，加载和执行壳代码

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has used a variety of Web shells.
Text: 威胁组织-3390使用了各种网络外壳

en_text: Threat Group-3390 actors look for and use VPN profiles during an operation to access the network using external VPN services. Threat Group-3390 has also obtained OWA account credentials during intrusions that it subsequently used to attempt to regain access when evicted from a victim network.
Text: 威胁组织-3390行动者在行动中寻找并使用VPN配置文件，使用外部VPN服务访问网络。威胁组织-3390还在入侵期间获得了OWA账户凭证，随后在被逐出受害者网络时用来试图重新获得访问权。

en_text: Threat Group-3390 actors installed a credential logger on Microsoft Exchange servers. Threat Group-3390 also leveraged the reconnaissance framework, ScanBox, to capture keystrokes.
Text: 威胁组织-3390行为人在微软Exchange服务器上安装了一个凭证记录器。威胁组织-3390还利用侦察框架ScanBox来捕获键盘信息。

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has moved staged encrypted archives to Internet-facing servers that had previously been compromised with China Chopper prior to exfiltration.
Text: 威胁组织-3390已经将阶段性的加密档案转移到面向互联网的服务器上，这些服务器在渗出之前已经被中国斩波器攻破

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has exploited the Microsoft SharePoint vulnerability CVE-2019-0604.
Text: 威胁组织-3390已经利用了微软SharePoint的漏洞CVE-2019-0604

en_text: Threat Group-3390 has locally staged encrypted archives for later exfiltration efforts.
Text: 威胁组织-3390在本地存放了加密档案，以便日后进行渗出

en_text: To establish persistence, Okrum can install itself as a new service named NtmSsvc.
Text: 为了建立持久性，Okrum可以把自己安装成一个名为NtmSsvc的新服务

en_text: To establish persistence, SslMM identifies the Start Menu Startup directory and drops a link to its own executable disguised as an "Office Start," "Yahoo Talk," "MSN Gaming Z0ne," or "MSN Talk" shortcut.
Text: 为了建立持久性，SslMM识别了 "开始 "菜单的 "启动 "目录，并将其自身的可执行文件链接伪装成 "Office Start"、"Yahoo Talk"、"MSN Gaming Z0ne "或 "MSN Talk "快捷方式

en_text: To establish persistence, Truvasys adds a Registry Run key with a value "TaskMgr" in an attempt to masquerade as the legitimate Windows Task Manager.
Text: 为了建立持久性，Truvasys添加了一个注册表运行键，其值为 "TaskMgr"，试图伪装成合法的Windows任务管理器

en_text: To move laterally on a victim network, FIN6 has used credentials stolen from various systems on which it gathered usernames and password hashes.
Text: 为了在受害者网络中横向移动，FIN6使用了从各种系统中窃取的凭证，在这些系统中收集用户名和密码散列

en_text: Unknown Logger can obtain information about the victim's IP address.
Text: 未知的记录器可以获得受害者的IP地址信息

en_text: Unknown Logger can obtain information about the victim usernames.
Text: 未知的记录器可以获得有关受害者用户名的信息

en_text: Unknown Logger is capable of spreading to USB devices.
Text: 未知的记录器能够传播到USB设备

en_text: Unknown Logger is capable of recording keystrokes.
Text: 未知的记录器能够记录击键

en_text: Unknown Logger has functionality to disable security tools, including Kaspersky, BitDefender, and MalwareBytes.
Text: 未知记录器具有禁用安全工具的功能，包括卡巴斯基、BitDefender和MalwareBytes

en_text: Unknown Logger can obtain information about the victim computer name, physical memory, country, and date.
Text: 未知记录器可以获得有关受害者计算机名称、物理内存、国家和日期的信息

en_text: Unknown Logger is capable of stealing usernames and passwords from browsers on the victim machine.
Text: 未知记录器能够从受害者机器上的浏览器窃取用户名和密码

en_text: Unknown Logger is capable of downloading remote files.
Text: 未知记录仪能够下载远程文件

en_text: Winnti Group looked for a specific process running on infected servers.
Text: 温蒂集团寻找在受感染的服务器上运行的一个特定进程

en_text: The file name AcroRD32.exe, a legitimate process name for Adobe's Acrobat Reader, was used by APT1 as a name for malware.
Text: 文件名AcroRD32.exe是Adobe公司Acrobat Reader的一个合法进程名称，被APT1用作恶意软件的名称

en_text: Mosquito can upload and download files to the victim.
Text: 蚊子可以向受害者上传和下载文件

en_text: A Volgmer variant is encoded using a simple XOR cipher.
Text: 沃尔格默变体是用一个简单的XOR密码来编码的

en_text: Volgmer queries the system to identify existing services.
Text: 沃尔格默查询系统以确定现有服务

en_text: Volgmer can gather a list of processes.
Text: 沃尔格默可以收集一个进程的清单

en_text: Hi-Zor has the ability to create a reverse shell.
Text: 希-佐尔有能力创造一个反向的外壳

en_text: Responder captures hashes and credentials that are sent to the system after the name services have been poisoned.
Text: 响应者捕获名称服务被毒害后发送到系统的哈希值和凭证。

en_text: Impacket modules like GetUserSPNs can be used to get Service Principal Names (SPNs) for user accounts. The output is formatted to be compatible with cracking tools like John the Ripper and Hashcat.
Text: 像GetUserSPNs这样的Impacket模块可以用来获取用户账户的服务主名称（SPNs）。输出的格式与John the Ripper和Hashcat等破解工具兼容。

en_text: Micropsia creates a shortcut to maintain persistence.
Text: 小儿麻痹症创造了一个维持持久性的捷径

en_text: Pony has been delivered via spearphishing attachments.
Text: 小马哥是通过鱼叉式钓鱼的附件传递的

en_text: Pony can download additional files onto the infected system.
Text: 小马可以下载更多的文件到受感染的系统

en_text: Pony has used the Adobe Reader icon for the downloaded file to look more trustworthy.
Text: 小马使用了Adobe Reader的图标来下载文件，看起来更值得信赖

en_text: Pony has used several Windows functions for various purposes.
Text: 小马为各种目的使用了几个Windows功能

en_text: Many Misdat samples were programmed using Borland Delphi, which will mangle the default PE compile timestamp of a file.
Text: 许多Misdat样本是用Borland Delphi编程的，它将会篡改一个文件的默认PE编译时间戳

en_text: Many ZeroT samples can perform UAC bypass by using eventvwr.exe to execute a malicious file.
Text: 许多ZeroT样本可以通过使用eventvwr.exe执行恶意文件来进行UAC绕过

en_text: Rising Sun can detect the username of the infected host.
Text: 旭日公司可以检测到被感染主机的用户名

en_text: Rising Sun can detect the computer name, operating system, and other native system information.
Text: 旭日公司可以检测计算机名称、操作系统和其他本地系统信息

en_text: Rising Sun can detect network adapter and IP address information.
Text: 旭日公司可以检测网络适配器和IP地址信息

en_text: Rising Sun can modify file attributes to hide files.
Text: 旭日公司可以修改文件属性来隐藏文件

en_text: Rising Sun executed commands using cmd.exe.
Text: 旭日公司使用cmd.exe执行命令

en_text: Configuration data used by Rising Sun is encrypted using RC4.
Text: 旭日公司使用的配置数据是用RC4加密的

en_text: Rising Sun used dynamic API resolutions to various Windows APIs by leveraging LoadLibrary() and GetProcAddress().
Text: 旭日公司通过利用LoadLibrary()和GetProcAddress()对各种Windows API进行了动态API解析

en_text: Rising Sun has used HTTP for command and control.
Text: 旭日公司已将HTTP用于指挥和控制

en_text: Rising Sun can enumerate information about files from the infected system, including file size, attributes, creation time, last access time, and write time. Rising Sun can enumerate the compilation timestamp of Windows executable files.
Text: 旭日公司可以列举被感染系统中的文件信息，包括文件大小、属性、创建时间、最后访问时间和写入时间。旭日阳刚可以列举出Windows可执行文件的编译时间戳。

en_text: Rising Sun can enumerate all running processes and process information on an infected machine.
Text: 旭日公司可以列举出受感染机器上的所有运行进程和进程信息

en_text: Leafminer has infected victims using watering holes.
Text: 叶蝉利用浇水孔感染了受害者

en_text: Night Dragon has used compromised VPN accounts to gain access to victim systems.
Text: 夜龙 "利用被入侵的VPN账户进入受害者系统

en_text: Night Dragon used pass-the-hash tools to gain usernames and passwords.
Text: 夜龙 "使用传递哈希工具获得用户名和密码

en_text: Night Dragon has used several remote administration tools as persistent infiltration channels.
Text: 夜龙 "使用了几个远程管理工具作为持久的渗透渠道

en_text: Night Dragon enticed users to click on links in spearphishing emails to download malware.
Text: 夜龙 "诱使用户点击鱼叉式网络钓鱼邮件中的链接，下载恶意软件

en_text: Night Dragon has performed SQL injection attacks of extranet web servers to gain access.
Text: 夜龙公司对外网网络服务器进行了SQL注入攻击，以获得访问权限

en_text: Night Dragon sent spearphishing emails containing links to compromised websites where malware was downloaded.
Text: 夜龙公司发送的鱼叉式网络钓鱼电子邮件中包含有下载恶意软件的受损网站的链接

en_text: Night Dragon has copied files to company web servers and subsequently downloaded them.
Text: 夜龙公司将文件复制到公司的网络服务器上，随后下载了这些文件

en_text: Night Dragon has used HTTP for C2.
Text: 夜龙公司已将HTTP用于C2

en_text: Night Dragon has disabled anti-virus and anti-spyware tools in some instances on the victim’s machines. The actors have also disabled proxy settings to allow direct communication from victims to the Internet.
Text: 夜龙公司在某些情况下禁用了受害者机器上的反病毒和反间谍软件工具。行动者还关闭了代理设置，允许受害者与互联网直接通信。

en_text: Night Dragon has dumped account hashes with Carbanak and cracked them with Cain & Abel.
Text: 夜龙用Carbanak倾倒了账户哈希值，用Cain破解了它们

en_text: Once APT28 gained access to the DCCC network, the group then proceeded to use that access to compromise the DNC network.
Text: 一旦APT28获得了对DCCC网络的访问权，该组织就开始使用这一访问权来破坏DNC网络

en_text: Once Shamoon has access to a network share, it enables the RemoteRegistry service on the target system. It will then connect to the system with RegConnectRegistryW and modify the Registry to disable UAC remote restrictions by setting SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Policies\System\LocalAccountTokenFilterPolicy to 1.
Text: 一旦Shamoon能够访问一个网络共享，它就会在目标系统上启用RemoteRegistry服务。然后，它将用RegConnectRegistryW连接到系统，并通过将SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Policies\System\LocalAccountTokenFilterPolicy设置为1，修改注册表以禁用UAC远程限制。

en_text: HTTPBrowser deletes its original installer file once installation is complete.
Text: 一旦安装完成，HTTPBrowser将删除其原始安装文件

en_text: Emotet leverages the Admin$ share for lateral movement once the local admin password has been brute forced.
Text: 一旦本地管理员密码被暴力破解，Emotet就会利用Admin$共享进行横向移动

en_text: Shamoon will reboot the infected system once the wiping functionality has been completed.
Text: 一旦擦除功能完成，Shamoon将重新启动被感染的系统

en_text: Once loaded into memory, MESSAGETAP deletes the keyword_parm.txt and parm.txt configuration files from disk.
Text: 一旦加载到内存中，MESSAGETAP就会从磁盘中删除keyword_parm.txt和parm.txt配置文件

en_text: Once a removable media device is inserted back into the first victim, USBStealer collects data from it that was exfiltrated from a second victim.
Text: 一旦可移动媒体设备被插回第一个受害者体内，USBStealer就会从其中收集从第二个受害者身上渗出的数据

en_text: Goopy has the ability to delete emails used for C2 once the content has been copied.
Text: 一旦内容被复制，Goopy有能力删除用于C2的电子邮件

en_text: Once a file is uploaded, Machete will delete it from the machine.
Text: 一旦文件被上传，Machete将从机器上删除它

en_text: An APT19 HTTP malware variant establishes persistence by setting the Registry key HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\Windows Debug Tools-%LOCALAPPDATA%\.
Text: 一个APT19 HTTP恶意软件变体通过设置注册表键HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\Windows Debug Tools-%LOCALAPPDATA%\建立持久性

en_text: An APT19 Port 22 malware variant registers itself as a service.
Text: 一个APT19端口22的恶意软件变体将自己注册为一个服务

en_text: An APT28 macro uses the command certutil -decode to decode contents of a .txt file storing the base64 encoded payload.
Text: 一个APT28宏使用命令certutil -decode来解码存储base64编码有效载荷的.txt文件的内容

en_text: An APT28 backdoor may collect the entire contents of an inserted USB device.
Text: 一个APT28后门可能会收集插入的USB设备的全部内容

en_text: An APT28 loader Trojan adds the Registry key HKCU\Environment\UserInitMprLogonScript to establish persistence.
Text: 一个APT28加载器木马添加注册表键HKCU\Environment\UserInitMprLogonScript以建立持久性

en_text: An APT28 loader Trojan uses a cmd.exe and batch script to run its payload. The group has also used macros to execute payloads.
Text: 一个APT28装载机木马使用cmd.exe和批处理脚本来运行其有效载荷

en_text: An APT32 backdoor can use HTTP over a non-standard TCP port (e.g 14146) which is specified in the backdoor configuration.
Text: 一个APT32后门可以通过一个非标准的TCP端口（如14146）使用HTTP，这在后门配置中被指定

en_text: An APT3 downloader uses the Windows command "cmd.exe" /C whoami to verify that it is running with the elevated privileges of "System."
Text: 一个APT3下载器使用Windows命令 "cmd.exe" /C whoami来验证它是以 "系统 "的高权限运行。

en_text: An APT3 downloader uses the Windows command "cmd.exe" /C whoami. The group also uses a tool to execute commands on remote computers.
Text: 一个APT3下载器使用Windows命令 "cmd.exe" /C whoami。该组织还使用一个工具在远程计算机上执行命令。

en_text: An APT3 downloader first establishes a SOCKS5 connection to 192.157.198[.]103 using TCP port 1913; once the server response is verified, it then requests a connection to 192.184.60[.]229 on TCP port 81.
Text: 一个APT3下载器首先使用TCP端口1913与192.157.198[.]103建立了一个SOCKS5连接；一旦服务器的响应被验证，它就要求通过TCP端口81与192.184.60[.]229建立连接

en_text: An APT3 downloader creates persistence by creating the following scheduled task: schtasks /create /tn "mysc" /tr C:\Users\Public\test.exe /sc ONLOGON /ru "System".
Text: 一个APT3下载器通过创建以下计划任务来创建持久性： schtasks /create /tn "mysc" /tr C:\Users\Public\test.exe /sc ONLOGON /ru "System"。

en_text: An APT3 downloader establishes SOCKS5 connections for its initial C2.
Text: 一个APT3下载器为其初始C2建立了SOCKS5连接

en_text: A BlackEnergy 2 plug-in uses WMI to gather victim host details.
Text: 一个BlackEnergy 2插件使用WMI来收集受害者主机的详细信息

en_text: A Dipsind variant registers as a Winlogon Event Notify DLL to establish persistence.
Text: 一个Dipsind变体注册为Winlogon Event Notify DLL以建立持久性

en_text: A FinFisher variant uses DLL search order hijacking.
Text: 一个FinFisher变体使用DLL搜索顺序劫持

en_text: A FinFisher variant uses a custom packer.
Text: 一个FinFisher变体使用一个定制的包装器

en_text: A gh0st RAT variant has used rundll32 for execution.
Text: 一个gh0st RAT变种使用rundll32来执行

en_text: A gh0st RAT variant has used DLL side-loading.
Text: 一个gh0st RAT的变种使用了DLL侧载

en_text: A JHUHUGIT variant encodes C2 POST data base64.
Text: 一个JHUHUGIT变体对C2 POST数据base64进行编码

en_text: A JHUHUGIT variant accesses a screenshot saved in the clipboard and converts it to a JPG image.
Text: 一个JHUHUGIT变体访问保存在剪贴板中的屏幕截图并将其转换为JPG图像

en_text: A JHUHUGIT variant gathers network interface card information.
Text: 一个JHUHUGIT变体收集网络接口卡信息

en_text: A JHUHUGIT variant takes screenshots by simulating the user pressing the "Take Screenshot" key (VK_SCREENSHOT), accessing the screenshot saved in the clipboard, and converting it to a JPG image.
Text: 一个JHUHUGIT变体通过模拟用户按下 "截图 "键（VK_SCREENSHOT）来进行截图，访问保存在剪贴板中的截图，并将其转换为JPG图像

en_text: A JPIN variant downloads the backdoor payload via the BITS service.
Text: 一个JPIN变体通过BITS服务下载后门有效载荷

en_text: A Lazarus Group malware sample adds persistence on the system by creating a shortcut in the user’s Startup folder.
Text: 一个Lazarus集团的恶意软件样本通过在用户的启动文件夹中创建一个快捷方式来增加系统的持久性

en_text: A Linux version of Derusbi checks if the victim user ID is anything other than zero (normally used for root), and the malware will not execute if it does not have root privileges. Derusbi also gathers the username of the victim.
Text: Derusbi的Linux版本会检查受害者的用户ID是否为零（通常用于root），如果没有root权限，恶意软件将不会执行。Derusbi还收集了受害者的用户名。

en_text: A OilRig macro has run a PowerShell command to decode file contents. OilRig has also used certutil to decode base64-encoded files on victims.
Text: 一个OilRig的宏已经运行了一个PowerShell命令来解码文件内容。OilRig还使用certutil来解码受害者的base64编码文件。

en_text: A Patchwork payload was packed with UPX.
Text: 一个Patchwork有效载荷被装入UPX

en_text: A Patchwork payload deletes Resiliency Registry keys created by Microsoft Office applications in an apparent effort to trick users into thinking there were no issues during application runs.
Text: 一个Patchwork有效载荷删除了微软Office应用程序创建的Resiliency注册表键，显然是为了欺骗用户，使其认为在应用程序运行期间没有问题

en_text: A Patchwork payload uses process hollowing to hide the UAC bypass vulnerability exploitation inside svchost.exe.
Text: 一个Patchwork有效载荷使用进程中空来隐藏在svchost.exe内的UAC绕过漏洞利用

en_text: A Patchwork payload has searched all fixed drives on the victim for files matching a specified list of extensions.
Text: 一个Patchwork有效载荷已经搜索了受害者的所有固定驱动器，以寻找与指定扩展名列表相匹配的文件

en_text: A Turla JavaScript backdoor has used Google Apps Script as its C2 server.
Text: 一个Turla JavaScript后门使用谷歌应用脚本作为其C2服务器

en_text: A Turla Javascript backdoor added a local_update_check value under the Registry key HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run to establish persistence. Additionally, a Turla custom executable containing Metasploit shellcode is saved to the Startup folder to gain persistence.
Text: 一个Turla Javascript后门在注册表键HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run下增加了一个local_update_check值以建立持久性。此外，一个包含Metasploit shellcode的Turla定制可执行文件被保存在启动文件夹中，以获得持久性。

en_text: A TYPEFRAME variant can force the compromised system to function as a proxy server.
Text: 一个TYPEFRAME变体可以迫使被攻击的系统作为一个代理服务器发挥作用。

en_text: One TYPEFRAME variant decrypts an archive using an RC4 key, then decompresses and installs the decrypted malicious DLL module. Another variant decodes the embedded file by XORing it with the value "0x35".
Text: 一个TYPEFRAME变体使用RC4密钥对档案进行解密，然后解压并安装解密的恶意DLL模块。另一个变种通过与数值 "0x35 "进行XOR来解码嵌入式文件。

en_text: A Winnti for Windows implant file was named ASPNET_FILTER.DLL, mimicking the legitimate ASP.NET ISAPI filter DLL with the same name.
Text: 一个Winnti for Windows的植入文件被命名为ASPNET_FILTER.DLL，模仿同名的合法ASP.NET ISAPI过滤器DLL

en_text: A Patchwork .dll that contains BADNEWS is loaded and executed using DLL side-loading.
Text: 一个包含BADNEWS的Patchwork.dll被加载，并使用DLL侧面加载执行

en_text: A Word document delivering TYPEFRAME prompts the user to enable macro execution.
Text: 一个提供TYPEFRAME的Word文档提示用户启用宏执行

en_text: A Night Dragon DLL included an XOR-encoded section.
Text: 一个夜龙DLL包括一个XOR编码部分

en_text: A dropper used by Putter Panda installs itself into the ASEP Registry key HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run with a value named McUpdate.
Text: 一个由Putter Panda使用的dropper将自己安装到ASEP注册表键HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run中，其值名为McUpdate

en_text: Some Backdoor.Oldrea samples contain a publicly available Web browser password recovery tool.
Text: 一些Backdoor.Oldrea样本包含一个公开可用的网络浏览器密码恢复工具

en_text: Some Backdoor.Oldrea samples use standard Base64 + bzip2, and some use standard Base64 + reverse XOR + RSA-2048 to decrypt data received from C2 servers.
Text: 一些Backdoor.Oldrea样本使用标准的Base64 bzip2，一些使用标准的Base64反向XOR RSA-2048来解密从C2服务器收到的数据

en_text: Several BRONZE BUTLER tools encode data with base64 when posting it to a C2 server.
Text: 一些BRONZE BUTLER工具在将数据发布到C2服务器时用base64进行编码

en_text: Some Daserf samples were signed with a stolen digital certificate.
Text: 一些Daserf样品是用被盗的数字证书签署的

en_text: Some Felismus samples use a custom method for C2 traffic that utilizes Base64.
Text: 一些Felismus样本对C2流量使用了一种自定义的方法，利用Base64

en_text: Some Felismus samples use a custom encryption method for C2 traffic that utilizes AES and multiple keys.
Text: 一些Felismus样本对C2流量使用自定义加密方法，利用AES和多个密钥

en_text: Some FinFisher variants incorporate an MBR rootkit.
Text: 一些FinFisher变种包含了一个MBR rootkit

en_text: Some InnaputRAT variants create a new Windows service to establish persistence.
Text: 一些InnaputRAT变种创建一个新的Windows服务以建立持久性

en_text: Some InnaputRAT variants establish persistence by modifying the Registry key HKU\\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run:%appdata%\NeutralApp\NeutralApp.exe.
Text: 一些InnaputRAT变种通过修改注册表键HKU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run:%appdata%\NeutralApp\NeutralApp.exe建立持久性

en_text: Several Lazarus Group malware families collect information on the type and version of the victim OS, as well as the victim computer name and CPU information. A Destover-like variant used by Lazarus Group also collects disk space information and sends it to its C2 server..
Text: 一些Lazarus集团的恶意软件家族会收集受害者操作系统的类型和版本信息，以及受害者计算机的名称和CPU信息。Lazarus集团使用的一个类似Destover的变体也收集磁盘空间信息并将其发送到其C2服务器。

en_text: Several Lazarus Group malware families encrypt C2 traffic using custom code that uses XOR with an ADD operation and XOR with a SUB operation. Another Lazarus Group malware sample XORs C2 traffic. Other Lazarus Group malware uses Caracachs encryption to encrypt C2 payloads.
Text: 一些Lazarus集团的恶意软件家族使用自定义代码对C2流量进行加密，这些代码使用XOR与ADD操作和XOR与SUB操作。另一个Lazarus集团的恶意软件样本XOR了C2流量。其他Lazarus集团的恶意软件使用Caracachs加密来加密C2有效载荷。

en_text: Several Lazarus Group malware families gather a list of running processes on a victim system and send it to their C2 server. A Destover-like variant used by Lazarus Group also gathers process times.
Text: 一些Lazarus集团的恶意软件家族收集受害者系统上正在运行的进程列表，并将其发送到他们的C2服务器。Lazarus集团使用的一个类似Destover的变体也收集了进程时间。

en_text: Some Lazarus Group malware uses a list of ordered port numbers to choose a port for C2 traffic, creating port-protocol mismatches.
Text: 一些Lazarus集团的恶意软件使用有序的端口号列表来选择C2流量的端口，造成端口协议的不匹配。

en_text: Several Lazarus Group malware samples use a common function to identify target files by their extension. Lazarus Group malware families can also enumerate files and directories, including a Destover-like variant that lists files and gathers information for all drives.
Text: 一些Lazarus集团的恶意软件样本使用一个共同的功能，通过其扩展名来识别目标文件。Lazarus集团的恶意软件家族还可以列举文件和目录，包括一个类似Destover的变种，列出文件并收集所有驱动器的信息。

en_text: Some MiniDuke components use Twitter to initially obtain the address of a C2 server or as a backup if no hard-coded C2 server responds.
Text: 一些MiniDuke组件使用Twitter最初获得C2服务器的地址，或者在没有硬编码的C2服务器响应时作为备份。

en_text: Some Orz versions have an embedded DLL known as MockDll that uses Process Hollowing and regsvr32 to execute another payload.
Text: 一些Orz版本有一个被称为MockDll的嵌入式DLL，使用Process Hollowing和regsvr32来执行另一个有效载荷。

en_text: Some Orz versions have an embedded DLL known as MockDll that uses process hollowing and Regsvr32 to execute another payload.
Text: 一些Orz版本有一个被称为MockDll的嵌入式DLL，它使用进程挖空和Regsvr32来执行另一个有效载荷。

en_text: Some Orz strings are base64 encoded, such as the embedded DLL known as MockDll.
Text: 一些Orz字符串是以base64编码的，例如被称为MockDll的嵌入式DLL

en_text: Some Reaver variants use HTTP for C2.
Text: 一些Reaver变种使用HTTP进行C2

en_text: Some Reaver variants use raw TCP for C2.
Text: 一些Reaver变种使用原始TCP进行C2

en_text: Some Sakula samples use cmd.exe to delete temporary files.
Text: 一些Sakula样本使用cmd.exe来删除临时文件

en_text: Some Sakula samples install themselves as services for persistence by calling WinExec with the net start argument.
Text: 一些Sakula样本通过调用带有net start参数的WinExec将自己安装为持久性服务

en_text: Some SeaDuke samples have a module to use pass the ticket with Kerberos for authentication.
Text: 一些SeaDuke样本有一个模块，可以使用Kerberos的pass the ticket进行认证

en_text: Some SeaDuke samples have a module to extract email from Microsoft Exchange servers using compromised credentials.
Text: 一些SeaDuke样本有一个模块，可以使用被破坏的凭证从微软Exchange服务器中提取电子邮件

en_text: Some TrickBot samples have used HTTP over ports 447 and 8082 for C2.
Text: 一些TrickBot样本通过447和8082端口使用HTTP进行C2

en_text: Some Volgmer variants add new services with display names generated by a list of hard-coded strings such as Application, Background, Security, and Windows, presumably as a way to masquerade as a legitimate service.
Text: 一些Volgmer变种增加了新的服务，其显示名称由一系列硬编码的字符串生成，如应用、后台、安全和Windows，大概是作为一种伪装成合法服务的方式

en_text: Some ZeroT DLL files have been packed with UPX.
Text: 一些ZeroT DLL文件已经被打包成UPX

en_text: Some versions of CozyCar will check to ensure it is not being executed inside a virtual machine or a known malware analysis sandbox environment. If it detects that it is, it will exit.
Text: 一些版本的CozyCar会检查以确保它没有在虚拟机或已知的恶意软件分析沙盒环境中执行

en_text: Some malware that has been used by Axiom also uses steganography to hide communication in PNG image files.
Text: 一些被Axiom使用过的恶意软件也使用隐写术，将通信隐藏在PNG图像文件中

en_text: Some Volgmer variants use SSL to encrypt C2 communications.
Text: 一些沃尔格默的变种使用SSL来加密C2通信

en_text: Some Brave Prince variants have used South  Korea's Daum email service to exfiltrate information, and later variants have posted the data to a web server via an HTTP post command.
Text: 一些勇敢的王子变种使用韩国的Daum电子邮件服务来渗出信息，后来的变种通过HTTP发布命令将数据发布到网络服务器上

en_text: Emotet has been observed enumerating local processes.
Text: 已观察到Emotet列举了当地的进程

en_text: HOPLIGHT has been observed loading several APIs associated with Pass the Hash.
Text: 已观察到HOPLIGHT加载了与Pass the Hash相关的几个API

en_text: HOPLIGHT has been observed enumerating system drives and partitions.
Text: 已观察到HOPLIGHT在列举系统驱动器和分区

en_text: LockerGoga has been observed deleting its original launcher after execution.
Text: 已观察到LockerGoga在执行后删除了它的原始启动器

en_text: Equation has been observed utilizing environmental keying in payload delivery.
Text: 已观察到在有效载荷交付中利用环境键控的方程

en_text: Kimsuky has been observed disabling the system firewall.
Text: 已经观察到Kimsuky禁用了系统防火墙

en_text: ComRAT samples have been seen which hijack COM objects for persistence by replacing the path to shell32.dll in registry location HKCU\Software\Classes\CLSID{{42aedc87-2188-41fd-b9a3-0c966feabec1}}\InprocServer32.
Text: 已经看到ComRAT样本通过替换注册表位置HKCU\Software\Classes\CLSID{{42aedc87-2188-41fd-b9a3-0c966feabec1}}{InprocServer32}中的shell32.dll路径来劫持COM对象以实现持久化

en_text: Derusbi variants have been seen that use Registry persistence to proxy execution through regsvr32.exe.
Text: 已经看到Derusbi变种利用注册表的持久性，通过regsvr32.exe代理执行

en_text: Pteranodon can execute commands on the victim.
Text: 翼龙可以对受害者执行命令

en_text: Brave Prince gathers file and directory information from the victim’s machine.
Text: 勇敢的王子从受害者的机器上收集文件和目录信息

en_text: Brave Prince lists the running processes.
Text: 勇敢的王子列出了正在运行的进程

en_text: Brave Prince gathers information about the Registry.
Text: 勇敢的王子收集了关于注册处的信息

en_text: Brave Prince terminates antimalware processes.
Text: 勇敢的王子终止了反恶意软件进程

en_text: Exaramel for Linux has a command to execute a shell command on the system.
Text: 用于Linux的Exaramel有一个命令可以在系统上执行shell命令

en_text: Exaramel for Windows has a command to execute VBS scripts on the victim’s machine.
Text: 用于Windows的Exaramel有一个命令可以在受害者的机器上执行VBS脚本

en_text: Exaramel for Windows has a command to launch a remote shell and executes commands on the victim’s machine.
Text: 用于Windows的Exaramel有一个启动远程shell的命令，并在受害者的机器上执行命令

en_text: FlawedAmmyy may obfuscate portions of the initial C2 handshake.
Text: 有缺陷的Ammyy可能混淆了初始C2握手的部分内容

en_text: EvilBunny has been observed querying installed antivirus software.
Text: 有人观察到EvilBunny查询已安装的防病毒软件

en_text: Kimsuky has been observed turning off Windows Security Center.
Text: 有人观察到Kimsuky关闭了Windows安全中心

en_text: Silence has been observed making videos of victims to observe bank employees day to day activities.
Text: 有人观察到沉默者制作受害者的视频，观察银行员工的日常活动

en_text: BBSRAT has been seen persisting via COM hijacking through replacement of the COM object for MruPidlList {{42aedc87-2188-41fd-b9a3-0c966feabec1}} or Microsoft WBEM New Event Subsystem {{F3130CDB-AA52-4C3A-AB32-85FFC23AF9C1}} depending on the system's CPU architecture.
Text: 有人看到BBSRAT通过COM劫持，通过替换MruPidlList {{42aedc87-2188-41fd-b9a3-0c966feabec1}}或Microsoft WBEM New Event Subsystem {{F3130CDB-AA52-4C3A-AB32-85FFC23AF9C1}}的COM对象持续存在，具体取决于系统的CPU架构

en_text: BBSRAT has been seen loaded into msiexec.exe through process hollowing to hide its execution.
Text: 有人看到BBSRAT通过进程空洞化加载到msiexec.exe中以隐藏其执行

en_text: Emotet has been seen exploiting SMB via a vulnerability exploit like ETERNALBLUE (MS17-010) to achieve lateral movement and propagation.
Text: 有人看到Emotet通过像ETERNALBLUE（MS17-010）这样的漏洞利用SMB来实现横向移动和传播

en_text: Okrum was seen using a RAR archiver tool to compress/decompress data.
Text: 有人看到Okrum使用RAR存档工具来压缩/解压数据。

en_text: TA505 has been seen injecting a DLL into winword.exe.
Text: 有人看到TA505将一个DLL注入winword.exe中

en_text: Okrum was seen using a keylogger tool to capture keystrokes.
Text: 有人看到奥克鲁姆使用键盘记录器工具来捕捉键盘信息

en_text: There is a variant of RATANKBA that uses a PowerShell script instead of the traditional PE form.
Text: 有一个RATANKBA的变种，使用PowerShell脚本而不是传统的PE形式

en_text: The discovery modules used with Duqu can collect information on process details.
Text: 与Duqu一起使用的发现模块可以收集关于进程细节的信息

en_text: The discovery modules used with Duqu can collect information on accounts and permissions.
Text: 与Duqu一起使用的发现模块可以收集关于账户和权限的信息

en_text: The discovery modules used with Duqu can collect information on open windows.
Text: 与Duqu一起使用的发现模块可以收集开放窗口的信息

en_text: The discovery modules used with Duqu can collect information on network connections.
Text: 与Duqu一起使用的发现模块可以收集网络连接的信息

en_text: The reconnaissance modules used with Duqu can collect information on network configuration.
Text: 与Duqu一起使用的侦察模块可以收集有关网络配置的信息

en_text: CosmicDuke collects LSA secrets.
Text: 宇宙公爵收集LSA的秘密

en_text: ShimRat can sleep when instructed to do so by the C2.
Text: 在C2的指示下，ShimRat可以睡觉

en_text: Downdelph inserts pseudo-random characters between each original character during encoding of C2 network requests, making it difficult to write signatures on them.
Text: 在C2网络请求的编码过程中，Downdelph在每个原始字符之间插入了伪随机字符，使其难以写入签名

en_text: In one version of KeyBoy, string obfuscation routines were used to hide many of the critical values referenced in the malware.
Text: 在KeyBoy的一个版本中，字符串混淆程序被用来隐藏恶意软件中引用的许多关键值

en_text: Commands such as net group and net localgroup can be used in Net to gather information about and manipulate groups.
Text: 在Net中可以使用net group和net localgroup等命令来收集有关组的信息并进行操作

en_text: Commands such as net use and net session can be used in Net to gather information about network connections from a particular host.
Text: 在Net中可以使用net use和net session等命令来收集来自特定主机的网络连接信息

en_text: Commands such as net view can be used in Net to gather information about available remote systems.
Text: 在Net中可以使用net view等命令来收集可用的远程系统的信息

en_text: During the T9000 installation process, it drops a copy of the legitimate Microsoft binary igfxtray.exe. The executable contains a side-loading weakness which is used to load a portion of the malware.
Text: 在T9000的安装过程中，它投放了一份合法的微软二进制文件igfxtray.exe的副本。该可执行文件包含一个侧面加载的弱点，用来加载一部分恶意软件。

en_text: Before being appended to image files, HAMMERTOSS commands are encrypted with a key composed of both a hard-coded value and a string contained on that day's tweet. To decrypt the commands, an investigator would need access to the intended malware sample, the day's tweet, and the image file containing the command.
Text: 在被附加到图像文件之前，HAMMERTOSS的命令是用一个由硬编码值和当天推特上的字符串组成的密钥加密的。要解密这些命令，调查人员需要获得预定的恶意软件样本、当天的推特和包含命令的图像文件。

en_text: After creating a new service for persistence, TDTESS sets the file creation time for the service to the creation time of the victim's legitimate svchost.exe file.
Text: 在创建一个新的持久性服务后，TDTESS将服务的文件创建时间设置为受害者的合法svchost.exe文件的创建时间

en_text: Silence has used port 444 when sending data about the system from the client to the server.
Text: 在从客户端向服务器发送有关系统的数据时，Silence使用了444号端口

en_text: After encrypting C2 data, BADNEWS converts it into a hexadecimal representation and then encodes it into base64.
Text: 在对C2数据进行加密后，BADNEWS将其转换为十六进制表示，然后将其编码为base64

en_text: After encrypting its own log files, the log encryption module in Prikormka deletes the original, unencrypted files from the host.
Text: 在对自己的日志文件进行加密后，Prikormka的日志加密模块会从主机上删除原始的、未加密的文件

en_text: After loading the keyword and phone data files, MESSAGETAP begins monitoring all network connections to and from the victim server.
Text: 在加载关键词和电话数据文件后，MESSAGETAP开始监控所有进出受害者服务器的网络连接

en_text: After checking for the existence of two files, keyword_parm.txt and parm.txt, MESSAGETAP XOR decodes and read the contents of the files.
Text: 在检查是否存在两个文件，keyword_parm.txt和parm.txt之后，MESSAGETAP XOR解码并读取文件的内容

en_text: After copying itself to a DLL file, a variant of Elise calls the DLL file using rundll32.exe.
Text: 在将自己复制到一个DLL文件后，Elise的一个变种使用rundll32.exe调用该DLL文件

en_text: at can be used to schedule a task on a system.
Text: 在可以用来安排一个系统上的任务

en_text: Following exploitation with LOWBALL malware, admin@338 actors created a file containing a list of commands to be executed on the compromised computer.
Text: 在利用LOWBALL恶意软件后，admin@338行为人创建了一个文件，其中包含一个将在被攻击的计算机上执行的命令列表

en_text: Sharpshooter downloaded additional payloads after a target was infected with a first-stage downloader.
Text: 在目标被第一阶段的下载器感染后，Sharpshooter下载了额外的有效载荷

en_text: After decrypting itself in memory, RARSTONE downloads a DLL file from its C2 server and loads it in the memory space of a hidden Internet Explorer process. This "downloaded" file is actually not dropped onto the system.
Text: 在内存中解密后，RARSTONE从其C2服务器下载一个DLL文件，并将其加载到一个隐藏的Internet Explorer进程的内存空间

en_text: During its initial execution, BACKSPACE extracts operating system information from the infected host.
Text: 在其初始执行过程中，BACKSPACE从被感染的主机中提取操作系统信息

en_text: After compromising a victim, Poseidon Group discovers all running services.
Text: 在入侵受害者后，波塞冬集团发现了所有正在运行的服务

en_text: Attor has staged collected data in a central upload directory prior to exfiltration.
Text: 在渗出之前，Attor已将收集的数据存放在一个中央上传目录中

en_text: Before exfiltration, Okrum's backdoor has used hidden files to store logs and outputs from backdoor commands.
Text: 在渗出之前，Okrum的后门已经使用隐藏文件来存储日志和后门命令的输出

en_text: Soft Cell compressed and staged files in multi-part archives in the Recycle Bin prior to exfiltration.
Text: 在渗透之前，Soft Cell在回收站的多部分档案中压缩和暂存了文件

en_text: Ebury has disabled logging when the backdoor is used.
Text: 在使用后门时，Ebury已经禁用了日志记录

en_text: Maze has used the "Wow64RevertWow64FsRedirection" function following attempts to delete the shadow volumes, in order to leave the system in the same state as it was prior to redirection.
Text: 在试图删除影子卷之后，Maze使用了 "Wow64RevertWow64FsRedirection "函数，以使系统处于重定向之前的状态

en_text: Following data collection, FIN6 has compressed log files into a ZIP archive prior to staging and exfiltration.
Text: 在收集数据后，FIN6在分期和渗出前将日志文件压缩成ZIP档案

en_text: Suckfly the victim's internal network for hosts with ports 8080, 5900, and 40 open.
Text: 在受害者的内部网络中搜索8080、5900和40端口开放的主机

en_text: After downloading its main config file, Downdelph downloads multiple payloads from C2 servers.
Text: 在下载其主配置文件后，Downdelph从C2服务器下载多个有效载荷

en_text: Before writing to disk, Kwampirs inserts a randomly generated string into the middle of the decrypted payload in an attempt to evade hash-based detections.
Text: 在写入磁盘之前，Kwampirs在解密的有效载荷中间插入一个随机生成的字符串，以试图逃避基于哈希的检测

en_text: In one instance, menuPass added PlugX as a service with a display name of "Corel Writing Tools Utility."
Text: 在一个例子中，menuPass将PlugX添加为一个服务，显示名称为 "Corel Writing Tools Utility"

en_text: During execution, Threat Group-3390 malware deobfuscates and decompresses code that was encoded with Metasploit’s shikata_ga_nai encoder as well as compressed with LZNT1 compression.
Text: 在执行过程中，Threat Group-3390恶意软件对用Metasploit的shikata_ga_nai编码器编码以及用LZNT1压缩的代码进行了解密和解压

en_text: Zeus Panda decrypts strings in the code during the execution process.
Text: 在执行过程中，Zeus Panda对代码中的字符串进行解密

en_text: Gallmaker obfuscated shellcode used during execution.
Text: 在执行过程中使用了Gallmaker混淆的壳代码

en_text: Upon execution, Metamorfo has unzipped itself after being downloaded to the system.
Text: 在执行时，Metamorfo在被下载到系统后已经解压

en_text: Bankshot searches for certain Registry keys to be configured before executing the payload.
Text: 在执行有效载荷之前，Bankshot搜索某些需要配置的注册表键

en_text: After re-establishing access to a victim network, Threat Group-3390 actors download tools including gsecdump and WCE that are staged temporarily on websites that were previously compromised but never used.
Text: 在重新建立对受害者网络的访问后，威胁集团-3390行动者下载了包括gsecdump和WCE在内的工具，这些工具被暂时放置在以前被入侵但从未使用过的网站上

en_text: After initial compromise, Chaos will download a second stage to establish a more permanent presence on the affected system.
Text: 在最初的妥协之后，Chaos将下载第二阶段，在受影响的系统上建立一个更永久的存在

en_text: FlawedAmmyy beacons out the victim operating system and computer name during the initial infection.
Text: 在最初感染期间，FlawedAmmyy会标出受害者的操作系统和计算机名称

en_text: Proton zips up files before exfiltrating them.
Text: 质子 "在渗出文件之前对其进行了压缩

en_text: Proton persists via Launch Agent.
Text: 质子号通过发射代理持续存在

en_text: Proton removes logs from /var/logs and /Library/logs.
Text: 质子将日志从 质子号将日志从 质子公司从以下方面删除日志

en_text: Proton uses macOS' .command file type to script actions.
Text: 质子使用macOS的.command文件类型来编写行动脚本

en_text: Proton uses VNC to connect into systems.
Text: 质子使用VNC来连接到系统

en_text: Proton uses a keylogger to capture keystrokes.
Text: 质子使用键盘记录器来捕捉键盘信息

en_text: Proton uses an encrypted file to store commands and configuration values.
Text: 质子使用一个加密的文件来存储命令和配置值

en_text: Proton prompts users for their credentials.
Text: 质子提示用户的证书

en_text: Proton gathers credentials for Google Chrome.
Text: 质子为谷歌浏览器收集凭证

en_text: Proton captures the content of the desktop with the screencapture binary.
Text: 质子用屏幕捕捉二进制文件来捕捉桌面的内容

en_text: Proton gathers credentials in files for 1password and keychains.
Text: 质子在文件中为1password和钥匙串收集凭证

en_text: China Chopper's server component can spider authentication portals.
Text: 中国砍柴网的服务器组件可以蜘蛛认证门户

en_text: China Chopper's server component can download remote files.
Text: 中国斩波器的服务器组件可以下载远程文件

en_text: China Chopper's server component is capable of opening a command terminal.
Text: 中国斩波器的服务器组件能够打开一个命令终端

en_text: China Chopper's server component executes code sent via HTTP POST commands.
Text: 中国斩波器的服务器组件执行通过HTTP POST命令发送的代码

en_text: APT1 has been known to use credential dumping using Mimikatz.
Text: 众所周知，APT1使用Mimikatz进行凭证转储

en_text: APT3 has been known to brute force password hashes to be able to leverage plain text credentials.
Text: 众所周知，APT3会对密码散列进行暴力破解，以便能够利用纯文本凭证

en_text: Axiom actors have been known to use the Sticky Keys replacement within RDP sessions to obtain persistence.
Text: 众所周知，Axiom行为者在RDP会话中使用Sticky Keys替换，以获得持久性

en_text: Darkhotel has been known to establish persistence by adding programs to the Run Registry key.
Text: 众所周知，Darkhotel通过将程序添加到运行注册表键来建立持久性

en_text: Emotet is known to use RSA keys for encrypting C2 traffic.
Text: 众所周知，Emotet使用RSA密钥对C2流量进行加密

en_text: Equation is known to have the capability to overwrite the firmware on hard drives from some manufacturers.
Text: 众所周知，Equation有能力覆盖一些制造商的硬盘上的固件

en_text: Ke3chang is known to use RAR with passwords to encrypt data prior to exfiltration.
Text: 众所周知，Ke3chang在渗出前使用带有密码的RAR来加密数据

en_text: Moafee has been known to employ binary padding.
Text: 众所周知，Moafee采用了二进制填充

en_text: The Deep Panda group is known to utilize WMI for lateral movement.
Text: 众所周知，深层熊猫组织利用WMI进行横向移动

en_text: Night Dragon is known to use software packing in its tools.
Text: 众所周知，夜龙公司在其工具中使用软件包装

en_text: Zeus Panda can hook GetClipboardData function to watch for clipboard pastes to collect.
Text: 宙斯熊猫可以钩住GetClipboardData函数，观察剪贴板的粘贴情况，以便收集

en_text: Commands such as net group /domain can be used in Net to gather information about and manipulate groups.
Text: 诸如net group之类的命令 诸如net group等命令 诸如net group这样的命令 诸如net group之类的指令

en_text: Anchor can establish persistence by creating a service.
Text: 主播可以通过创建一个服务来建立持久性

en_text: Anchor can create a scheduled task for persistence.
Text: 主播可以为持久性创建一个计划任务

en_text: Anchor can use secondary C2 servers for communication after establishing connectivity and relaying victim information to primary C2 servers.
Text: 主播在建立连接并将受害者信息转发给主播的C2服务器后，可以使用二级C2服务器进行通信

en_text: Recent versions of Cherry Picker delete files and registry keys created by the malware.
Text: 最近版本的Cherry Picker删除了由恶意软件创建的文件和注册表键

en_text: Net Crawler uses Windows admin shares to establish authenticated sessions to remote systems over SMB as part of lateral movement.
Text: 作为横向移动的一部分，Net Crawler使用Windows管理共享通过SMB建立与远程系统的认证会话

en_text: As part of the data reconnaissance phase, Proxysvc grabs the system time to send back to the control server.
Text: 作为数据侦察阶段的一部分，Proxysvc抓取系统时间发回给控制服务器
